NK010(tha)012:1: // bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa rgyud lugs las
NK010(tha)012:2: dbang chog dngos grub rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs zhes bya
NK010(tha)012:3: ba bzhugs / bcom ldan 'das rdo rje phur pa
NK010(tha)012:4: rgyud lugs kyi dbang gi cho ga dngos grub rgya
NK010(tha)012:6: dpal chen khrag 'thung badz+ra ku m+aa ra la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)012:7: de la rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi 'jug sgo'i
NK010(tha)012:8: thog ma ni dbang la ma brten par mi 'grub
NK010(tha)012:9: ste / rdo rje khros pa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:10: bla ma mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK010(tha)012:11: dbang gis smin par ma byas na //
NK010(tha)012:12: thos bsam sgom pa don med 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:13: de bas dbang bskur mchog thob gyis //
NK010(tha)012:15: phur pa rnal 'byor chen po las /
NK010(tha)012:16: 'khor ba dag las byang chub tu //
NK010(tha)012:17: sems bskyed smin par byed pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:18: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK010(tha)012:21: mthar gyi thob bya'i 'bras bu yang dbang gi ngo bo nyid du gnas pa yin te /
NK010(tha)012:23: sems nyid rtogs na dbang yin te //
NK010(tha)012:24: thams cad rang rig phur bu yin //
NK010(tha)012:26: de bas na go 'phang gang la bkri ba po
NK010(tha)012:27: yang yongs grub chen po'i bskyed rim la goms pa'i
NK010(tha)012:28: rdo rje slob dpon ni mchog yin la /
NK010(tha)012:29: min na'ang gzhi'i bsnyen pa sngon du song nas gzhan
NK010(tha)012:30: rgyud smin grol gyi nus pa thob cing cho ga'i
NK010(tha)012:31: bya ba la mkhas pa dag gis slob ma rjes
NK010(tha)012:33: de la dbang bzhi po gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor yang bshad rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:34: rdul tshon lus dang byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)012:35: de bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK010(tha)012:36: brten nas dbang rnams yang dag bskur //
NK010(tha)012:37: bum pa gsang ba shes rab dbang //
NK010(tha)012:38: bzhi pa mchog gi dbang chen yin //
NK010(tha)012:40: dang po rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la sta gon dang /
NK010(tha)012:44: slob dpon sta gon gnas pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:45: slob ma lha dang bum pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:46: sta gon gnas pa shes par bya //
NK010(tha)012:48: dang po slob dpon sta gon ni bsnyen pa zhal gso ba nyid yin te /
NK010(tha)012:50: rdo rje rigs kyi srog la yang //
NK010(tha)012:51: 'bum phrag gcig tu nges bzlas pas //
NK010(tha)012:53: gnyis pa lha sta gon gyi sngon du 'gro ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:54: lha yi lung ni bstan pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:55: sa brtag dkyil 'khor drag por sbyangs //
NK010(tha)012:56: rdo rje rigs kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK010(tha)012:57: gru gsum gru bzhi mthing nag ldan //
NK010(tha)012:58: ma tram bsgral zhing bdud rtsi lnga //
NK010(tha)012:59: dur khrod rdzas kyis byug par bya //
NK010(tha)012:62: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NK010(tha)012:63: sa brtag sa bzung byin gyis brlab //
NK010(tha)012:64: dang po brtag pa'i gnas chen der //
NK010(tha)012:65: sngags mkhan bya ba kun byas te //
NK010(tha)012:66: sta gon gnas pa'i bya ba byas //
NK010(tha)012:67: zhes pas sngar ma sbyangs shing ma dul ba'i gnas
NK010(tha)012:68: su ni rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs nas brtag
NK010(tha)012:72: bsrung ba ste lnga'i rim pa las /
NK010(tha)012:74: dang po mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:76: klu yi mig dang 'byung po'i srang //
NK010(tha)012:77: sa yi bgegs dang ma rungs sa //
NK010(tha)012:78: mi shis pa yi sa min par //
NK010(tha)012:79: las kyi bya ba gzhung bsham la //
NK010(tha)012:80: bkra shis don gyi gnas yin pas //
NK010(tha)012:82: me tog gling dang rin chen ri //
NK010(tha)012:83: dpag bsam shing dang skad snyan bya //
NK010(tha)012:84: 'bru sna tshogs dang gnas sa legs //
NK010(tha)012:85: dbyibs legs lung pa ran pa ru //
NK010(tha)012:86: bkra shis gzhung bzang gnas yin pas //
NK010(tha)012:87: gnas kyi dam pa yin zhes bshad //
NK010(tha)012:88: drag po'i las su bya ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:89: dang po phur pa bsgrub pa'i gnas //
NK010(tha)012:90: nags ri tsher ma can gyi shing //
NK010(tha)012:91: gcan gzan gdug pa sna tshogs yod //
NK010(tha)012:92: gnam ni gri mda' ral gri'i shul //
NK010(tha)012:93: sa ni gru gsum me dpung 'dra //
NK010(tha)012:94: logs la dur khrod yod pa ru //
NK010(tha)012:95: mkhas pas brtags te btsal byas na //
NK010(tha)012:96: 'di ni phur bu bsgrub gnas yin //
NK010(tha)012:100: dbyibs 'dra'i sa gzhi rab tu brtag /
NK010(tha)012:101: ri bo chen po rab dben par //
NK010(tha)012:102: yid 'ong me tog brgyan pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:103: yang na sdong gcig me reg pa //
NK010(tha)012:104: lung gsum mdo dang dur khrod gnas //
NK010(tha)012:105: 'bab chu chen po'i ngos su bsgrub //
NK010(tha)012:107: sdong gcig me reg pa ni shing grib gcig gis
NK010(tha)012:108: gcig la me reg pa yin par rgyud las bshad
NK010(tha)012:109: yod do // gnyis pa pra brtag pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:111: nyi ma rim par 'gro ba bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:112: lto 'phye'i gzhung du brtags nas su //
NK010(tha)012:114: de nas pus gang tsam du brko //
NK010(tha)012:115: sa yi ro lnga bsal byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:116: sa de nyid kyis dgang bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:117: khengs nas lhag na dngos grub rab //
NK010(tha)012:118: kha da chad na dngos grub 'bring //
NK010(tha)012:119: ma khengs gyur nas gzhan du spo //
NK010(tha)012:120: zhes pa ltar lto 'phye brtags te brkos pa'i ro lnga bsal ba'i shul phyur bur khengs na bzang /
NK010(tha)012:121: ma khengs na ngan pas sbyin bsreg la sogs bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:122: gnyis pa blang ba la'ang gnyis te rgyud de las /
NK010(tha)012:123: yul lam sa de'i bdag po la //
NK010(tha)012:124: bden pas bkrol la sa rin bcal //
NK010(tha)012:126: gzugs can gyi bdag gir byas na rin gyis barngana no //
NK010(tha)012:127: gnyis pa mi snang ba la blang ba'i tshul /
NK010(tha)012:129: phyi yi gtor ma btang nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:130: zhes pas cha gsum dang sa lha la man+dala zlum
NK010(tha)012:131: po ba byung dang dri yis byugs pa la me
NK010(tha)012:133: chu gcig dang bcas pa'i phyi mchod lnga dang gtor ma gsum bsham /
NK010(tha)012:134: skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed nas rdo rje khros pa'i nga rgyal bsgom ste /
NK010(tha)012:135: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du pam las
NK010(tha)012:136: sa'i lha mo gser btso ma'i mdog can bum pa
NK010(tha)012:138: +amo pri th+ai d+he wi sa ma ya dzahdzah zhes
NK010(tha)012:139: brjod pas sa'i lha mo klu gnyan sa bdag gis
NK010(tha)012:143: rang sngags la ar+g+ham push+pe la sogs btags pas nyer spyod dang /
NK010(tha)012:144: a k+aa ros gtor ma bsngo /
NK010(tha)012:145: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)012:146: spyod pa'i tshul dang khyad par dang //
NK010(tha)012:147: sa dang pha rol phyin rnams la //
NK010(tha)012:148: lha mo khyod ni dbang du gyur //
NK010(tha)012:149: sh+aakya seng ge skyob pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:150: ji ltar bdud kyi sde bcom pa //
NK010(tha)012:151: de bzhin bdag gis bdud sde las //
NK010(tha)012:152: rgyal bar byas te dkyil 'khor bri //
NK010(tha)012:153: de phyir sa 'di gnang bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:156: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod ci dga' bar longs spyod cig /
NK010(tha)012:157: ces gnang ba byin par bsam la gtor ma dang po 'bul /
NK010(tha)012:158: sa'i lha mo badz+ra mus gshegs gsol bya /
NK010(tha)012:159: gtor ma gnyis pa gzhi bdag dkar phyogs pa la a k+aa ros bsngosa nas /
NK010(tha)012:160: gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu //
NK010(tha)012:161: gnod sbyin srin po gzhan dag la //
NK010(tha)012:162: sa 'di bdag gis blang bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:163: dkyil 'khor don du stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:164: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)012:166: gsum pa nag phyogs pa la byin nas /
NK010(tha)012:169: gtor ma byin pa 'di long la //
NK010(tha)012:170: ma grub bar du gzhan du dengs //
NK010(tha)012:171: h'u bzhi'i sngags dang gu gul gyis bskrad /
NK010(tha)012:173: lag pa g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga phral ba rdo
NK010(tha)012:174: rje rtse lnga par bsam ba shar dang byang cung
NK010(tha)012:175: zad gzhol ba'i steng gi khor yug du bskor zhing
NK010(tha)012:177: +amo ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:178: ces brjod cing rdo rje las phyung ba'i 'od zer gyis snod bcud du 'dzin pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)012:180: zhes brjod pas sa phyogs thams cad nam mkha'i rang bzhin du gyur par bsgom /
NK010(tha)012:182: rang nyid rdo rje gzhon nu'i nga rgyal la gnas
NK010(tha)012:183: pa'i mig gnyis nyi zla mig 'bras h'u las ye
NK010(tha)012:185: bgegs dang log par 'dren pa'i tshogs la gzir bas
NK010(tha)012:186: rnam smin gyi lus bsregs shing sems chos nyid kyi
NK010(tha)012:187: ngang du gsos par bsam la /
NK010(tha)012:188: rkang pa rdo rje'i 'gros kyis bskor zhing /
NK010(tha)012:189: +amo s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra dz+wa la dz+wa la h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:191: spro na lha'i rnal 'byor dang ma bral bas chas su zhugs te /
NK010(tha)012:192: rkang pa byin gyis brlabs nas gar gyi gzhi bca' ba sngon du btang ste /
NK010(tha)012:193: khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs dang phyag rgya sgrub thabs
NK010(tha)012:194: na yod pa bzhin bya ba'i gnas dngos bstan 'dir
NK010(tha)012:196: rdo rje stabs dang rdo rje rol pa'i gar //
NK010(tha)012:197: rdo rje lta bas kun bltas te //
NK010(tha)012:198: bar chad bgegs bskrad dkyil 'khor bsrung //
NK010(tha)012:201: rgya gram gyi phyag rgya bstan la /
NK010(tha)012:202: me di ni badz+ra b+han+d+ha h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:203: ces brjod pas snang ba thams cad rdo rje'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK010(tha)012:204: +amo badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata kyis bsrung bar bya zhing /
NK010(tha)012:205: shis brjod dang smon lam kyang bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:206: de yang sgrub pa chen po dang 'brel na bshad rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:207: bsrung ba'i rim pa yang dag bya //
NK010(tha)012:208: dam sri bsgral dang ma tram bsgyel //
NK010(tha)012:209: sgo la rim dang de bzhin sbyar //
NK010(tha)012:210: zhes pa ltar phyi rol gom pa bdun cu rtsa bzhi'i sar rgyal tho gzug cing /
NK010(tha)012:211: phyogs bzhi'i rgyal po rnams rang gi thugs ka'i 'od
NK010(tha)012:212: zer dang lhan cig pa'i badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan
NK010(tha)012:214: +amo d+h+ri ta rash+ta ya h'u dzah zhes bzla /
NK010(tha)012:215: rang sngags de la ar+g+ham sogs gdags nas nyer spyod dang /
NK010(tha)012:216: a k+aa ros gtor ma phul /
NK010(tha)012:217: mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)012:218: sogs kyis phrin las bcol bas dri za'i gdon bsrung ba'i las mdzad par bsam /
NK010(tha)012:219: tish+tha badz+ra sa brtan par bya /
NK010(tha)012:220: phyogs gzhan gsum po la'ang des 'gre zhing rang sngags
NK010(tha)012:221: ni lho phyogs pa la bi ru d+ha ka h'u
NK010(tha)012:222: dzah nub phyogs pa la bi ru pak+sha ya h'u
NK010(tha)012:223: dzah byang phyogs pa la +amo bee sh+ra ba na
NK010(tha)012:224: h'u dzah zhes bsgyur zhing rim par grul bum dang
NK010(tha)012:226: gnod sbyin gyi gdon mtshams gcod par 'don pa bsgyur /
NK010(tha)012:227: de nas bar mtshams dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:228: r+au pa bya mgo can gyi snying gar /
NK010(tha)012:229: ya ma dam sri gam pa ri m+aa ra ya dzah zhes bris pa brub khung du bkod /
NK010(tha)012:231: bden bdar dgug gzhug byas nas /
NK010(tha)012:232: de'i snying gar phur pa gdab cing /
NK010(tha)012:233: +aar+ya a tsa la dam sri b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha m+aa ra ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:236: thod pa mtshan ngan du bcug ste sgrub khang gi them pa'i phyi rol du mnan /
NK010(tha)012:237: ro g.yam rgya gram bris pas mnan /
NK010(tha)012:239: de'i steng du dpon slob rnams lag pa lu gu
NK010(tha)012:240: rgyud du sbrel nas sum b+ha ni bzla bzhin par
NK010(tha)012:241: bro brdung / de nas sgo byang gdags pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:242: ro ras sam ra sog la gshed po'i sku sngags
NK010(tha)012:243: byang dang bcas pa bris pa sgo ya them phye
NK010(tha)012:244: mar gdags / badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK010(tha)012:246: ar+g+ham la sogs pas mchod cing gtor ma bsngo /
NK010(tha)012:248: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po kun //
NK010(tha)012:249: khyod kyi 'khor dang g.yog lags na //
NK010(tha)012:250: rnam par smin pa'i chos shod la //
NK010(tha)012:251: bdag gi 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK010(tha)012:252: sgo 'di tshun chad ma btang zhig /
NK010(tha)012:254: de rjes gsang mtshams dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:256: rtag bdag zhe sdang las 'khrul pa //
NK010(tha)012:258: sngon yang bskal pa re re la //
NK010(tha)012:259: bar gcod srin por gyur pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:260: 'di ma btul na sems can dag /
NK010(tha)012:261: thams cad ma lus dmyal bar 'gro //
NK010(tha)012:262: zhes pas rgyud kyi gleng gzhi dang rjes su mthun
NK010(tha)012:263: par bsgral ba'i tshul ma tram gyi gzugs byas pa
NK010(tha)012:265: rkang pa byang shar du bstan pa gan rkyal du bzhag /
NK010(tha)012:266: yi dam gyi nga rgyal la gnas pas lcags kyu'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK010(tha)012:268: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:269: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:270: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:271: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)012:272: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku sprul pa //
NK010(tha)012:273: rig 'dzin nges pa mang po la //
NK010(tha)012:274: dngos grub 'phrog par byed pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:275: r+au tra rtag pa'i rgyal po 'di //
NK010(tha)012:276: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)012:277: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK010(tha)012:278: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar gyis //
NK010(tha)012:279: ma tram ka ru tra dzah dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK010(tha)012:280: tshogs rnams kyi bden pas dngos grub la bar du
NK010(tha)012:281: gcod pa'i bdud dang log 'dren thams cad +aa kar+sha
NK010(tha)012:282: ya dzah tri yam dzah dzahmh'u bam hohs bstim /
NK010(tha)012:284: snying rjes khyod bsgral dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)012:285: bsad mnan bya ba ma yin te //
NK010(tha)012:286: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas la //
NK010(tha)012:287: rnam par shes pa mya ngan 'da' //
NK010(tha)012:289: chos la blta dang gang zag blta //
NK010(tha)012:290: rtag chad blta ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK010(tha)012:291: bdag med stong pa'i tho bas gzhom //
NK010(tha)012:292: 'jigs byed chen po'i zhabs kyis mnan //
NK010(tha)012:293: ma rig sgo lnga'i sbubs las dral //
NK010(tha)012:294: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su phata //
NK010(tha)012:295: ces rtse gsum gyi phyag rgya snying gar bsnun pas
NK010(tha)012:296: gzugs phung hrul gyis zhig pa'i khog pa bros sbyang
NK010(tha)012:298: dur khrod bdag po ma tram ni //
NK010(tha)012:299: bardzisa pa'i stabs kyis mnan par bya //
NK010(tha)012:303: stong gsum stong gi lo ki na //
NK010(tha)012:304: dbus phyogs stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK010(tha)012:305: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng nas //
NK010(tha)012:306: rdo rje khrag 'thung bro rar chas //
NK010(tha)012:307: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mthing nag sku //
NK010(tha)012:308: rdo rje dbyings phyug yum la 'khyud //
NK010(tha)012:309: rdo rje thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK010(tha)012:310: dur khrod chas kyis lha srin 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:311: rdo rje gshog pa bar snang brgyangs //
NK010(tha)012:312: spyan gsum dmar zlum stong gsum bsreg /
NK010(tha)012:313: mche ba gtsigs pas bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:314: ljags dmar glog stong 'khyug pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:315: stong gsum ma lus gsal bar byed //
NK010(tha)012:316: h'u gi sgra ni 'brug bzhin sgrogs //
NK010(tha)012:317: brkyang bskum zhabs gnyis bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:318: bdud ni phye mar 'thag pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:319: klu ni yongs su rngod pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:320: bgegs rnams mer ni bsreg pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:321: ma bdud thal bar rlog pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:322: dur khrod 'di ru bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:323: dam nyams gshed ni brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:324: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK010(tha)012:325: phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:326: bar chad bgegs ni sbyang bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:327: khro bcu rdo rje 'gros kyis blangs //
NK010(tha)012:328: drag po bya ba'i 'gros kyis blangs //
NK010(tha)012:329: bdud kyi sgo la 'jug thag bcad //
NK010(tha)012:330: sa yi rten phur 'og tu dgod //
NK010(tha)012:331: rdo rje rgya gram thag pas drags //
NK010(tha)012:332: dkyil 'khor stan du r+au tra bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:333: dur khrod gzhal yas khang du bzung //
NK010(tha)012:334: sgrub pa byed pa'i rdzas su bzung //
NK010(tha)012:335: thugs dam bskang ba'i bdud rtsir bzung //
NK010(tha)012:336: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK010(tha)012:341: ces brjod la yan lag lnga so so dang /
NK010(tha)012:344: mtshan ma brgyad dkyil 'khor phyogs mtshams brgyad du bkod /
NK010(tha)012:345: bdag gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phros khog pa la
NK010(tha)012:346: thim pas dur khrod rol pa'i gzhal yas khang gi
NK010(tha)012:347: mtha' bskor bar gyur par bsam zhing /
NK010(tha)012:348: khu tshur dpung mgor bsnol ba dbye ba dang bcas /
NK010(tha)012:349: h'u pra we sha ya phata /
NK010(tha)012:350: ces lan bdun gyis sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo dbye /
NK010(tha)012:354: ces rdo rje'i gar 'gros kyis lan gsum bskor nas dkyil 'khor gyi nang du tshud par bsgom mo //
NK010(tha)012:355: de dag ni gzhung dus bcad pa'i rim pa nye bar bsdus pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:356: spyi tsam du sa'i cho ga'i rim pa ji ltar smos pa bzhin du ma grub pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:357: gal te slob dpon nus ldan gyis dkyil 'khor gyi
NK010(tha)012:358: khang pa nyid du sngon nas rung bar byas pa
NK010(tha)012:359: yin kyang mi mngon pa la blang ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:361: gzung ba rnams bya ba legs shing /
NK010(tha)012:362: ras bris la brten tshe sa gzung ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:364: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba'i gzhi la bdud rtsi lnga byug cing /
NK010(tha)012:365: badz+ra a mri ta man+da la h'u /
NK010(tha)012:369: kam ka p+aa la man+da la h'u /
NK010(tha)012:372: ba yi rnam lnga rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:373: lha yi gnas su me tog ni //
NK010(tha)012:374: tshom bu sngon po lha grangs dgod //
NK010(tha)012:375: bdud rtsi lnga yi thig le dgod //
NK010(tha)012:376: ces pas dbus nas bzung ste lha gnas so sor
NK010(tha)012:377: bdud rtsi lnga'i thig le btab pa la ba byung
NK010(tha)012:378: gis sbags pa'i me tog sngon po'i tshom bu lha
NK010(tha)012:379: grangs dang mnyam pa dgod bzhin par /
NK010(tha)012:380: +amo na mahs man+ta man+da la h'u /
NK010(tha)012:383: phun sum tshogs pa lnga ldan pas //
NK010(tha)012:384: dkyil 'khor lha la gsol ba gdab //
NK010(tha)012:386: cho ga bzhin du mngon dkyil nus na rab /
NK010(tha)012:387: ma nus na lha gnas so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK010(tha)012:388: lha tshogs rtsa sngags tsam la brten nas mos pas
NK010(tha)012:389: bskyed la bdun rnam dag 'bul ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:390: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK010(tha)012:392: rang gi lce h'u las skyes pa'i rdo rje'i rang bzhin tu gyur /
NK010(tha)012:393: rdo rje gzhon nu'i lha tshogs rnams //
NK010(tha)012:394: bdag la gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)012:395: rgyal ba mchod dang gzhan don du //
NK010(tha)012:397: gnang zhing rjes su bstan par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:398: khyed rnams la ni mchod byed dang //
NK010(tha)012:399: slob ma rjes su gzung ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:401: sta gon la ni gnas par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:403: dz+ny+aa na dza ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:406: b+h+r+aum ba ti ka ra sid+d+hi h'u /
NK010(tha)012:407: a mri ta a we sha ya a +aa /
NK010(tha)012:410: pany+tsa li ka +aa we sha ya +aa /
NK010(tha)012:411: kalpo prik+sha h'u +aah zhes lan gsum brjod la sta
NK010(tha)012:412: gon gyi ye shes pa rnams rdo rje khu tshur
NK010(tha)012:416: gsum pa bum pa sta gon ni /
NK010(tha)012:417: bum pa mthing shun sngon po'i mdog /
NK010(tha)012:418: bsangs shing dur khrod ras kyis dkri //
NK010(tha)012:419: ljon shing bzang pos kha brgyan zhing //
NK010(tha)012:420: bdud rtsi lnga yis bum pa dgang //
NK010(tha)012:421: dbang dang bdud sel gegs bsal ba'i //
NK010(tha)012:422: bum pa gsum du yang dag nges //
NK010(tha)012:424: sman lnga 'bru lnga rin chen lnga //
NK010(tha)012:425: spos dang snying po lnga dag dang //
NK010(tha)012:426: kha rgyan mgul rgyan de bzhin bsham //
NK010(tha)012:427: zhes pas mtshan nyid spyi dang bye brag pa tshang
NK010(tha)012:428: ba'i bum pa gsum rgyun 'babs kyi chus sum gnyis
NK010(tha)012:429: bkang la bcud rdzas nyer lnga'i steng du bdud rtsi
NK010(tha)012:430: lnga bsnan pa'i sum cu pa btab /
NK010(tha)012:431: rgya shug dkar po'i kha rgyan dang bcas stegs la bkod /
NK010(tha)012:432: bum pa'i nang du lha tshogs bskyed pa la dmigs nas bzlas pa bya ste /
NK010(tha)012:433: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rigs kyi lha //
NK010(tha)012:434: ye shes khro bo thugs bskul sngags //
NK010(tha)012:435: lha yi sngags rnams rab tu bzlas //
NK010(tha)012:436: khri dang stong gis dngos grub 'byung //
NK010(tha)012:439: yab dang yum dang shes rab thabs //
NK010(tha)012:440: bum pa'i nang du byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)012:441: ye shes bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun dbab //
NK010(tha)012:442: ces pa ltar las mthar bum pa'i lha 'od zhu bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:443: bzhi pa slob ma sta gon ni /
NK010(tha)012:446: man+dala phul te 'dug nas bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:448: ye shes lnga ldan bla ma rdo rje 'dzin //
NK010(tha)012:449: rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)012:450: khrag 'thung khro bo khro mos byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)012:451: bdag gi lus kyis srog gcod ma byin blangs //
NK010(tha)012:452: mi tshangs spyad cing ting 'dzin sku ma gsal //
NK010(tha)012:453: sku yi dam tshigs nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)012:454: bdag gi ngag gis rdzun dang phra ma dang //
NK010(tha)012:455: ngag 'khyal tshig rtsub bzlas brjod grangs ma skyol //
NK010(tha)012:456: rdo rje bzlas pa'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)012:457: gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)012:458: bdag gis snod ldan sems can thams cad la //
NK010(tha)012:459: brnab sems gnod sems log lta skyes pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:460: chos nyid zab mo'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)012:461: lta ba thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa bshags //
NK010(tha)012:462: sems can thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK010(tha)012:463: ma rtogs bdag gis barngana dang skyon du bgrangs //
NK010(tha)012:464: sangs rgyas yon tan mtha' yas ma brjod cing //
NK010(tha)012:465: yon tan dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)012:466: sangs rgyas phrin las sna tshogs dpag med kyi //
NK010(tha)012:467: snying rje chen pos sems can don ma byas //
NK010(tha)012:468: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod ma nus shing //
NK010(tha)012:469: phrin las dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)012:470: skye ba rnam bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)012:471: chos sku rnam dag dbyings las gzugs skur snang //
NK010(tha)012:472: bde ba chen po'i kun la khyab dmigs te //
NK010(tha)012:473: yang dag don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)012:475: zhes snying thag pa nas bshags su bcug ste rgyud dag par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:476: de nas sdom pa bzung ba'i gsol gdab ni /
NK010(tha)012:477: skye rga na dang 'chi ba yi //
NK010(tha)012:478: chu srin pir thogs 'jigs byed las //
NK010(tha)012:479: gdon par nus pa khyod 'ba' zhig /
NK010(tha)012:480: dga' chen khyod bdag ston par bas //
NK010(tha)012:481: mgon po chen po bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)012:482: byang chub chen po'i tshul ston pa //
NK010(tha)012:483: dam tshig de nyid bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)012:484: byang chub sems kyang bdag la rtsol //
NK010(tha)012:485: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK010(tha)012:486: skyabs gsum dag kyang bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)012:487: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK010(tha)012:488: mgon po chen pos gzung du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:490: sdom pa bzung ba dngos ni /
NK010(tha)012:491: zhe sdang yongs su dag pa'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:492: so sor thar pa dang por byin //
NK010(tha)012:493: de nas byang chub sdom chen byin //
NK010(tha)012:494: de nas dbu ma'i chos rnams bshad //
NK010(tha)012:495: mthar ni 'bras bu theg chen gyi //
NK010(tha)012:497: ces sdom gsum rim par bzung ba'ang yod de /
NK010(tha)012:498: 'dir rtsa rgyud kyi rjes su 'brangs nas theg chen
NK010(tha)012:499: gyi rigs la nus pa sad par bya phyir smon
NK010(tha)012:500: 'jug spyi dang bye brag pa stabs gcig tu blang
NK010(tha)012:501: ba tsam sngags rang sa'i grub mthar nges shing dgag
NK010(tha)012:502: bya chung bas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK010(tha)012:503: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin sogs dang //
NK010(tha)012:504: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)012:506: chos sku mkha' 'dra gzugs sku 'ja' ltar snang //
NK010(tha)012:507: gsang sngags sgra snyan lta bur sgra bsgrags shing //
NK010(tha)012:508: khro bo khro mo'i tshul gyis gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:509: bla med dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)012:511: bdag gis byang chub sems mchog ni //
NK010(tha)012:512: ma lus pa ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:513: ngan song gsum las ma grol ba //
NK010(tha)012:514: lha mi gnyis su dgrol bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:515: ma bsgral pa yi lha mi rnams //
NK010(tha)012:516: byang chub sa la bsgral bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:517: dbugs ma phyung ba'i byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)012:518: sa brgyad pa la dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK010(tha)012:519: sems can mya ngan 'das pa'i mtha' //
NK010(tha)012:520: rdo rje 'chang la rab tu dgod //
NK010(tha)012:522: lan gsum gyis brtan par gzung ngo //
NK010(tha)012:523: de ltar byang sa'i thun mong pa'i steng du tha
NK010(tha)012:524: mal gyi snang zhen ldog pa'i nyes spyod sdom pa
NK010(tha)012:525: / 'khrul snang ye shes su sdud pa'i dge ba chos sdud /
NK010(tha)012:526: las bzhi'i phrin las kyi sgo nas sems can don
NK010(tha)012:527: byed de byang sdom bye brag pa'am de las 'da'
NK010(tha)012:528: par bya ba ma yin pa'i cha nas dam tshig
NK010(tha)012:529: tu btags pa'i gnas rnams bzung ngo snyam pas 'di'i
NK010(tha)012:531: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK010(tha)012:532: 'gro ba rigs drug sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)012:533: dug lnga nyon mongs tshar gcad phyir //
NK010(tha)012:534: rigs lnga khrag 'thung nyid du brjod //
NK010(tha)012:536: rtog 'joms ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:537: ye nas skye med chos sku la //
NK010(tha)012:538: snang ba 'khrul pa snying re rje //
NK010(tha)012:540: thams cad rdo rje'i rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:541: cis kyang mi cod mi shigs zhing //
NK010(tha)012:542: skye 'gag med pa rdo rje'i ngang //
NK010(tha)012:543: de bzhin nyid du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:545: dbyings la ngo bo ma grub kyang //
NK010(tha)012:546: snang ba tsam du khrag 'thung sku //
NK010(tha)012:547: dug lnga rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:548: rigs lnga'i khro bo rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:550: rigs lnga khro bor bsgrub pa la //
NK010(tha)012:551: snying rje sems can la bskyed nas //
NK010(tha)012:552: thar par 'dod pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:553: dam tshig lnga po gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:555: thams cad mkhyen pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)012:556: rigs lnga 'dus pa'i khro rgyal gtso //
NK010(tha)012:557: rdo rje gzhon du khros pa'i dpal //
NK010(tha)012:558: skal ldan rnams kyis thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:559: ces lan gsum gyis thob par nges shes bskyed do //
NK010(tha)012:560: de nas slob ma'i skye mched lha'i phyag rgyar byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:561: gnas so sor rdo rje dang bcas pa'i dri'i thig les reg cing //
NK010(tha)012:562: gtsug tor sangs rgyas khrag 'thung dpal //
NK010(tha)012:564: lag g.yas rdo rje khrag 'thung dpal //
NK010(tha)012:566: lag g.yon rin chen khrag 'thung dpal //
NK010(tha)012:568: rkang g.yas las kyi khrag 'thung dpal //
NK010(tha)012:571: thugs ka gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK010(tha)012:573: mthong bas rigs lnga khrag 'thung sku //
NK010(tha)012:574: bshags pas lus ngag dag par byed //
NK010(tha)012:577: rgyud las bsrung ba so shing skyor ba'i chu //
NK010(tha)012:578: ku sha'i sngas stan steng du ni //
NK010(tha)012:579: dur khrod zhing lpags steng nyal mi lam brtag /
NK010(tha)012:581: h'u las skyed pa'i srad bu dmar po slob bu'i
NK010(tha)012:582: lus tshad dang mnyam pa gsum lta ba la rdo
NK010(tha)012:583: rje'i mdud pa gsum du byas pa las chus bsangs
NK010(tha)012:584: shing 'khyil pa'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK010(tha)012:585: khu rdul gnyis kyi cha'i bar chad bsrung phyir skyes pa'i dpung pa g.yon dang /
NK010(tha)012:586: bud med kyi g.yas su bcings shing 'khyil pa'i sngags dang /
NK010(tha)012:587: sarba bud+d+ha mee tri rak+sha rak+sha sarbam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)012:588: zhes bzla bzhin par phyi nang gi bar chad bsrung phyir nyis rim du bcings /
NK010(tha)012:589: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i dri chus mdud pa la
NK010(tha)012:590: rgya gram du reg pas lus rdo rje'i go chas
NK010(tha)012:591: zhu lugs su g.yogs par bsgom zhing /
NK010(tha)012:592: lus kyi nyes pa dag pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:593: bsrung dang sta gon gnas par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:596: de nas so shing gi rtsa ba phur bu'i rnam
NK010(tha)012:597: pa can la rtse mor me tog gi phreng ba
NK010(tha)012:598: bcings pa bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i sngags kyis byin gyis
NK010(tha)012:600: dgos pa ni phur pa 'jig rten snang byed las /
NK010(tha)012:601: ngag gi nyes pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:602: so shing byin la so rtsa brud //
NK010(tha)012:603: phrin las bzhi yi dngos grub brtag /
NK010(tha)012:605: khru gang gru bzhi pa'i man+dala pad 'dab brgyad pa
NK010(tha)012:606: mu khyud kyi ra ba can la dri bzang dang
NK010(tha)012:607: ba byung gis sbags pa'i tshom bu bkod pa'i steng
NK010(tha)012:608: du mkha' dbyings kyi rgyas bzung nas dngos grub kyi
NK010(tha)012:609: ltas brtag pa'i 'dun pa rtse gcig pas dor du
NK010(tha)012:611: ngag gi nyes pa bsal ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:612: dbang gi lha rnams bstan du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:613: +aa dzim sham pa ti na h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:615: rigs lnga'i dngos grub phyogs bzhi dbus //
NK010(tha)012:616: mtshams phran steng mkha' 'og sa spyod //
NK010(tha)012:617: rtsa ba rang bstan lan gsum bskyar //
NK010(tha)012:618: g.yas yo tshe thar g.yon yo sbyin //
NK010(tha)012:619: phred bsags mar me brgya rtsa sbar //
NK010(tha)012:620: kun ngan bsags sbyang rgya cher bya //
NK010(tha)012:622: dung zhal gyi chu bam las bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur pa 'bru gsum gyi byin gyis brlab /
NK010(tha)012:623: slob bu'i lag pa g.yas su lan gsum sbyin /
NK010(tha)012:624: cung zad btung ba'i lhag ma dpung pa g.yon steng
NK010(tha)012:625: nas rgyab tu dor bas sgo gsum gyi dri ma
NK010(tha)012:626: bag chags dang bcas pa dag pa'i mos pa gyis
NK010(tha)012:629: +amo h+r+ai bi shud d+he sarba hi ni h'u phata
NK010(tha)012:630: p+aa pam do sha ya sarba bi na ya h'u
NK010(tha)012:631: phata / blud pas yid kyi sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)012:632: sta gon la ni gnas par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:635: chun po che ba h'u dang chung ba d+hi las
NK010(tha)012:636: byung ba'i ku sha sngon po rtsa rtse ma nyams
NK010(tha)012:637: la rmi lam mi 'khrugs pa'i nus pa can du
NK010(tha)012:638: gyur pa che ba stan gyi don du slob dpon
NK010(tha)012:640: chung ba sngas kyi don du g.yas par bzung ba bsnol nas gtod cing /
NK010(tha)012:646: do nub bla ma dang dkyil 'khor la mos pa
NK010(tha)012:647: rtse gcig pas sngas byang du bstan la seng ge'i
NK010(tha)012:648: nyal stabs kyis bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i sngags bzla bzhin
NK010(tha)012:649: par nyol la nang par rmi lam gang yin pa
NK010(tha)012:653: gsang sngags zab mo'i dbang mchog 'bras bu la //
NK010(tha)012:654: las 'phro skal bar ldan dang mi ldan pa //
NK010(tha)012:655: lus bkru gos gtsang gyon la nyal bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:656: gsang sngags zab mo'i dbang mchog thob mi thob //
NK010(tha)012:657: rdo rje slob dpon phyag cha gnang zhing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:658: thugs kyi dngos grub thob pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:659: lag tu b+han+d+ha thogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:660: kun gyi dmag dpon byed cing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:661: sku la rgyan cha 'dogs shing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:662: sku yi dngos grub thob pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:663: gser g.yu lus la btags pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:664: gzhan yang zangs lcags rin po che //
NK010(tha)012:665: bdag ni rtags tu 'chang zhing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:666: yon tan dngos grub thob pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:667: lag tu pad+ma me tog thogs //
NK010(tha)012:668: nyi dro zla gsal me mthong ba //
NK010(tha)012:669: rgya mtsho chen po brgal zhing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:670: bdag gi lus kyang bshas nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:671: sha khrag mi yis zos shing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:672: gsung gi dngos grub thob pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:673: mda' gzhu go mtshon thogs pa ngang //
NK010(tha)012:674: rtsi shing mang po bsums pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:675: nam mkha' la ni 'phur zhing rmi //
NK010(tha)012:676: phrin las dngos grub thob pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:678: de la mtshan mo thun bzhir bcad //
NK010(tha)012:680: tho rengs bden pas rig pas brtag /
NK010(tha)012:681: zhes gsungs pa ltar brtag go //
NK010(tha)012:682: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis /
NK010(tha)012:687: dkyil 'khor skyang nul thig gdab la //
NK010(tha)012:688: srad bu lnga dang ldan pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:689: thig ni rab tu gdab pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:691: sngar lha sta gon byas pa'i gzhi la rak+ta dang
NK010(tha)012:692: bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pas khyem med par byug
NK010(tha)012:693: cing skyang nul legs par byas pa la thig gi
NK010(tha)012:694: bya ba bsgrub pa yin te /
NK010(tha)012:696: khams gsum srid gsum dbang du sdud pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:697: rak+ta chags pa'i dbang gis chag chag gdab //
NK010(tha)012:698: srid gsum ye nas ye shes chen po lnga //
NK010(tha)012:699: gti mug stsogs pa'i dug lnga gnas gzhom phyir //
NK010(tha)012:700: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga yis chag chag gdab //
NK010(tha)012:701: rin chen sna lnga'i kha dog tshon rnams ni //
NK010(tha)012:702: 'bru lngas byin gyis brlab cing bri bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:703: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med las //
NK010(tha)012:704: byang chub sems kyi thig gdab bo //
NK010(tha)012:706: de la thig ni dpa' bo'i rin gyis nyos pa'i ras bal gyi skud pa lnga tshan lnga pa'am /
NK010(tha)012:708: gtsang ma'i spu dang a shwata shun //
NK010(tha)012:709: zhes pas gzhon nu mas bkal ba'i srad bu tshon
NK010(tha)012:710: sna lnga pa srid du dkyil 'khor gyi nyis 'gyur
NK010(tha)012:711: la sbom phra sgo'i nyi shu char byas pa slob
NK010(tha)012:712: dpon dang gzungs ma gtso bo yab yum gyi nga
NK010(tha)012:714: thig skud mi dmigs pa'i ngang nas rigs lnga yab
NK010(tha)012:715: yum gyi ngo bor gyur pa yab kyi skur bsdus
NK010(tha)012:716: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du zhu ba yum
NK010(tha)012:718: dzahdzahdzah zhes yab yum so so'i rlung gi 'gro ldog dang mthun par yum la gtad /
NK010(tha)012:719: rten 'brel snying pos rab tu gnas /
NK010(tha)012:720: slob dpon shar dang gzungs ma nub tu phyogs pas /
NK010(tha)012:721: b+h+r+aum dz+ny+aa na ma d+ha la h'u /
NK010(tha)012:722: zhes lan gsum brjod cing lte ba'i thad kyi bar snang la g.yas pa'i mtheb mdzub kyis bzung /
NK010(tha)012:723: g.yon pas thig skud brkyang zhing se gol gtogs pa
NK010(tha)012:724: dang bcas ye shes kyi thig tshang thig gnyis tsam
NK010(tha)012:727: bcu drug pa sogs thig skor ma nor bar gdab cing /
NK010(tha)012:728: thig gi sgra las bri bya'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha'
NK010(tha)012:729: la bkra lam gyis gsal ba la mchod bstod kyang
NK010(tha)012:732: thig skud ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK010(tha)012:733: lte bar khu tshur g.yon gyis bzung //
NK010(tha)012:734: las kun byed pas bzung nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:735: nam mkhar btab pas rang bzhin dang //
NK010(tha)012:737: gzugs brnyan gsal phyir sa thig gdab //
NK010(tha)012:739: de nas thig gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:741: lha dang gnyis med gnas pa'i thig /
NK010(tha)012:742: mchod byas ye shes thig ni gdab //
NK010(tha)012:743: gnyis pas gzugs brnyan thig gdab bo //
NK010(tha)012:745: thig skud zur pa yod na dang /
NK010(tha)012:746: med na de'i ye shes pa badz+ra mus gshegs pa
NK010(tha)012:747: la thig skud gnyis pa'i tha snyad btags pa'i las
NK010(tha)012:748: thig de nyid bdud rtsi lnga dang dkar chal gyis
NK010(tha)012:749: sbags / thig chen brgyad nas brtsams te rim par gdab tshul rdo rje 'bar ba las /
NK010(tha)012:750: shar nas nub la lho nas byang //
NK010(tha)012:751: phyi yi phyogs bzhir rab tu gdab //
NK010(tha)012:752: me dang bden bral mtshams gnas te //
NK010(tha)012:753: gru yi thig ni mnyam par gdab //
NK010(tha)012:756: tshangs thig dang po gdab pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:757: tshangs thig gnyis pa'ang de bzhin gdab //
NK010(tha)012:758: de bzhin phyogs mtshams ma 'khrul gdab //
NK010(tha)012:759: cha brgyad de bsres bcu drug cha //
NK010(tha)012:760: cha phran drug cu rtsa bzhir gdab //
NK010(tha)012:761: dbus kyi phyi rol bcu drug bskor //
NK010(tha)012:762: phyi rim sgo dang rgyan du bya //
NK010(tha)012:763: zhes bshad kyang rgyud thig 'jug pa mi bde bas man ngag thig gis gsal bar byas pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:764: dang po tshangs zur thig chen brgyad //
NK010(tha)012:765: bya rjes la brten btab byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:766: 'khor lo'i tog nas tog bar gyi //
NK010(tha)012:767: mtshan ma tshangs thig rtse la btab //
NK010(tha)012:768: mtshan ma re dang lte ba'i 'dzom //
NK010(tha)012:769: sked gtubs zur nas gru bzhir gdab //
NK010(tha)012:770: rtsa thig gam ni rtsig pa'i nang //
NK010(tha)012:771: rtsa thig de dang mtshan ma'i bar //
NK010(tha)012:772: phyed gtubs de'i yang nang gshags pa //
NK010(tha)012:773: sgo tshad dam ni cha chen gnyis //
NK010(tha)012:774: ma chen nang ma'i mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK010(tha)012:775: rtsig pa 'dod snam pha gu yin //
NK010(tha)012:776: nang ma'i phyed gdab phyi ma'ang gdab //
NK010(tha)012:777: d+r+wa phyed shar bu mda' yab bo //
NK010(tha)012:778: sgo dang sgo khyud la sogs phyir //
NK010(tha)012:779: tshangs pa'i g.yas g.yon cha chen ni //
NK010(tha)012:780: gnyis re gdab pa'i nang ma ni //
NK010(tha)012:781: phyed gdab phyi ma'ang gdab par bya //
NK010(tha)012:782: de'i phyi cha phran bzhi ru bgo //
NK010(tha)012:783: rim bzhin sgo khyud sgo 'gram logs //
NK010(tha)012:784: rtsigs mun ka ba ka rgyan no //
NK010(tha)012:785: rta babs bzhi po cha phran te //
NK010(tha)012:786: dang po'i zheng dang ka rgyan mnyam //
NK010(tha)012:787: gnyis gsum bzhi pa cha re bskum //
NK010(tha)012:788: chu skyes zheng ni sgo tshad la //
NK010(tha)012:789: srid du cha phran gcig nyid do //
NK010(tha)012:790: 'khor lo srid zheng cha phran gnyis //
NK010(tha)012:791: gdugs ni cha phran tog dang bcas //
NK010(tha)012:792: mun mthong glang rgyab dbyibs bya phyir //
NK010(tha)012:793: rta snam gnyis pa'i phyi thig dang //
NK010(tha)012:794: tshangs thig rgya gram thebs sa nas //
NK010(tha)012:795: cha phran gnyis bskor dbus ma yin //
NK010(tha)012:796: rta snam dang po'i phyi thig dang //
NK010(tha)012:797: sgo cha g.yas g.yon phrad mtshams nas //
NK010(tha)012:798: rang rang cha phran gnyis gnyis bskor //
NK010(tha)012:799: nang thig phyis pa thig 'di phyi basngasa na mi yong /
NK010(tha)012:801: de nas ka rgyan rtser bskyed bskor //
NK010(tha)012:802: rdo rje ra ba'i nang thig yin //
NK010(tha)012:803: de nas 'phrad gnyis gyen du gcig /
NK010(tha)012:804: phyin la ra ba'i phyi mtha' bskor //
NK010(tha)012:805: phyi rim pad+ma cha chen phyed //
NK010(tha)012:806: mtshan bzang sum cu rtsa gnyis grangs //
NK010(tha)012:807: lha snam dur khrod cha chen re //
NK010(tha)012:808: rdo ra cha phyed me ri gcig /
NK010(tha)012:810: de'i tshe thig la mi 'gong ba'i 'dun pa bsgyur ba'ang /
NK010(tha)012:812: ye shes thig la mi 'gong ste //
NK010(tha)012:815: de nas nang dang lha gnas tshul //
NK010(tha)012:816: lte ba cha chen bzhi spyi dril bzhi zlum skor //
NK010(tha)012:818: dbus su chos 'byung mthing nag bri //
NK010(tha)012:819: phyi rol rtsibs bcur cha chen gcig /
NK010(tha)012:820: chos 'byung dbus su gtso bo'i mtshan //
NK010(tha)012:821: mdun du sgrol yum zla gam dmar //
NK010(tha)012:822: gsum po'i g.yas g.yon sras bzhi dang //
NK010(tha)012:823: rgyab tu gcig pa'i lha mtshan bya //
NK010(tha)012:824: rtsibs bcu'i steng ma shar gyi shar //
NK010(tha)012:825: 'og ma nub kyi nub byas pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:826: khro bcu so so'i lha mtshan dang //
NK010(tha)012:827: rtsibs mchan g.yas g.yon phra phyag bkod //
NK010(tha)012:828: khyams bzhir dbang mo bdun bdun dang //
NK010(tha)012:829: sgo la sgo srung mu ran la //
NK010(tha)012:830: dam can bcu gnyis rgyud so so'i //
NK010(tha)012:831: rang lugs de ma thag tu ston //
NK010(tha)012:833: sor bzhi pa nas bzung nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:834: ji srid dpag tshad rgyang grags bar //
NK010(tha)012:835: sems can bsam pa'i dbang gis ni //
NK010(tha)012:836: tshad rnams nges pa ma gsungs so //
NK010(tha)012:838: re zhig gnas dang 'byor pa'i dbang du byas na ye shes rtse mo las /
NK010(tha)012:839: sor mo nyis brgya rtsa bcu brgyad //
NK010(tha)012:840: mkhas pas dkyil 'khor tshad du bya //
NK010(tha)012:842: dur khrod las byung ba'i tshon rnams kyang dpa' bo
NK010(tha)012:843: 'bru lngas brlabs te dgye ba'i tshul phrin las kyi
NK010(tha)012:844: rgyud las / sngon po la sogs tshon rnams ni //
NK010(tha)012:845: dpa' bo 'bru lngas byin gyis brlabs //
NK010(tha)012:846: gzhung dang mthun par tshon bkye ste //
NK010(tha)012:849: rdul tshon kha ba bab pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:850: g.yas nas bskor te rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:854: gru bzhi pa la sgo bzhi pa //
NK010(tha)012:855: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad mu khyud bcas //
NK010(tha)012:856: bar khyams gser khyams khrag khyams gnyis dgos pa 'og gi shes so //
NK010(tha)012:858: rta babs kyis ni mdzes pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:859: h+aa ra h+aa ra phyed nyi zla //
NK010(tha)012:860: dril bu dar dpyangs 'phan la sogs //
NK010(tha)012:861: thod sbrul nyi zlas brgyan pa la //
NK010(tha)012:864: karma ku ru'i rgyud las kyang /
NK010(tha)012:865: lte ba nag po 'khor lo ser //
NK010(tha)012:866: de yi gong ras nag por bya //
NK010(tha)012:867: gser khyams dbang phyug nyer brgyad kyi gnas ye shes
NK010(tha)012:868: rtse mo las bshad pa'i rnam par gsod byed kyi
NK010(tha)012:869: khro bo rnams kyi gnas mtshon pa yin no //
NK010(tha)012:871: gru chad ljang gu lcags ri nag /
NK010(tha)012:872: ces pa dang yang bstun no //
NK010(tha)012:873: gzhan yang gsang ba'i dgongs rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:874: 'khor lo brgyad thig dag tu gdab //
NK010(tha)012:875: dbus su drag po gru gsum la //
NK010(tha)012:876: zla gam dmar po dbang gi tshul //
NK010(tha)012:877: zlum po gong ras gru bzhi rgyas pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:878: gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:879: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:881: las bzhi so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam bzhag kyang de'i le'u gsum pas ston la /
NK010(tha)012:882: gzhan rnams sgrub thabs dang bstun par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:883: de'i tshe spyod lam gzab pa'i tshul yang /
NK010(tha)012:884: skud pa chad na slob dpon 'chi //
NK010(tha)012:885: thig sna shor na slob bu 'chi //
NK010(tha)012:886: phyogs 'khrul pas ni gnyis ka nyams //
NK010(tha)012:887: rgyun chad lam la gnod par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:888: de phyir mkhas pas bsgrims te bya //
NK010(tha)012:890: de yang thog mar slob dpon dang de nas dpon
NK010(tha)012:891: slob thams cad kyis g.yas su 'khor bar srab 'thug
NK010(tha)012:892: med cing snyoms par bris nas rtsigs pa sbrel ba'i
NK010(tha)012:893: tshe pra brtag pa'i tshul yang ku ku r+aa dzas
NK010(tha)012:894: / re kh+aa dma' bas mi 'grub cing //
NK010(tha)012:895: yon pos gdung ba skyed par byed //
NK010(tha)012:896: chad pas slob dpon slob ma dag /
NK010(tha)012:898: chad lhag las ni nad 'byung zhing //
NK010(tha)012:901: de nas slob dpon nam rgyal tshab kyis lha mtshan dgod pa'i tshul ni ye shes rtse mo las /
NK010(tha)012:902: las la lung thob gang yin pas //
NK010(tha)012:903: phyag rgya dgod pa brtsam par bya //
NK010(tha)012:904: dbus ma mnyam pa ni rdo rje //
NK010(tha)012:905: mig sman gyi ni mdog dang 'dra //
NK010(tha)012:906: gtso bo'i grangs dang mnyam pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:907: rtse mo 'phro ba dbus su bzhag /
NK010(tha)012:908: rtsibs brgyad pa ni 'bar ba ste //
NK010(tha)012:909: mdun du yang dag gnas par bya //
NK010(tha)012:910: rdo rje mdzes pa de ltar ro //
NK010(tha)012:911: 'od zer du ma'i rin po che //
NK010(tha)012:912: rang gi gnas su gzhag par bya //
NK010(tha)012:913: zhes pa'i lte ba la rdo rje rtse gsum nag po dang /
NK010(tha)012:914: sras mchog lnga la so so'i rigs kyi phyag mtshan rang mdog /
NK010(tha)012:915: rtsibs brgyad la khro bcu so so'i rigs kyi mtshan ma yongs dag gi rgyud dang bstun na /
NK010(tha)012:916: brgya byin phyogs su rdo rje kha gdangs bri //
NK010(tha)012:917: mer ni rdo rje rin chen bri //
NK010(tha)012:918: gshegs rje'i phyogs su rdo rje mda' //
NK010(tha)012:919: bden bral phyogs su rdo rje gzhu //
NK010(tha)012:920: chu bdag rdo rje kyo ba bri //
NK010(tha)012:921: rlung gi phyogs su rdo rje me //
NK010(tha)012:922: gnod sbyin phyogs su rdo rje dbyug /
NK010(tha)012:923: dbang ldan rdo rje rtse gsum bri //
NK010(tha)012:924: shar stod rdo rje thod pa 'bri //
NK010(tha)012:925: nub smad rdo rje rkang pa bri //
NK010(tha)012:928: de yang steng rnam rgyal shar gyi shar dang /
NK010(tha)012:929: 'og stobs po che nub kyi nub tu bkod cing
NK010(tha)012:930: rtsibs mchan rnams la phur pa gnyis gnyis dang lhag
NK010(tha)012:931: ma rnams ni / karma ku ru'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:932: de yi phyi rol snam bu la //
NK010(tha)012:933: srung ma rnams ni spel mar bkod //
NK010(tha)012:934: sgo la sgo ma bzhi rnams te //
NK010(tha)012:935: lcags ri la ni dbang phyug ma //
NK010(tha)012:936: don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK010(tha)012:937: bran gyi tshul du mu ran bzhugs //
NK010(tha)012:938: zhes bshad kyang 'dir rtsa bshad kyi rjes su 'brangs
NK010(tha)012:939: nas dbang mo nyer brgyad khyams kyi phyogs bzhir bzhugs
NK010(tha)012:941: de ltar bkod nas sta gon gyi dus na ye
NK010(tha)012:942: shes pa nam mkhar bzhugs pa rnams phyag rgya bzhi
NK010(tha)012:943: sngags dang bcas pa dal la bstim mo //
NK010(tha)012:944: de nas rgyan dang mchod rdzas dgram pa'i tshul yang gsang rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:945: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas dang //
NK010(tha)012:946: mda' dang phur bu ral gri dang //
NK010(tha)012:947: me long dar sna srung skud dang //
NK010(tha)012:950: drag po'i rdzas rnams rab tu gsog /
NK010(tha)012:951: lhu dum bcad 'phro dum bu dang //
NK010(tha)012:952: sgal tshigs klad pa khrag dang mgo //
NK010(tha)012:953: gru gsum mthing nag gtor ma bcas //
NK010(tha)012:954: dug sogs drag po'i rdzas rnams basngagasa //
NK010(tha)012:955: mkha' 'gro'i rdzas dang bcas pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:956: bsags te mchod pa bya ba yin //
NK010(tha)012:957: zhes pas dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang mchod rdzas drag pos 'or pa dag dang /
NK010(tha)012:958: sngar sta gon du grub pa'i bum pa gsum la
NK010(tha)012:959: sogs dbang rdzas rnams ma tshang ba med par 'du
NK010(tha)012:960: bya'o // gnyis pa dbang gi bya ba la gsum /
NK010(tha)012:966: rdzas rnams phun sum tshogs ldan pa //
NK010(tha)012:967: lha rnams bsgrub pa tshul bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)012:968: zhes pas bskyed rdzogs la goms pa brtan pas bdag mdun bum gsum 'jug pa gcig pa'ang rung la /
NK010(tha)012:969: mos pas spyod pa rnams ni so sor cho ga
NK010(tha)012:970: tha dad pas dmigs rnam phyed pa nyed legs so
NK010(tha)012:973: gsol gdab dbang yang nod par bya //
NK010(tha)012:974: sku dang gsung dang thugs dang ni //
NK010(tha)012:975: yon tan phrin las lnga ru bskur //
NK010(tha)012:976: phyogs bcu srog la dbang bskur bas //
NK010(tha)012:977: srog ni ye shes gyur nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:978: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:979: zhes phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas
NK010(tha)012:980: pa gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rnam
NK010(tha)012:982: rig pa'i dbang lnga bskur ba'i bya ba mdzad pa'i
NK010(tha)012:983: tshe bde stong zung du 'jug pa'i nyams gsar du
NK010(tha)012:984: skyes pa la dbang rnam bzhi'i rim pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:985: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin bum dbang gi chus dri ma mtha' dag sbyangs nas /
NK010(tha)012:986: chu lhag ma gyen du ldog pa nyid rigs lnga'i
NK010(tha)012:987: dbu rgyan du gyur par mos pa ni dkyil 'khor
NK010(tha)012:988: gsum gyi srog ye shes su dbang bskur ba dang
NK010(tha)012:989: / de las bdag nyid kyang gdod nas grub pa'i
NK010(tha)012:990: dkyil 'khor du gsal ba'i gnas gsum du sku gsung
NK010(tha)012:991: thugs kyi lha gsum la phyag mtshan gsum dang sa
NK010(tha)012:992: bon gsum gyis mtshan pa las 'od zer 'phros /
NK010(tha)012:993: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi las dang nyon mongs pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)012:994: ma rtogs par 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rtogs pa byang
NK010(tha)012:995: chub kyi sems su bsgral nas bdag dang gnyis su
NK010(tha)012:996: med par bsdu ba ni khams gsum gyi srog la
NK010(tha)012:997: dbang bskur ba zhes bya ste /
NK010(tha)012:999: khams gsum ye nas sangs rgyas yin //
NK010(tha)012:1000: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1001: gnyis med byang chub sems su bsgral //
NK010(tha)012:1002: slar 'dus bdag la dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1004: 'di ni phur pa rang lugs kyi bdag 'jug gi
NK010(tha)012:1005: don po sngon chad gzhan gyis ma rtogs pa mang
NK010(tha)012:1006: ste / rnam pa'i bya ba slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba'i cho gas 'jug go //
NK010(tha)012:1012: dar dkar yol ba bres pa ru //
NK010(tha)012:1013: rdzas dang lag cha kun bkram nas //
NK010(tha)012:1014: slob ma lnga'am gcig kyang rung //
NK010(tha)012:1015: gdong g.yogs dar gyis rab dkris la //
NK010(tha)012:1016: dag pa'i khrus kyis bkrus byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:1017: rin chen sna tshogs snyim par bzung //
NK010(tha)012:1019: sku gsung thugs kyi yig 'bru yis //
NK010(tha)012:1020: de yi lus ngag yid gsum bkru //
NK010(tha)012:1021: zhes pas 'bru gsum bsdus pa'i las bum gyis khrus bya /
NK010(tha)012:1022: slob ma'i bdud dang bgegs bsal te //
NK010(tha)012:1023: yon ni khas ni len du gzhug /
NK010(tha)012:1024: ces pas bgegs bsal ba'i phyir phyi rol pa la gtor ma byin nas bskrad pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1025: bdud bsal ba'i phyir rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:1026: khro bo yig 'bru phyag mtshan gyi //
NK010(tha)012:1028: ces pas khro mo rdo rje sder mo sogs kyi
NK010(tha)012:1029: drag sngags bzlas pa'i las bum gyi khrus nas dbyung
NK010(tha)012:1030: ba dang / blo bcos pa'i chos bshad pa sogs spyi ltar byas nas /
NK010(tha)012:1031: yid mchog tu bya ba'i phyir mig dar /
NK010(tha)012:1032: badz+ra tsak+shub+han+d+ha wa ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)012:1035: zhes nam mkha'i dpa' bo bos nas me tog gtad
NK010(tha)012:1036: pas rigs lnga'i sa bon rang rang las skyes pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1037: me tog gi phreng ba so so'i sa bon gyis
NK010(tha)012:1038: mtshan pa re snyim par bzung bar bsgom /
NK010(tha)012:1039: de nas slob ma rnams kyis yol ba'i phyi rol nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:1041: khrag 'thung rdo rje he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:1042: bdag gi bdud rtsi lngas mchod de //
NK010(tha)012:1043: bdag ni rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK010(tha)012:1044: mi phyed rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK010(tha)012:1047: skal ldan rig 'dzin rigs kyi bu //
NK010(tha)012:1048: lhag pa'i bsam pa bzang po'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1049: da lta'i dus nas sems bskyed nas //
NK010(tha)012:1050: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK010(tha)012:1051: zhes pa'i lan du slob bus /
NK010(tha)012:1052: bdag ni skal bzang bde chen la //
NK010(tha)012:1053: bde chen mchog la bdag dga' ste //
NK010(tha)012:1054: bla med byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1056: zhes brjod pa la dam tshig bsgrags nas sdom pa thun mong ba byin pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:1059: rigs kyi bu khyod 'jug par byos //
NK010(tha)012:1060: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:1061: dam tshig gnyan las khyod ma 'da' //
NK010(tha)012:1062: dkyil 'khor gsang ba ma mthong zhing //
NK010(tha)012:1063: gsang ba dam pa ma mthong la //
NK010(tha)012:1064: gsang ba dam pa smra ma byed //
NK010(tha)012:1065: khyod kyis sems can srog ma gcod //
NK010(tha)012:1066: ma byin len pa rdzun la sogs //
NK010(tha)012:1067: mi dge'i las rnams spang bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:1069: theg chen gyi rigs sad par byed pa'i smon 'jug
NK010(tha)012:1070: stabs gcig pa sngar sta gon bzhin du byed nas
NK010(tha)012:1071: rdo rje'i rnal 'byor du sems bskyed pa'i phyir gsol
NK010(tha)012:1074: rdo rje ye shes chen po yi //
NK010(tha)012:1075: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1076: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje ste //
NK010(tha)012:1077: de ring bdag la dbang bskur shog /
NK010(tha)012:1078: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1079: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)012:1080: ma lus gzhung bzhin bsgrub nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:1081: sku gsung thugs kyi phur pa bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:1082: ye shes rdo rje dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)012:1083: bdag gis dad pas 'jug par bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:1084: rdo rje 'joms byed chen po yis //
NK010(tha)012:1085: bdag la dbang mchog de ring gsol //
NK010(tha)012:1088: nga ni ye shes rdo rje ste //
NK010(tha)012:1089: nyon mongs rnam rtog 'joms pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1091: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK010(tha)012:1092: zhes brjod nas slob bu'i snying gar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK010(tha)012:1093: khyod gzhan don du sangs rgyas sgrub par 'dun pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1094: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems de nyid snying gar
NK010(tha)012:1095: zla ba nya gang ba'i steng du /
NK010(tha)012:1096: don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems rdo rje rtse
NK010(tha)012:1097: lnga pa 'od zer lnga ldan gyi rnam pa can
NK010(tha)012:1098: du sgom la thams cad rnal 'byor du sems bskyed
NK010(tha)012:1100: +amo sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+pa ta ya m+ai /
NK010(tha)012:1103: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)012:1104: rnam rtog 'joms phyir ye shes gsal //
NK010(tha)012:1105: sangs rgyas bdag la dbang ldan shog /
NK010(tha)012:1107: de nas sngags sdom bye brag pa gzung ba'i phyir mos pa brtan pos 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK010(tha)012:1110: sangs rgyas kun gyi 'grub pa'i gzhi //
NK010(tha)012:1111: bla med rdo rje'i dam tshig ste //
NK010(tha)012:1112: dam tshig 'di ni gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:1113: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK010(tha)012:1114: dkon mchog mkha' 'gro ma yang gzung //
NK010(tha)012:1115: phyag rgya sngags rnams rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:1116: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK010(tha)012:1117: gsang ba chen po smra mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:1118: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams gzung //
NK010(tha)012:1119: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK010(tha)012:1120: zhe sdang gti mug chags nga rgyal //
NK010(tha)012:1121: dkar dmar ljang ser mthing ga'i mdog /
NK010(tha)012:1122: dag pa'i snod bcud mi dor ro //
NK010(tha)012:1123: yan lag bcu yi dam tshig mdo //
NK010(tha)012:1124: bdag gis brtan por gzung bar bgyi //
NK010(tha)012:1125: nam du yang ni mi spang ngo //
NK010(tha)012:1126: lan gsum gyis sngags sdom thob par nges shes bskyed do //
NK010(tha)012:1127: de nas dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:1128: dbang thob bya dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba la brten nas thob kyang /
NK010(tha)012:1129: dbang 'dzin pa dam tshig la brten nas 'dzin pa
NK010(tha)012:1130: yin pas nan tur du smos pa ste rang sngags
NK010(tha)012:1131: kyis bzlos pa'i dam chu byin la /
NK010(tha)012:1132: de ring khyod kyi snying la ni //
NK010(tha)012:1133: rdo rje sems dpa' yang dag gnas //
NK010(tha)012:1134: gal te tshul 'di dral gyur na //
NK010(tha)012:1135: skad cig gis ni dral te gshegs //
NK010(tha)012:1136: de bas dam las ma 'da' zhig /
NK010(tha)012:1138: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1139: phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyi //
NK010(tha)012:1140: nga yis smras pa thams cad kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1141: nges pa kho nar bya dgos so //
NK010(tha)012:1142: bdag la smad par ma byed cig /
NK010(tha)012:1143: gal te smad par byas na ni //
NK010(tha)012:1144: tshe yi 'du byed byas nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1145: dam chu 'di yis rkyen byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:1146: rdo rje dmyal bar 'gyur ta re //
NK010(tha)012:1147: skal dang ldan pa rigs kyi bu //
NK010(tha)012:1148: khyod kyis bsrung bar bya ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1149: lha dang bla ma spun mi spang //
NK010(tha)012:1150: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad //
NK010(tha)012:1151: gsang ba gzhan la spel mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:1152: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ste //
NK010(tha)012:1153: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nges thub na //
NK010(tha)012:1154: dam chu 'di yis rkyen byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:1155: ye shes sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:1158: khyod la dam tshig 'bog pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1159: yi dam lha la rtag par gnas //
NK010(tha)012:1160: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:1161: bla ma mig gi 'bras ltar blta //
NK010(tha)012:1162: rdo rje spun la brtse gdung che //
NK010(tha)012:1163: gsang ba'i man ngag thabs mchog 'di //
NK010(tha)012:1164: snod ngan gzhan la mi spel lo //
NK010(tha)012:1165: rgyud 'grel blo zhen bsgrub la zhugs //
NK010(tha)012:1166: sbyor sgrol mchod pa rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:1167: rdzas dang lag cha rtag tu 'chongs //
NK010(tha)012:1168: lta ba nam mkha' bcos pa med //
NK010(tha)012:1169: sgom pa ngang bzhag blang dor bral //
NK010(tha)012:1170: spyod pa sa gzhi bzhin du gyis //
NK010(tha)012:1171: dam tshig 'jig pa'i mkhar bzhin bsrung //
NK010(tha)012:1172: gsang ba'i dam tshig 'da' bar dka' //
NK010(tha)012:1173: gsang sngags ston pa'i slob dpon la //
NK010(tha)012:1174: smad sems 'phya sems byas na ni //
NK010(tha)012:1175: dngos grub med cing dmyal bar ltung //
NK010(tha)012:1176: srog la bar chad myur du 'ong //
NK010(tha)012:1179: de nas lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i rten 'brel sgrig phyir 'jug pa dngos ni /
NK010(tha)012:1181: khrus dang gtsang sbra dri zhim lus //
NK010(tha)012:1182: sna tshogs rgyan gyis rnam par brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:1183: h'u snyems byams pa'i sgra yang sgrogs //
NK010(tha)012:1184: hi hi 'jigs pa'i sgo phye nas //
NK010(tha)012:1185: dkyil 'khor chen por zhugs par gyur //
NK010(tha)012:1188: zhes tshad med bzhi dang mthun pa'i sgo dbye bar bsam zhing /
NK010(tha)012:1189: slob ma'i lag pa nas bzung la shar sgo nas
NK010(tha)012:1190: rim par g.yas skor gyi sgo bzhir khrid par mos
NK010(tha)012:1191: la / rat+na push+pa a b+ai ra h'u kham /
NK010(tha)012:1197: zhes sgo so sor sku gsung thugs phyag bya ba yan ni phyi 'jug go //
NK010(tha)012:1199: thog mar slob ma'i rnam smin gyi phung po sbyangs
NK010(tha)012:1200: nas dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po'i sras su bya ba'i
NK010(tha)012:1202: sras kyi mchog tu rab tu dmigs //
NK010(tha)012:1204: dbang ni rab tu blang bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:1205: zhes pas dang por gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:1207: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shees sku //
NK010(tha)012:1208: ngang nyid rdo rje chos nyid las //
NK010(tha)012:1209: 'bar ba'i khra bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:1210: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)012:1212: dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum bde ba chen po'i rba rlabs g.yos /
NK010(tha)012:1213: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h'u h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1214: ces brjod pa'i sgra dang 'od zer gyis slob ma'i rnam smin gyi phung po sbyangs /
NK010(tha)012:1215: rnam par shes pa la ngo bo nyid med pa ni chos kyi sku /
NK010(tha)012:1216: de'i ngang las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin h'u du gyur pa yab kyi zhal nas drangs /
NK010(tha)012:1217: yum gyi b+ha gar rdo rje gzhon nur smin pas sku gsum rdzogs /
NK010(tha)012:1218: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes brjod pas phyir phyung
NK010(tha)012:1219: ste yab kyi phyag rigs lnga yab yum du gyur
NK010(tha)012:1220: pas blang / sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK010(tha)012:1221: zhes brjod pas bde ba'i rlabs kyis dbang bzhi bskur /
NK010(tha)012:1222: de la ye shes dbab pa'i phyir spos rol bya
NK010(tha)012:1223: zhing rdzas kyi sbyor ba dmigs bsal bsreg pa dang
NK010(tha)012:1225: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)012:1226: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)012:1227: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:1228: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag gsol cig /
NK010(tha)012:1229: sangs rgyas 'dus pa thams cad kyis //
NK010(tha)012:1230: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)012:1231: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya +aa be sha ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1232: ces lan mang du brjod cing /
NK010(tha)012:1233: slob mas lus ngag yid gsum drang por bzhag pas 'dar ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:1240: rtogs pa thod rgal du skye ba ni dbang las byung ba'i ye shes ma nor ba nyid de /
NK010(tha)012:1241: mdor na sgo gsum la blang dor med pa'i spyod pa sna tshogs 'char ro //
NK010(tha)012:1242: phebs rtags byung ma thag spyi bor rdo rje rgya gram 'jog cing /
NK010(tha)012:1243: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)012:1244: ma gu la pra ta la h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1245: ces brjod pas brtan par bya /
NK010(tha)012:1246: de nas rigs dang las 'brel brtag pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor dngos sam /
NK010(tha)012:1247: re kh+aa'i nang du me tog sngon po sna tshogs
NK010(tha)012:1248: phyi rol du ma 'das par dor zhing bshad rgyud
NK010(tha)012:1250: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)012:1251: rdo rje rigs kyi me tog dor nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1252: khrag 'thung rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1253: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rab 'byams rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1254: skal ldan rig 'dzin bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:1255: bdag ni rdo rje'i rigs su gzung du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:1256: +amo bo d+hi tsit+ta p+au tsa ho /
NK010(tha)012:1257: de nas bla mas rigs de dang mthun pa'i ming
NK010(tha)012:1258: gdags shing dngos grub thob par lung bstan nas lhag
NK010(tha)012:1259: pa'i lha des rjes su 'dzin pa'i rten 'brel sgrig
NK010(tha)012:1260: phyir slar cod pan spyi bor bcings shing /
NK010(tha)012:1261: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1262: ming ni rdo rje che ge mo //
NK010(tha)012:1263: rdo rje kun grags yin par nges //
NK010(tha)012:1264: rdo rje'i mtshan gyis kun grags shog /
NK010(tha)012:1266: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)012:1267: byang chub rdo rje lam nas spyan drangs nas //
NK010(tha)012:1268: khrag 'thung rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs kyi //
NK010(tha)012:1269: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rab 'byams rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1270: skal ldan rig 'dzin khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK010(tha)012:1273: de nas mig dbye ba ni rtsa bshad kyi rgyud las dngos su ma bstan kyang /
NK010(tha)012:1275: mig dbye dkyil 'khor don rtags rab tu bstan //
NK010(tha)012:1277: slob dpon gyis mig thur thogs la /
NK010(tha)012:1278: sngon tshe mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK010(tha)012:1279: gser gyi gtsags bu thogs nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:1280: mig gi ling tog bsal ba ltar //
NK010(tha)012:1281: thugs rje ye shes thabs ldan pas //
NK010(tha)012:1282: mi shes rmongs pa'i rab rib dang //
NK010(tha)012:1283: ma rig mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:1284: deng khyod rdo rje sems kyis ni //
NK010(tha)012:1285: mig kun nges par 'byed mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:1286: mig 'byed pa la brtson par byed //
NK010(tha)012:1287: rdo rje'i mig tu bla med 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:1288: +amo badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu pra we sha phata /
NK010(tha)012:1290: de nas dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:1291: chos rnams gzugs brnyan 'dra ba yi //
NK010(tha)012:1292: rang bzhin dag par rnyog pa med //
NK010(tha)012:1293: gzugs brnyan gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)012:1294: kun gyis dri ma med mthong shog /
NK010(tha)012:1295: dkyil 'khor nyid la da lta nyid //
NK010(tha)012:1296: dad pa'i shugs kyis blta bar gyis //
NK010(tha)012:1297: khyed kyang sangs rgyas rigs las skyes //
NK010(tha)012:1298: sngags dang phyag rgya'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)012:1300: badz+ra man+dala pra we sha ya hoh e ma snod dang ldan pa'i bu //
NK010(tha)012:1302: tshon rtsi mthong bas sdig las grol //
NK010(tha)012:1303: de phyir dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK010(tha)012:1304: rtags kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ni //
NK010(tha)012:1305: don gyi 'og min nyid yin te //
NK010(tha)012:1306: byang chub phyogs kyi chos kun dang //
NK010(tha)012:1307: sa lam 'bras bu'i yon tan rdzogs //
NK010(tha)012:1308: de na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kun //
NK010(tha)012:1309: rang gi sems su shes par gyis //
NK010(tha)012:1310: sems ni chos nyid la gnas pas //
NK010(tha)012:1311: rang byung lhun grub dkyil 'khor yin //
NK010(tha)012:1312: zhes mthong ba spyir bstan no //
NK010(tha)012:1314: rten dang brten pa'i dag sbyor ji bzhin du rtogs
NK010(tha)012:1315: par 'dod na dag pa rgyas par brjod pa la
NK010(tha)012:1316: gnyis / dang po rten gzhal yas khang gi dag pa ni gsang dgongs las /
NK010(tha)012:1317: gzhal yas gsal ba'i don rtags ni //
NK010(tha)012:1318: gzhal yas gru bzhir byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1319: tshad med bzhi yi don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1320: phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1321: rnam thar ye shes don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1322: rta babs yang dag spong ba bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:1323: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1324: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1325: nyon mongs gnas su dag pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1326: zhing smug ka ba brgyad btegs pa //
NK010(tha)012:1327: 'phags pa'i lam brgyad don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1328: tshangs pa'i gdung lnga bkye ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1329: dug lnga gnas su dag pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1330: nyi zla'i ka gdan ka gzhu ni //
NK010(tha)012:1331: thabs dang shes rab don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1332: zhing gi ya khal ma khal gyis //
NK010(tha)012:1333: ya them ma them byas pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1334: pha ma'i chags sdang gnas su dag pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1335: sbrul nag skye bu byas pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1336: 'khor ba zhe sdang bsad pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1337: dur khrod chen pos brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1338: nyon mongs cho 'phrul sngon du phyung //
NK010(tha)012:1339: yang sprul sum sprul gtod cing zab pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1340: 'dod yon lha mos brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1341: longs spyod lnga ldan don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1342: rin chen pha gu la sogs brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:1343: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:1344: rin chen sna lnga'i rtsig pas brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:1345: ye shes lnga yi don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1346: zur sgor rgyal mtshan bzhi yis brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1347: rnam rtog bdud las rgyal ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1348: dpag bsam shing gis rgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1349: thugs rjes yongs la khyab pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1350: ri dwags sha ras brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1351: byang chub sems dpas bskor ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1352: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1353: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK010(tha)012:1354: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1355: zhing gi gdugs dang 'phan gyis brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1356: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK010(tha)012:1357: so sor yang dag don ni ston pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:1358: nang ni thod pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)012:1359: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1360: dbus su gru gsum mthing nag byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1361: chos kyi dbyings nyid skye med las //
NK010(tha)012:1362: sku gsung thugs gsum byung ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1363: zla gam dmar po gsum du byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1364: srid gsum dbang du sdud pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1365: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1366: don gyi 'khor lo rgyas par bskor ba'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1367: pho brang zlum por byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1368: skye med lhun gyis grub pa'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1369: dkar po zlum por byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1370: zhi ba chen po'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1371: ser po gru bzhir byung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1372: rgyas pa chen po'i don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1373: rdo rje ra bas bskor ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1374: thugs ni yang dag don rtags yin //
NK010(tha)012:1376: de yang nang du rdo rje phung po'i grong khyer la tshang ba'i tshul ni /
NK010(tha)012:1378: rkang pa rlung gi dal yin te //
NK010(tha)012:1380: gsus pa chu yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK010(tha)012:1381: pho ba sa yi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK010(tha)012:1382: brag ni keng rus ri rab ste //
NK010(tha)012:1383: mgo bo thod pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)012:1384: rtsa gnas dbus na lha tshogs bzhugs //
NK010(tha)012:1385: zhes pas rdo rje'i lus ni gsang sngags bla med
NK010(tha)012:1386: kyi gdod nas grub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po yin
NK010(tha)012:1387: te / 'dom gang gru bzhi pas dal gru bzhi yod pa mtshon /
NK010(tha)012:1388: 'khor lo lnga ni dbus kyi pho brang chen po /
NK010(tha)012:1389: kha sna dang 'og sgo gnyis ni 'jug pa'i sgo bzhi /
NK010(tha)012:1390: mig gnyis dang rna ba gnyis ni lkog gyur ye shes chen po'i sgo bzhi /
NK010(tha)012:1391: snying gi phyogs bzhi nas 'byung bzhi'i rlung rgyu bas bar gyi sgo bzhi /
NK010(tha)012:1408: phyi rol gyi rtsa rnams srung ba'i 'khor lo'i rim pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:1409: de dag kyang gsang bar rang sems la tshang ste /
NK010(tha)012:1410: sems nyid la mtha' dbus med pas stong pa nam mkha'i dal /
NK010(tha)012:1411: sems gcig tu mi gnas pas g.yo ba rlung gi dal /
NK010(tha)012:1412: sems las yon tan thams cad 'byung bas gsher ba chu'i dal /
NK010(tha)012:1413: sems gang gis kyang mi bshigs pas sra ba sa'i dal /
NK010(tha)012:1414: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal zhing rno bas bsregs pa me'i dal /
NK010(tha)012:1415: sems la 'khor 'das thams cad brtan pas ri rab /
NK010(tha)012:1416: sems la byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun 'dus pas gzhal yas khang /
NK010(tha)012:1417: kun gzhi'i rnam shes rgya ma chad pas lte ba zlum po /
NK010(tha)012:1418: nyon mongs pa'i yid zur rno bas lha snam gru bzhi /
NK010(tha)012:1419: yid kyi rnam shes gdangs phyed pas rta babs /
NK010(tha)012:1420: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kun tu 'jug pas sgo bzhi ba glang mig dang bcas pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:1421: rgyu dus na rtsa thig rlung gsum gyi dag bya'i
NK010(tha)012:1422: sgrib pa nyid 'dir phyi nang gzhan gsum gyi dkyil
NK010(tha)012:1423: 'khor du shar ba'i brda' don rtags gsum gyis mtshon
NK010(tha)012:1424: par byas pas don gyi ye shes phyi rol nas
NK010(tha)012:1425: btsal du med pa'i gnas lugs mthong ba yin no
NK010(tha)012:1426: // gnyis pa ni gzhal yas khang de na bzhugs
NK010(tha)012:1427: pa'i brten pa lha'i tshogs de dag kyang 'khor ba
NK010(tha)012:1428: dang rnam pa mthun pa'i khro gtum can rang rgyud
NK010(tha)012:1429: par bzung na r+au tra dang srin po bzhin du
NK010(tha)012:1430: 'khor ba'i go 'phang las gzhan du ma yin pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1432: lha nyid gzhi rtsa ma bral na //
NK010(tha)012:1433: yang dag don gyi phur pa min //
NK010(tha)012:1434: 'dzin pas bcings pa'i lha nyid ni //
NK010(tha)012:1435: gzhi dang rtsa ba bcas pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1436: nges pa can du gyur pas na //
NK010(tha)012:1437: bya btsal med pa'i ye shes min //
NK010(tha)012:1438: don gyi phur pa gzhi rtsa bral //
NK010(tha)012:1439: snang ba tsam du bstan pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1440: rang rang rgyud du 'dzin pa med //
NK010(tha)012:1441: ces pas chos sku'i dbyings las re zhig gzugs sku'i
NK010(tha)012:1442: rnam par rol pa brda' dang rtags kyis mtshon par
NK010(tha)012:1443: brtan pa'i rnam dag 'di ltar du blta bar bya
NK010(tha)012:1445: dbu gsum phyag drug rdo rje'i gshog pa can //
NK010(tha)012:1446: dbu gsum rnam thar gsum gyi dbu //
NK010(tha)012:1447: dbus ni mthing gar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1448: chos kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1449: zhe sdang rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:1450: g.yas ni dkar bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1451: chos kyi sku la nyes pa med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1452: nyon mongs nang du dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1453: g.yon ni dmar bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1454: thugs rje thabs kyi chags pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1455: 'dod chags rtsad nas bcad pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:1456: spyan mig dgu ru bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1458: theg pa dgu dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1459: mche ba bcu gnyis bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1460: skye mched bcu gnyis rtsad nas gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1461: sha za gdug pa'i mche ba dmar ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1462: shangs ni gsum du bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1463: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1464: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1465: zhal ni gsum du bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1466: dug gsum zhal du gsol ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1467: stong gsum sgra yis dgang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1468: ba spu gyen du 'khyil bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1469: khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1470: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i sa la dgod pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1471: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1472: gdug pa can rnams dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1473: srid pa'i rtse mo zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1474: phyag drug ye shes drug gi rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:1475: g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1476: sa dgu lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1477: theg pa dgu dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1478: bar pa rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1479: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1480: rigs lnga 'gro ba'i don mdzad phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1481: g.yon gyi dang po me dpung bsnams pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1482: ye shes me ru 'bar ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1483: 'khor ba nyon mongs bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1484: g.yon gyi bar ma kha t+w+aam rtse gsum bsnams par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1485: dug gsum rtsad nas gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1486: rigs gsum mgon po rnams dang gnyis su med pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1487: g.yas g.yon tha ma rdo rje ri rab phur bu 'dril bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1488: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1489: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1490: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la gsol ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1491: rnam shes tshogs brgyad rtsad nas gcod pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:1492: glang chen ko rlon sku la gsol bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1493: gti mug rtsad nas bcad nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1494: thugs rje thabs dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1495: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1496: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1497: thugs rje chags par ldan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1498: stag gi sham thabs sku la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1499: zhe sdang rtsad nas bcad pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1500: thugs rje thabs dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1501: thod pa skam pos dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1502: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1503: skye ba med pa'i don rnams grub pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1504: thod pa rnying pas sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1505: longs spyod sku dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1506: thams cad kun tu longs skur bsam mi khyab pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1507: thod pa tshal bus sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1508: sprul pa'i sku dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1509: sprul sku 'gro ba'i don du cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)012:1510: zhag gi zo ris sku la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1511: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1512: mar me mdzad dang bstan pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1513: thal chen tshom bus sku la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1514: da ltar sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1515: bcom ldan 'das dang skal ba gcig pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1516: rak+ta'i thig les sku la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1517: ma byon sangs rgyas rnams dang gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1518: rgyal ba byams pa'i bstan pa gcig pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1519: rdo rje gshog pas sku la brgyan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1520: ma mo mkha' 'gro zil gyis gnon pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1521: thams cad kun tu dbang du sdud pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1522: sbrul chen rigs bzhis sku la brgyan par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1523: gdug pa klu rnams rtsad nas gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1524: zhe sdang 'joms pa'i rgyan ni rigs bzhir bstan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1525: zhabs bzhi mngon par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1526: rdzu 'phrul bzhi yi rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:1527: g.yas gnyis bskum par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1528: pho gnyis 'gram par bardzisa pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1529: thabs nyid shes rab rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:1530: g.yon gnyis brkyang bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1531: mo nyid nu phrag bardzisa pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1532: shes rab thabs kyi rang bzhin phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1533: rdo rje ba spu khro bos gtams par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1534: 'jigs pa med par dbang du sdud pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1535: thams cad kun tu sprul par khyab pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1537: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs dgyes pa skor ba'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:1538: rdo rje rigs kyi gtso mo yum chen mo //
NK010(tha)012:1539: sku mdog mthing bar bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1540: 'gyur ba med pa'i rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:1541: thams cad chos skur gcig pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1542: don rnams thams cad thugs su chud pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1543: spyan mig gnyis su bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1544: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1546: zhal ni gcig tu bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1547: yab la dgyes par bzhad pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1548: dug lnga zhal du gsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1549: mche ba bzhi ru bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1550: skye ba rnam bzhi rtsad nas gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1551: gdug pa'i tshems 'dra rngam pa'i sha za'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1552: shangs ni gcig tu bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1553: chos rnams chos skur gcig pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1554: dri yi mchod pa mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1555: g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1556: shes rab thabs la chags pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1557: dgyes pa chen po bskang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1558: g.yon pa b+han+d+ha rak+ta bsnams pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1559: yum gyi chags pa sel ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1560: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1561: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la gsol ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:1562: sdug bsngal brgyad po rtsad nas bcad nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1563: rnam pa thams cad chos nyid dbyings su sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:1564: zhabs gnyis mngon par bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1565: rkang gnyis kun la brtse bar dgongs pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1566: bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs dam dgyes bskang phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1568: de ltar bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dag
NK010(tha)012:1569: pa brjod nas phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la'ang
NK010(tha)012:1571: phyogs rang bzhin med par ma rtogs shing mi dge
NK010(tha)012:1572: ba bcu'i kun tu rtog pa can rnams ni phyogs
NK010(tha)012:1573: bcu'i gdon gyi gzhan dbang can yin pas de dag
NK010(tha)012:1574: gdul ba'i gnyen por dbang bcu dang sa bcu'i ngo
NK010(tha)012:1575: bo nyid khro bo yab yum bcu sprul pa phra
NK010(tha)012:1576: thabs nyi shu dang bcas par bstan pa'ang /
NK010(tha)012:1578: dregs pa phyogs skyong 'dul ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:1579: kun kyang srin po'i cha byad can //
NK010(tha)012:1580: gnyen po gdul ba'i yum mchog dang //
NK010(tha)012:1581: yab yum sprul pas gdul bya 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:1583: mtshan don dang mthun pa'i dag brjod ni le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK010(tha)012:1584: h'u ni ye shes lnga ldan zhing //
NK010(tha)012:1585: k+aa yis dug lnga 'joms par byed //
NK010(tha)012:1586: ras ni rnam rtog dbyings su thim //
NK010(tha)012:1587: yum chen mi phyed rdo rje sde //
NK010(tha)012:1588: sangs rgyas bskyed par byed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:1589: sems can bud d+ha 'gyur byed tshe //
NK010(tha)012:1590: mi phyed ye shes rdo rje ste //
NK010(tha)012:1591: sgra 'byin brag cha ltar snang ma //
NK010(tha)012:1592: ma ni sprul pa bskyed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:1593: sprul pa rol pa 'gag med nyid //
NK010(tha)012:1594: phag pa ma rig mun pa sel //
NK010(tha)012:1595: rmig bus 'dam rdzab skem par byed //
NK010(tha)012:1597: snang ba mun sel rdo rje snyems //
NK010(tha)012:1598: snang ba sna tshogs stag gi mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1599: bya rgod nam mkha' lta bu ste //
NK010(tha)012:1600: dbyug pas log rtog 'joms byed cing //
NK010(tha)012:1601: sngon pos mtshan ma'i rnam rtog 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:1602: gnyis med rdo rje sder mo ste //
NK010(tha)012:1603: las rnams mi rtog dbyings su thim //
NK010(tha)012:1604: g.yag mgo dbyings las 'gyur ba med //
NK010(tha)012:1605: bya rog chos dbyings rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:1606: gshin ni gzung dang 'dzin pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1607: dmyal ba'i khams mi dpag med kyang //
