NK010(tha)012:1608: don dam dbyings la yod ma yin //
NK010(tha)012:1609: rje ni chos kyi dbyings su thim //
NK010(tha)012:1610: dur khrod rol pa dpag med kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1611: bdag po mkha' dbyings rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:1612: sha ba skye 'gag med pa nyid //
NK010(tha)012:1613: 'ug pa shes rab dbyings nyid de //
NK010(tha)012:1614: lo ka chos brgyad nyid kyi sems //
NK010(tha)012:1615: rtag tu yengs shing gnas pa yang //
NK010(tha)012:1616: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyi //
NK010(tha)012:1617: mi g.yo thig le nyag gcig go //
NK010(tha)012:1618: sems can don byed thams cad kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1619: dam pa'i dbyings ni don yin no //
NK010(tha)012:1620: rdo rje gnyis med zung 'jug dang //
NK010(tha)012:1621: gtun khung snang ba 'joms byed ma //
NK010(tha)012:1622: don dam nyid las ma g.yos so //
NK010(tha)012:1623: thig le nyag gcig gzig gi mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1624: khwa ta nam mkha' lta bur khyab //
NK010(tha)012:1625: rta mgrin rta skad sgra snyan lta bu ste //
NK010(tha)012:1626: rdo rje stong pa'i ngang nyid kyis //
NK010(tha)012:1627: khro bar snang ba gtum mo'o //
NK010(tha)012:1629: pu shud bzang ngan rnam rtog rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1630: don dam nyid las don ma yin //
NK010(tha)012:1631: nyon mongs nye ba'i nyon mongs rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1632: rtog med mkha' dbyings gzhan mi thub //
NK010(tha)012:1633: mi shes rdo rje 'bigs byed mda' //
NK010(tha)012:1634: mtshan ma 'joms par byed snyems ma //
NK010(tha)012:1635: spyang ki'i mgo ni ye sangs rgyas //
NK010(tha)012:1636: rnam rtog phra mor sems byed kyang //
NK010(tha)012:1637: yang dag nyid blta khra yi mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1638: bdud ni bzhi po snang byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:1639: rtsi yis mi shigs klong du thim //
NK010(tha)012:1640: 'khyil ni bde ba chen po'i ngang //
NK010(tha)012:1641: gcig dang du ma dang bral zhing //
NK010(tha)012:1642: rtog med dbyings ni rlung 'byin ma //
NK010(tha)012:1643: nyi ma lta bu'i gzi brjid kyis //
NK010(tha)012:1644: mun pa'i tshogs 'joms seng ge'i mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1645: yod med gnyis las 'das pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:1646: mtha' gnyis bral ba pha wang mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1647: lus ngag yid gsum snang ba yang //
NK010(tha)012:1648: don dam nyid la yod min te //
NK010(tha)012:1651: gzung 'dzin shes pa rtog pa gsod //
NK010(tha)012:1652: pha rol phyin ma yin pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1653: spyod pa barlanga po dom gyi mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1654: gang du mi gnas sre mong mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1655: don dam bden pas sems can gyi //
NK010(tha)012:1656: nyon mongs 'joms byed stobs po che //
NK010(tha)012:1657: rdo rje don dam bden pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1658: dam pa mkha' dbyings klong du bskyod //
NK010(tha)012:1659: bud d+ha bskyed pa'i yum yin la //
NK010(tha)012:1660: ye shes thogs med dred kyi mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1661: log pa'i lam zhugs sum byed cing //
NK010(tha)012:1662: de bzhin nyid gnas byi ba'i mgo //
NK010(tha)012:1664: de ltar yab yum so so'i ye shes kyi sprul pa bcu bcu'ang /
NK010(tha)012:1665: nyon mongs pa za byed stag dang /
NK010(tha)012:1666: shes bya la thogs med du rngam pa gzig dang /
NK010(tha)012:1667: rtsol sgrub zil gyis gnon pa'i byi la dang /
NK010(tha)012:1668: sbyor sgrol dbyings su dag pa'i spyang ki dang /
NK010(tha)012:1669: zhe sdang skyon gyis mi 'jigs pa'i seng ge dang /
NK010(tha)012:1670: khro gtum byams par sbyor ba'i dom ste drug po
NK010(tha)012:1671: ni yab kyi zhe sdang las bskyed cing zhe sdang
NK010(tha)012:1672: gi snyigs ma rus pa mthar rgyas pa'i za byed
NK010(tha)012:1673: mche ba can zhes bya ste /
NK010(tha)012:1674: de kun kyang rgyud kyi gleng gzhi'i dus na pha
NK010(tha)012:1675: ye shes kyi khro bo yin pas lus lhar snang
NK010(tha)012:1676: lam gdug pa byol song gi rigs las mgo bo
NK010(tha)012:1677: de nyid du snang bas phra men ma zhes bya'o
NK010(tha)012:1678: // de bzhin du 'gro don la chags thogs med pa'i bya rgod dang /
NK010(tha)012:1679: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i bya rog dang /
NK010(tha)012:1680: mi shes mun pa la gzigs pa'i 'ug pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1681: sdug bsngal gyi mtshang dbyings su bsnol ba'i khwa ta dang /
NK010(tha)012:1682: 'jab bur thabs shes su 'brel ba'i pu shud dang /
NK010(tha)012:1683: nyon mongs kyi bya gcan 'dul ba'i hor khra dang
NK010(tha)012:1684: drug po ni yum gyi 'dod chags las bskyed pas
NK010(tha)012:1685: 'dod chags kyi snyigs ma khrag mthar rgyas pa'i gsod
NK010(tha)012:1686: byed gshog pa can zhes bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:1687: de bzhin du gtsang sme'i rnam rtog 'joms pa'i dur phag dang /
NK010(tha)012:1688: chos nyid 'pho 'gyur med pa'i g.yag dang /
NK010(tha)012:1689: mtshan ma'i bag chags 'joms pa'i sha ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:1690: 'khor ba'i brlan dang bral ba'i rmigs bu dang /
NK010(tha)012:1691: rnam rtog skye med grol ba'i sre mong dang /
NK010(tha)012:1692: cir yang gzung 'dzin las grol ba'i byi ba dang
NK010(tha)012:1693: drug po ni yab yum gnyis su med pa'i gti
NK010(tha)012:1694: mug gi las bskyed cing gti mug snyigs ma sha
NK010(tha)012:1695: mthar rgyas pa'i bya ba la rmongs pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:1696: byed las kyi sgo nas dur phag ni gsod pa'i mche ba can dang /
NK010(tha)012:1697: sha ba ni nga yir 'dzin pa'i mche ba can dang /
NK010(tha)012:1698: g.yag ni ro la brtag pa'i mche ba can te gsum /
NK010(tha)012:1699: rmigs bu ni rtags 'dzin thob pa'i gshog pa can dang /
NK010(tha)012:1700: sre mong ni dug tsam che ba'i gshog pa can dang /
NK010(tha)012:1701: byi ba ni brku ba la dga' ba'i las kyi gshog pa can te gsum /
NK010(tha)012:1702: dred dang pha wang gnyis ni dug gsum cha mnyam
NK010(tha)012:1703: pas mtha' la mi gnas pa'i brda' ste yak+sha 'bar
NK010(tha)012:1704: ba'i rgyud las / zhe sdang rus pa'i mtha' la mche ba rgyas //
NK010(tha)012:1705: 'dod chags khrag gi mtha' la bya gshog rgyas //
NK010(tha)012:1706: gti mug sha yi mtha' la smra mi shes //
NK010(tha)012:1707: de phyir dug gsum 'joms pa'i dred mo la //
NK010(tha)012:1708: shes bya ma rmongs rtogs pa'i ye shes mnga' //
NK010(tha)012:1709: dug gsum 'joms mdzad gshog rlabs pha wang la //
NK010(tha)012:1710: ma rig mun pa sel ba'i ye shes mnga' //
NK010(tha)012:1712: brten pa'i lha rnams la thun mong du gyur ba'i sgo ma bzhi ni /
NK010(tha)012:1714: snang ba stong pas 'gugs byed ma //
NK010(tha)012:1715: lcags kyus ye shes sa la dgod //
NK010(tha)012:1716: stong pa bco brgyad zhags pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:1717: mi rtog rtog pa 'ching byed ma //
NK010(tha)012:1718: yod dang med pa'i phyogs spangs shing //
NK010(tha)012:1719: snying rje mi phyed lcags sgrog ma //
NK010(tha)012:1720: stong pa nyid kyi sgra bsgrags pas //
NK010(tha)012:1721: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:1722: shes rab pha rol phyin ma nyid //
NK010(tha)012:1723: gzung 'dzin dang bral dril bu ma //
NK010(tha)012:1725: de bzhin du phur pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgra don ni rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK010(tha)012:1726: phur pa'i rang bzhin don bstan pa //
NK010(tha)012:1727: phur ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK010(tha)012:1728: pa ni bla ma chen por bstan //
NK010(tha)012:1729: phur ni chos kyi dbyings zhes bya //
NK010(tha)012:1730: pa ni rig pa'i ye shes yin //
NK010(tha)012:1731: phur ni skye ba med pa'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)012:1732: pa ni 'gags pa med pa'i don //
NK010(tha)012:1733: gnyis su med par phur pa'i ngang //
NK010(tha)012:1734: phur ni thabs kyi rgyal po yin //
NK010(tha)012:1735: pa ni shes rab yum gyi don //
NK010(tha)012:1736: gnyis su med pa rdo rje'i ngang //
NK010(tha)012:1737: phur pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK010(tha)012:1738: phur pa khyab gdal nyi zla 'dra //
NK010(tha)012:1739: kun la snyoms pa'i ngo bor snang //
NK010(tha)012:1740: phur pa chos kyi dbyings nyid yin //
NK010(tha)012:1741: phur pa nam mkha'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK010(tha)012:1742: phur pa sems kyi sems nyid yin //
NK010(tha)012:1743: phur pa rgyud kyi rgyal po yin //
NK010(tha)012:1744: phur pa lung gi man ngag yin //
NK010(tha)012:1745: phur pa man ngag nges pa'i don //
NK010(tha)012:1747: de yan ni nang du 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK010(tha)012:1748: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK010(tha)012:1750: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag gi //
NK010(tha)012:1751: man ngag rnam gnyis stod smad do //
NK010(tha)012:1752: stod la drug ste smad la bcu //
NK010(tha)012:1753: gnyis su shes bya ting nge 'dzin //
NK010(tha)012:1754: smad ni gzas pa po yi las //
NK010(tha)012:1755: zhes stod smad kyi las gnyis su bsdu ba yang /
NK010(tha)012:1756: skabs 'dir dbang gi rtsa ba rnam pa bzhis stod las byang chub bsgrub pa'i don bstan pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1757: phrin las sna tshogs pa'i bdag nyid bsgrub pa dang
NK010(tha)012:1758: 'brel bar smad las drag po sgrol dbang bstan pa
NK010(tha)012:1759: dang / thams cad kyi srog dam tshig gi rang bzhin bstan pa ste gsum du dbye ba'o //
NK010(tha)012:1762: phan dang nus pa'i byin rlabs dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1763: rim pa bzhin du bskur bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:1764: zhes pa'i don stod las byang chub bsgrub pa la
NK010(tha)012:1765: gdeng gsum gces pa'i 'jug sgo ni rtsa ba'i dbang
NK010(tha)012:1766: rnam pa bzhi la ma brten par mi 'grub cing
NK010(tha)012:1767: / bzhi po'ang 'di ltar srog chags rnams la lus
NK010(tha)012:1768: stobs dang mtshungs pa'i theg pa che chung yod pa
NK010(tha)012:1769: ltar gong nas gong du khyad zhugs pa'i tshul sangs
NK010(tha)012:1771: sems can bsam pa'i dbang gis na //
NK010(tha)012:1772: rta dang glang po ma he dang //
NK010(tha)012:1773: rnga mo ri bong khal rnams bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:1774: phan dang nus dang lta dang zhugs //
NK010(tha)012:1775: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1776: gsang ba'i dbang dang thabs kyi dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1777: ji ltar gsungs kyang rnam pa bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:1778: bum pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1779: shes rab ye shes dbang mchog las //
NK010(tha)012:1780: de bzhin bzhi pa'i dbang du gsungs //
NK010(tha)012:1781: zhes phyi phan pa'i dbang dang nang nus pa 'jug
NK010(tha)012:1782: pa'i dbang gnyis ni bum dbang du bsdu ba yin
NK010(tha)012:1784: bum pa'i dbang zhes bya ba la //
NK010(tha)012:1785: bdag po'i dbang dang rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)012:1787: gnyis pa gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes kyi
NK010(tha)012:1788: dbang gnyis ni sbyor ba bzhi'i rang bzhin du blta
NK010(tha)012:1789: bas na lta ba bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:1790: gsang ba'i dbang zhes bya ba la //
NK010(tha)012:1791: lus dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1792: rtsa dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1793: rlung dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:1794: sems dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba yi //
NK010(tha)012:1795: gang yang gang du gzung bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:1796: gsang ba de ni dam pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:1798: de la lus dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba ni dbang
NK010(tha)012:1799: po'i gnas gnyis la so sor sa bon gyi yi
NK010(tha)012:1801: rtsa dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba ni 'khor lo lnga so so'i rtsa 'dab tu /
NK010(tha)012:1802: a ka tsa ta ta pa ya sha /
NK010(tha)012:1803: la sogs pa'i yig 'bru bsgom pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1804: rlung dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba ni yi ge de dag la dmigs nas srog stsol 'gog pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1805: sems dang yig 'bru'i sbyor ba ni rlung sems dbyer med kyi bden pas kun la khyab pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:1806: phan tshun rten dang brten pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK010(tha)012:1807: gsang ba'i dbang de nyid kyang ngag dang sems la
NK010(tha)012:1808: bskur ba gnyis su nang gses bas phyi ma'i dbang
NK010(tha)012:1809: rten gyi sgra las shes rab ye shes kyi dbang
NK010(tha)012:1810: du 'grub ste / shes rab ye shes dbang zhes pa //
NK010(tha)012:1811: shes rab ma yi mtshan nyid de //
NK010(tha)012:1813: 'byung ba bzhi yi mtshan nyid kyis //
NK010(tha)012:1814: bsdu ba rnam bzhi'i don dang mthun //
NK010(tha)012:1816: de ltar gsang dbang gnyis po'i rkyen las byung ba'i
NK010(tha)012:1817: dpe'i ye shes la brten nas don dam lhan cig
NK010(tha)012:1818: skyes pa'i ye shes slob ma'i rgyud la yang dag
NK010(tha)012:1819: par zhugs pas na zhugs pa zhes bya ste thabs
NK010(tha)012:1820: la brten nas 'byung bas na thabs kyi dbang zhes
NK010(tha)012:1821: bshad pa yin par bdag nyid kho nas rig pa
NK010(tha)012:1822: yin no // de yang dmangs rigs ni spyod pa barlanga zhing dngos snang la bden 'dzin che bas /
NK010(tha)012:1823: de dag pa'i snod bcud kyis ldog pa'i ched du bum pa'i dbang dang /
NK010(tha)012:1824: bram ze ni rang gi gsang tshig bsrung ba sogs
NK010(tha)012:1825: sangs rgya ba'i dgos pa med pa'i spyod pa gzo
NK010(tha)012:1826: ba kho na chos su sems pas de theg pa
NK010(tha)012:1827: chen po blang dor med pa'i chos kyis ldog pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1828: ched du gsang ba'i dbang dang /
NK010(tha)012:1829: rje'u rigs ni 'dod yon la gdung zhing sems kyi
NK010(tha)012:1830: rtog dpyod rno bas de thabs kyis lam du slong
NK010(tha)012:1831: ba la slob pa'i phyir sher dbang dang /
NK010(tha)012:1832: rgyal rigs ni 'byor pas snyems shing thams cad zil
NK010(tha)012:1833: gyis gnon pa la dga' bas rang nyid la mchog
NK010(tha)012:1834: tu 'dzin pa de mnyam pa nyid la gnas pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1835: brtul zhugs chen po'i shes rab ye shes kyis ldog
NK010(tha)012:1836: pa'i phyir dbang bzhi pa bstan par rig par bya
NK010(tha)012:1838: dang po dbang gi bskur sa ni //
NK010(tha)012:1839: sems can rtog pa ldog pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:1840: dmangs kyi rigs la bum pa bzhag /
NK010(tha)012:1841: bram ze'i rigs la gsang dbang ste //
NK010(tha)012:1842: rje yi rigs la shes rab dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1843: de bzhin rgyal po bzhi pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1844: rim pa de bzhin shes par bya //
NK010(tha)012:1846: yan lag lus ni shan pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:1847: d+r+wa ba can la bum pa sbyin //
NK010(tha)012:1848: ngag gi las ni bram ze ste //
NK010(tha)012:1849: 'jig rten can la gsang ba sbyin //
NK010(tha)012:1850: sems kyi las ni rje'u ste //
NK010(tha)012:1851: lhan cig skyes la shes rab dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1852: yon tan phrin las rgyal po ste //
NK010(tha)012:1853: kun ka tshogs la bzhi pa bskur //
NK010(tha)012:1855: de ltar dbang rnam pa bzhi las dang po phyi
NK010(tha)012:1856: dkyil drang don gyi bskyed rim rnams nyan du rung
NK010(tha)012:1857: ba'i skal pa ster byed phyi phan pa'i dbang lnga
NK010(tha)012:1859: bum pa rdo rje dril bu dang //
NK010(tha)012:1860: thod pa rdo rje ming du grags //
NK010(tha)012:1862: bskur tshul yang dbang rdzas gzhan lag las mi brgyud de rdo rje 'bar ba las /
NK010(tha)012:1863: dbang bskur ba yi rim pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:1864: sbyin sreg las rnams byed don du //
NK010(tha)012:1865: dkyil 'khor gyi ni yo byad rnams //
NK010(tha)012:1866: slob dpon gyis ni khyer bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:1867: slob mas khyer na dam tshig nyams //
NK010(tha)012:1869: de la dang po rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i chu dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1870: rnam bum spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)012:1873: gsang gsum dam tshig las byung ba //
NK010(tha)012:1874: yab yum gnyis med bde chen las //
NK010(tha)012:1875: byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun 'dis //
NK010(tha)012:1876: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1877: +amo bo d+hi tsit+ta +aa dar sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1878: rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i
NK010(tha)012:1879: ngo bo bum pa'i chus dbang bskur zhing nye reg
NK010(tha)012:1880: byas pas lus kyi sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)012:1881: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i dbang thob /
NK010(tha)012:1882: gzugs kyi phung po rdo rje mi bskyod pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:1883: chu'i khams m+aa ma k+ai'i rang bzhin du gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)012:1884: zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)012:1885: sangs rgyas rdo rje rigs kyi sku rnam pa thams
NK010(tha)012:1886: cad kyi bdag nyid 'gyur ba med pa thob nas
NK010(tha)012:1889: de nas rin 'byung dbu rgyan gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1890: dbang 'di thob nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rgyal
NK010(tha)012:1891: thabs la dbang bas na rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan la
NK010(tha)012:1892: thob pa'i lnga'i sgra chags pa ste /
NK010(tha)012:1893: de nyid mgo la bkon nas /
NK010(tha)012:1895: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid che //
NK010(tha)012:1896: thob pa lnga yi dbang bskur ba //
NK010(tha)012:1897: rin chen rigs kyi dbang bskur mchog /
NK010(tha)012:1898: rin chen khrag 'thung brtan gyur cig /
NK010(tha)012:1899: sa man+ta rat+na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1900: rigs kyi bu khyod la dbu rgyan 'di bkon pa tsam gyis /
NK010(tha)012:1901: sgo gsum gyi rmongs pa'i sgrib pa dag /
NK010(tha)012:1902: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yon tan gyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)012:1903: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK010(tha)012:1904: sa'i khams sangs rgyas spyan mar gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)012:1905: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)012:1906: sangs rgyas rin chen rigs kyi yon tan thams cad mkhyen nas 'gro ba'i don byed par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1907: snang mtha' rdo rje'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1908: ah sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1909: rdo rje gsung gi don mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:1911: rdo rje chos kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1913: pra ta pra we sha dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1914: rigs kyi bu khyod la snang ba mtha' yas kyi rang bzhin rdo rjes dbang bskur bas /
NK010(tha)012:1916: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung gi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)012:1917: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK010(tha)012:1918: me'i khams gos dkar mor gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)012:1919: 'dod chags so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)012:1920: sangs rgyas pad+ma'i rigs kyi gsung 'gag pa med pa
NK010(tha)012:1921: chos kyi sgra dbyangs thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed
NK010(tha)012:1922: par 'gyur ro // don yod grub pa dril bu'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1924: mkha' 'gro kun gyi dril bu'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:1925: rtog med chos kyi sgra 'byin zhing //
NK010(tha)012:1926: las kyi khrag 'thung phrin las bdag /
NK010(tha)012:1927: shes rab dril bu'i dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1928: krit+ya a nush+th+aa na badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1929: rigs kyi bu khyod la dril bu 'di gtad pa
NK010(tha)012:1930: tsam gyis nyon mongs pa bag la nyal gyi sgrib
NK010(tha)012:1931: pa dag / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phrin las kyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)012:1932: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub pa dang rlung gi khams dam tshig sgrol mar gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)012:1933: phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su grol te 'gro ba'i don byed par 'gyur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1934: rnam par snang mdzad ming gi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1936: sngar gyi gsang ming dkyil 'khor pa'i lha tshogs rnams kyis 'ur dir bsgrags par bsams nas /
NK010(tha)012:1938: rdo rje ming gi chos nyid de //
NK010(tha)012:1939: ces kyang mi tshugs mi shigs te //
NK010(tha)012:1940: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:1941: rdo rje ming du dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:1942: d+harma d+h+aa tu bi sho d+ha badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1943: rigs kyi bu khyod la rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK010(tha)012:1944: ngo bo ming che ge mo btags pa tsam gyis
NK010(tha)012:1946: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi dbang thob /
NK010(tha)012:1947: rnam par shes pa'i phung po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK010(tha)012:1948: nam mkha'i khams chos kyi dbyings phyug mar gnas gyur /
NK010(tha)012:1949: gti mug chos dbyings ye shes su grol te /
NK010(tha)012:1950: sangs rgyas de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rnam par mi rtog pa thob nas /
NK010(tha)012:1952: de ltar rig dbang lnga thob pa'i bral thob ni /
NK010(tha)012:1954: sangs rgyas lngar ni rnam dag pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:1955: dbang bskur lnga thob rgyud pas ni /
NK010(tha)012:1956: ma rig pa dang bral bas na //
NK010(tha)012:1957: ye shes lnga ni thob par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:1959: de nas rig dbang lnga'i mtha' rten du snang zhen
NK010(tha)012:1960: lha skur rdzogs byed rnam rgyal bum pa'i dbang ni
NK010(tha)012:1961: bum pa spyi bor bzung la /
NK010(tha)012:1964: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK010(tha)012:1966: g.yon nas yum gyis yab la 'khyud //
NK010(tha)012:1967: phyag gis bum pa rab tu blangs //
NK010(tha)012:1968: ye shes dbang gi chu bo 'di //
NK010(tha)012:1969: nyon mongs ma gos dkar la 'tsher //
NK010(tha)012:1970: skal ldan rigs kyi bu khyod la //
NK010(tha)012:1971: spyi bor bum pas dbang bskur bas //
NK010(tha)012:1972: nyon mongs gsum dang dug gsum sbyongs //
NK010(tha)012:1973: dbang gi chu bo rgyun bzhin 'bab //
NK010(tha)012:1974: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1975: d+aip+ta tsakra ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK010(tha)012:1976: ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK010(tha)012:1978: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:1979: gtso bo'i sku spyi bor bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:1981: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NK010(tha)012:1982: thugs rjes khams gsum gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:1983: gnyen pos las su rung mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:1984: 'jigs byed gnyen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:1985: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1986: k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1987: dar le brgan la sngags byang bris pa mgrin par bzung la /
NK010(tha)012:1989: gsung gi rang bzhin mtshon byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:1990: le brgan 'bar ba'i kha dog la //
NK010(tha)012:1991: snying po nus pa'i don dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:1992: nus pa can gyi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:1993: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:1994: wa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:1995: phur pa snying gar bzhag la /
NK010(tha)012:1997: tsit+ta smug po'i gzhal yas nas //
NK010(tha)012:1998: khams gsum dbang gi bdag po ste //
NK010(tha)012:1999: brkyang bskum rab tu gdengs pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2001: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:2003: yon tan dang phrin las gnyis ka'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:2004: ye shes sems dpa'i tsakli snying gar gtad la /
NK010(tha)012:2006: thugs ka rin chen zur brgyad las //
NK010(tha)012:2007: phrin las sna tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NK010(tha)012:2008: thams cad kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK010(tha)012:2009: ye shes sems dpa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2010: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:2011: gu na karma a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2012: de nas dur khrod chas brgyad kyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:2014: zhing chen g.yang gzhis 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod //
NK010(tha)012:2015: glang chen ko rlon thugs rje stobs kyi bdag /
NK010(tha)012:2016: stag sham yon tan phrin las rgyas pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2017: bdud chas dpa' bo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2019: thod pa skam po chos kyi sku yi rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2020: thod pa rnying pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2021: thod pa tshal bu sprul pa sku yi rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2022: sku gsum tshon byed thod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2024: rigs bzhi klu rnams ma lus 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2025: gdug pa sbrul ni rigs bzhis sku la brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:2026: zhe sdang chen po gnas su 'joms mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2027: gdug pa chas kyi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2029: zhag gi zo ris dam rdzas bcud kyi rgyan //
NK010(tha)012:2030: thal chen tshom bu 'khor ba 'joms pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2031: rak+ta'i thig le thugs rje chags pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2032: mtshan ma rnam pa gsum gyi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2035: rang byung rgyal po lha yi rgyan //
NK010(tha)012:2036: mdzes pas rab tu brgyan pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:2037: lha la rab tu mdzes pas brgyan //
NK010(tha)012:2038: dbu rgyan cod pan dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2040: ye shes me dpung 'khor ba bsreg pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2041: ye shes me ri ljang ser dmar ba'i 'od //
NK010(tha)012:2042: mdor na ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:2043: dug lnga bsreg pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2045: kham nag ral pa kun gyi rgyan du bcings //
NK010(tha)012:2046: srid pa'i rtse mo zil gyis gnod pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2047: gti mug chen po rtsad nas bcad nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:2048: dbu skra ral pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2050: tshon gang sku yi ba spu'i bu ga rnams //
NK010(tha)012:2051: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)012:2052: rdo rje phur pa rab tu k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:2053: gdug pa 'joms pa'i lha rnams dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2055: ye shes rdo rje rab tu 'bar ba yi //
NK010(tha)012:2056: rdo rje'i gshog pas khams gsum zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)012:2057: gdug byed rang bzhin med par gnon mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2058: rdo rje'i gshog pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2060: rdo rje thod khrag rab tu gsol ba yis //
NK010(tha)012:2061: khams gsum chags pa rab tu zhi bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:2062: 'dod chags rtsad nas gcod byed thod pa'i khrag /
NK010(tha)012:2063: rak+ta chen po'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2065: cod pan rab tu 'phur byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2066: lha mo lnga dang ldan pa'i mchod pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2067: mchod pa rgya cher mchod pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2068: de nas phyag mtshan gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:2070: rnam thar dgu dang rab ldan pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2071: theg pa dgu yi sgo gnas nas //
NK010(tha)012:2072: khyad par chen po ngan song 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:2073: sa dgu gnon pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2075: ye shes lnga dang rab ldan pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2076: rdo rje rtse lnga ye shes lnga //
NK010(tha)012:2078: dug lnga 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2080: ye shes me dpung 'bar ba ste //
NK010(tha)012:2081: thugs mchog rab tu 'bar ba'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:2082: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad bsreg /
NK010(tha)012:2083: nyon mongs sreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2085: mtshon gyi rgyal pos r+au tra sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:2086: sku gsum lhun grub rtse mos mtshon //
NK010(tha)012:2087: ngan song gsum po rtag tu sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:2088: dug gsum rtsad gcod dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2090: thugs rje'i phur pas gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:2091: bgegs kyi rgyal po sgrol mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2092: 'khor bo tshar gcod dbyings su sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:2093: gdug pa 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2094: gnyis pa nang nus pa 'jug pa'i dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:2096: nus pa bskyed par byed pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2097: rdo rje nang gi dbang lnga ste //
NK010(tha)012:2098: thos sgom smra byed phrin las dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2099: zhes pas skye mched rnams he ru ka lnga'i rang bzhin du byin gyis barloba pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:2100: rin chen khrag 'thung gi sa bon rna bar bskur
NK010(tha)012:2101: la gsal 'phro bstim gsum gyi dmigs pa'i bye brag
NK010(tha)012:2103: nyan byed rna ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)012:2104: gsal ba rin chen ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:2105: sa yi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK010(tha)012:2108: dbang de bskur zhing smin pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:2109: gsang ba'i dbang mchog dam pa las //
NK010(tha)012:2110: gsang ba gzhan las bsnyen par bya //
NK010(tha)012:2111: gsang ba'i don nyid rtogs bya zhing //
NK010(tha)012:2112: gsang ba gzhan du smra mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:2113: zhes dam tshig bstan pa ni kun la 'agre'o //
NK010(tha)012:2114: rdo rje khrag 'thung gi sa bon snying gar bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2116: bsam byed snying gi gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)012:2117: gsang ba rdo rje'i ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:2118: yi ge phreng ba'i tshogs mchog las //
NK010(tha)012:2121: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK010(tha)012:2122: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje gdan //
NK010(tha)012:2123: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod las //
NK010(tha)012:2124: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK010(tha)012:2125: pad+ma khrag 'thung gi sa bon lce la bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2126: +aah smra byed lce yi gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)012:2127: gsal ba a yi ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:2128: a yi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK010(tha)012:2130: +aah a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah chos kyi bdud rtsi bla na med //
NK010(tha)012:2131: dad ldan skyes bu ngom par byos //
NK010(tha)012:2132: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK010(tha)012:2133: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK010(tha)012:2134: don grub kyi sa bon lag mthil gnyis su bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2136: lag mthil gnyis kyi gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)012:2137: gsal ba rgya gram ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:2138: t+wa yi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK010(tha)012:2141: khyod ni rdo rje las yin pas //
NK010(tha)012:2142: las rnams ma lus kun gyis shig /
NK010(tha)012:2144: khyod kyi dgos pa byed par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2145: rnam snang gi sa bon spyi bor bskur te /
NK010(tha)012:2147: bskyod chen yan lag gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)012:2148: gsal ba +amo gyi ngo bo nyid //
NK010(tha)012:2150: rigs lnga khrag 'thung sku ru gsal //
NK010(tha)012:2152: phyogs bcu dus gsum thams cad kyi //
NK010(tha)012:2153: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK010(tha)012:2154: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa khyod //
NK010(tha)012:2156: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:2157: phur pa phrin las kyi rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:2158: ming dang chu dang dam tshig gsum //
NK010(tha)012:2159: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya dang //
NK010(tha)012:2160: rdo rje brtul zhugs skyabs sbyin gyi //
NK010(tha)012:2161: slob dpon dbang ni rab tu sbyin //
NK010(tha)012:2162: ngan song gnas ni dbang gis 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:2163: zhes pas dang po gnyis ni rigs dbang lnga'i khongs su ldan la /
NK010(tha)012:2164: dam tshig gsum la sogs pa'i tshul slob ma gtso
NK010(tha)012:2165: bo yab yum gyi nga rgyal la gnas pa la
NK010(tha)012:2166: / thugs kyi dam tshig rdo rje gsor ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:2167: gsung gi dam tshig dril bu 'khrol ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:2168: sku'i dam tshig thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i tshul
NK010(tha)012:2169: du bsnol nas 'khyud rgya byed pa ste dam tshig
NK010(tha)012:2170: gsum byin zhing / rgyal tshab tu 'os pa'i slob
NK010(tha)012:2171: bu yin na khri la bzhag ste 'khor lo dang
NK010(tha)012:2172: gsum byin zhing / / po ti dang /
NK010(tha)012:2176: thabs kyi spyod pas gzhan don du //
NK010(tha)012:2177: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)012:2178: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2179: dbang dang byin rlabs 'dir stsal to //
NK010(tha)012:2180: +amo bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya s+t+wam a b+hi
NK010(tha)012:2181: shiny+tsa +aah rigs kyi bu khyod la rdo rje dang
NK010(tha)012:2182: dril bu 'di gtad cing dam tshig gsum byin nas
NK010(tha)012:2183: rdo rje slob dpon du dbang bskur nas /
NK010(tha)012:2184: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bdag nyid pha rol
NK010(tha)012:2185: tu phyin pa drug gi rang bzhin sngags kyi lta
NK010(tha)012:2186: spyod zab mo'i thabs shes zung 'brel du rdzogs nas
NK010(tha)012:2187: 'khor ba ma spangs rang bzhin med par dag /
NK010(tha)012:2188: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pas 'gro ba'i don dpag
NK010(tha)012:2189: tu med par byed pa'i rten 'brel 'grigs pa yin
NK010(tha)012:2191: de ltar rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang bskur nas
NK010(tha)012:2192: slob mas kyang slob dpon gyi go 'phang brnyes par
NK010(tha)012:2193: bya ste / rdo rje 'bar ba las /
NK010(tha)012:2194: dbang bskur gnang ba thob nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:2195: nyan dang bsam pa la sogs pas //
NK010(tha)012:2196: bla ma'i rgyud la gnas pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:2197: sbyangs shing rtogs par ma byas na //
NK010(tha)012:2198: gcer bu lag pa stong par 'gro //
NK010(tha)012:2202: dbang bskur yi dam lhar bskyed la //
NK010(tha)012:2203: lus kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bya //
NK010(tha)012:2204: zhes pas slob ma'i lus kyi dngos por 'dzin pa
NK010(tha)012:2205: dag pa'i phyir lha dbang bskur ba'i tshul k+ai la
NK010(tha)012:2206: ya gsang ba'i dgongs rgyud las ji ltar bstan pa
NK010(tha)012:2207: nyid dbang bskur zab mo'i dag bya dag 'bras las
NK010(tha)012:2208: yin lugs kyi don la sbyor ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor
NK010(tha)012:2209: gyi bdag po'i thugs ka nas chu la chu bur
NK010(tha)012:2210: rdol ba bzhin byung ba'i lha tshogs rnams gnas so
NK010(tha)012:2211: sor thim pa'i mos pa mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:2213: spyi bor gtso bo'i sku bzhag la /
NK010(tha)012:2214: dngos por 'dzin pa gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2215: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nus dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2216: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata d+aip+ta tsakra
NK010(tha)012:2217: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK010(tha)012:2218: m+aam / sras mchog yab yum bcu yi sku ston cing //
NK010(tha)012:2219: gzugs kyi phung po gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2220: nam mkha'i rtsa la bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:2221: +amo bud+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya he ru ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2222: rnam shes phung po gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2223: sa yi rtsa la badz+ra he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:2224: +amo badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya he ru ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2225: tshor ba'i phung po gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2226: chu yi rtsa la rat+na he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:2227: +amo rat+na k+ai li k+ai la ya he ru ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2228: 'du shes phung po gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2229: me yi rtsa la pad+ma he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:2230: +amo pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya he ru ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2231: 'du byed phung po gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2232: rlung gi rtsa la karma he ru ka /
NK010(tha)012:2233: +amo karma k+ai li k+ai la ya he ru ka a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2234: 'byung ba lnga ni rgyal ba yum lnga'i mkha' //
NK010(tha)012:2235: sras mchog rigs lnga yab yum dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2236: khro bo bcu'i sku gnas so sor bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2238: zhe sdang gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2239: rna ba'i gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2240: khro bo rnam par rgyal bas dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2241: +amo badz+ra kro ta bi dza ya h'u badz+ra kro d+hi l+aa se ke h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2242: nga rgyal gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2243: dpung g.yas gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2244: khro bo gshin rje gshed pos dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2245: +amo badz+ra kro ta ya m+aan+ta ka h'u badz+ra kro ti s+t+wam b+ha ni h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2246: 'dod chags gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2247: mtshan ma'i gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2248: khro bo rta mgrin rgyal pos dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2249: +amo badz+ra kro ta h+ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu
NK010(tha)012:2250: lu h'u badz+ra kro d+h+ai tsan d+ha re ye ti
NK010(tha)012:2252: phrag dog gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2253: mig 'bras gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2254: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil pas dbang bsgyur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2255: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+da li h+aum badz+ra
NK010(tha)012:2256: kro d+hi ba yi ba ti h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK010(tha)012:2257: m+aam / gti mug gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2258: lte ba'i gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2259: khro bo stobs po che yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2260: +amo badz+ra kro ta ma h+aa ba la h'u badz+ra
NK010(tha)012:2261: kro d+hi tsun ta mu ne h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK010(tha)012:2262: m+aam / rdzun du smra ba gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2263: lce yi gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2264: khro bo dbyug pa sngon pos dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2265: +amo badz+ra kro ta n+ai la dan+da h'u badz+ra kro d+hi ti ru h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2266: srog gcod gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2267: dpung g.yon gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2268: khro bo mi g.yo mgon pos dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2269: +amo badz+ra kro ta +aar+ya a tsa la h'u badz+ra
NK010(tha)012:2270: kro d+hi mu kha la h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam
NK010(tha)012:2271: / ma byin len pa gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2272: rkang g.yas gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2273: khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2274: +amo badz+ra kro ta a pa r+aa dzi ta h'u
NK010(tha)012:2275: badz+ra kro d+hi sha bya ya h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK010(tha)012:2276: m+aam / gnod sems gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2277: rkang g.yon gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2278: khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2279: +amo badz+ra kro ta tree lokya bi dza ya h'u
NK010(tha)012:2280: badz+ra kro d+hi m+aa ra na h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa
NK010(tha)012:2281: m+aam / log par lta ba gnas su dag pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2282: mig g.yon gnad kyi rtsa la ni //
NK010(tha)012:2283: khro bo h'u k+aa ra yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2284: +amo badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra badz+ra kro d+hi
NK010(tha)012:2285: tsi na d+ha ya ti h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam
NK010(tha)012:2286: / de ltar bdag nyid rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK010(tha)012:2287: rol pa las mtshan ma rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK010(tha)012:2288: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang thob pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2289: / yon tan ni / bshad pa'i rgyud chen po las /
NK010(tha)012:2290: gtso bo nyid kyi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2292: h'u mdzad chen po'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2293: thog dang ser ba'i las rnams 'grub //
NK010(tha)012:2294: rnam par rgyal ba'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2296: dbyug sngon can gyi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2297: nyon mongs me ni bsreg par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2298: gshin rje gshed pa'i dbang bskur na //
NK010(tha)012:2299: sgrol ba chen po'i dbang yang thob //
NK010(tha)012:2300: mi g.yo mgon po'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2301: zhe sdang rang rgyud non par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2302: rta mgrin rgyal po'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2303: khams gsum dbang du sdud par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2304: gzhan gyis mi thub dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2305: nyon mongs sha mdangs phyed par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2306: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2307: khams gsum gdug pa gsod par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2308: khams gsum rnam rgyal dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2310: stobs po che yi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2312: sras mchog drug gi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2314: dur khrod rdzas kyi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2316: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2318: rdo rje phur pa'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2320: bkra shis dam pa'i rdzas la brten //
NK010(tha)012:2321: dam pa de nyid thob gyur na //
NK010(tha)012:2322: legs pa'i yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK010(tha)012:2323: rdo rje tshe yi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2324: tshe yi rdo rje nyid du 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2325: longs spyod gter gyi dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:2326: zad med 'phel ba'i dbang dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2327: dbang la yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK010(tha)012:2328: dbang rnams rdzogs par ma gyur na //
NK010(tha)012:2330: dbang rnams thob par ma gyur na //
NK010(tha)012:2331: nyi khri chig stong ston nus kyang //
NK010(tha)012:2332: rgyal po dmungs su bab pa 'dra //
NK010(tha)012:2334: de phyir dbang la nan tan bya //
NK010(tha)012:2336: de nas phra phyag so so'i tsakli spyi bor bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2337: btang snyoms byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2338: phra men phag gi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2339: badz+ra su ka ra mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2340: g.yo sgyu byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2341: phra men smig bu'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2342: badz+ra ka sha mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2343: dpa' rtsal byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2344: phra men stag gi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2345: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2346: thogs med byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2347: phra men bya rgod mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2348: badz+ra grid d+ha mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2349: gzi brjid byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2350: phra men g.yag gi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2351: badz+ra tsa ma ra mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2352: rang rig byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2353: phra men bya rog mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2354: badz+ra k+aa ka mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2355: gtsang ma srod byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2356: phra men sha ba'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2357: badz+ra ha ra mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2358: phra la gting zab byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2359: phra men 'ug pa'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2360: badz+ra hu lu mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2361: 'khor ba rngam byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2362: phra men gzig gi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2363: badz+ra b+y+aa gri mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2364: mi 'chor 'joms byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2365: phra men khwa yi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2366: badz+ra ba ya ti mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2367: gze myur 'joms byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2368: phra men byi la'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2369: badz+ra pa tsa la mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2370: thabs mkhas rdzu 'phrul byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2371: phra men pu shud mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2372: badz+ra bag shi mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2373: rngam mgyogs gsod byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2374: phra men spyang ki'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2375: badz+ra sh+aa na mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2376: 'dzin cing mgyogs byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2377: phra men khra yi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2378: badz+ra tsan d+ha mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2379: gnyen po gzhal med byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2380: phra men seng ge'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2381: badz+ra sing ha mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2382: shes rab thabs mkhas byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2383: phra men pha wang mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2384: badz+ra ti t+ai la mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2385: gtum shing gdug pa byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2386: phra men don gyi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2387: badz+ra dag shi mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2388: mgyogs shing gze ba'i byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2389: phra men sre mong mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2390: badz+ra na ku la mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2391: rtsol chen thogs men byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2392: phra men dred kyi mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2393: badz+ra rig sha mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2394: bskungs mkhas sgrol byed byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2395: phra men byi ba'i mgo can dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2396: badz+ra dung kam shi mu khadz+dza a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2397: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi so sor bskur la /
NK010(tha)012:2398: snying rje byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2399: lag g.yas lcags kyu ma yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2400: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzaha b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2401: byams pa byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2402: lag g.yon zhags pa ma yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2403: badz+ra p+aa sha h'u a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2404: dga' ba byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2405: rkang g.yon lcags sgrog ma yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2406: badz+ra s+pho ta bam a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2407: btang snyoms byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2408: rkang g.yas dril bu ma yis dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2409: badz+ra g+han+de hoha b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2411: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'dzin pa las //
NK010(tha)012:2412: lus 'di ye nas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK010(tha)012:2413: ye nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK010(tha)012:2414: bskyed kyang mi dgos rang bzhin gnas //
NK010(tha)012:2415: zhes dag pa brjod la rol mos byin dbab par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:2416: de nas phur srung dam can ma mo bcu gnyis
NK010(tha)012:2417: ming po dang bcas pa'i dbang ni shin tu gnyan
NK010(tha)012:2418: pas snod dang sbyar te bskur bar bya ba ni
NK010(tha)012:2420: 'jig rten khams rnams dbang du sdud pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:2421: lcags kyi spyang mos khams gsum dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)012:2422: mngags pa'i pho nya'i tshul te rngams pa'i mdangs //
NK010(tha)012:2423: dbang sdud dam can dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2425: khyi mo ral pa khams gsum dngangs pa'i bdag /
NK010(tha)012:2426: khams gsum zas su za ba'i rkan sgra can //
NK010(tha)012:2427: srid gsum skom du 'thung ba'i hub sgra can //
NK010(tha)012:2428: dam can mkha' 'gro'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2430: 'phar ba lce brgyad snang srid sil bur 'don //
NK010(tha)012:2431: khams gsum kun tu phyogs bzhi'i dmag dpung 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:2432: nga ro chen po phyogs bcu kun tu sgrogs //
NK010(tha)012:2433: mkha' 'gro dgyes pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2435: zangs kyi wa mos snang srid gdug pa 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:2436: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil ba'i dbang mo che //
NK010(tha)012:2437: tsit+ta don snying za ba'i rkan sgra can //
NK010(tha)012:2438: dbang sdud mkha' 'gro'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2439: dz+wa la dz+wa la badz+ra ma ma muk+ta la ye
NK010(tha)012:2440: dza pa du man d+hi shwa ri ni la pu
NK010(tha)012:2441: tsi h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2443: khams gsum nad kyi bdag mor dbang bsgyur ma //
NK010(tha)012:2444: 'jig rten khams kun khyab pa'i bya ma rta //
NK010(tha)012:2445: mi phyug kun la mnga' mdzad dbang mo che //
NK010(tha)012:2446: gdug pa ma mo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2448: dus gsum kun tu rgyas pa'i sku brnyes pa //
NK010(tha)012:2449: bstan pa rgyas pa'i slad du phrin las mdzad //
NK010(tha)012:2450: ser nag chen mo khams gsum kun gyi bdag /
NK010(tha)012:2451: mkha' 'gro dbang sdud dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2453: las su sha khrag ro la rngam pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:2454: khrag 'thung dmar nag srid gsum dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)012:2455: stong khams dge sdig bya ra byed pa'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:2456: dad pa stobs ldan mkha' 'gro'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2458: phrin las sna tshogs mthar phyin grub pa mo //
NK010(tha)012:2459: rgya mtsho'i gting gi klu rnams 'khrug byed ma //
NK010(tha)012:2460: ljang nag chen mo phrin las mthar phyin ma //
NK010(tha)012:2461: mkha' 'gro mthu yi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2462: ma tha ma tha badz+ra trag rak+sha ma ti he
NK010(tha)012:2463: dun b+h+yo ma h+aa k+aa la yak+sha nag mo he
NK010(tha)012:2464: dun b+h+yo a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2466: bdud kyi rigs rnams dbang du sdud mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)012:2467: mthing nag bdud kyi chas su rab tu zhugs //
NK010(tha)012:2468: khams gsum bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dbang mo che //
NK010(tha)012:2469: gdug pa bdud 'dul dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2471: 'jig rten gnod byed rab tu 'dul mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)012:2472: ser bas rgyal ba'i rang bzhin mtshon mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2473: ki kang las kyi bskal par 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2474: mkha' 'gro mthu byin dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2476: khams gsum gang 'dul dbang gi bdag mo ste //
NK010(tha)012:2477: rak+sha srin po za byed dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)012:2478: dpal gyi bka' nyan khrag gi dri snom ma //
NK010(tha)012:2479: dbang phyug chen mo'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2481: gdug pa klu rnams rab tu 'dul mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)012:2482: nad ngan phrin las dbang gi bdag mo ste //
NK010(tha)012:2483: klu la mnga' mdzad nad kyi bdag mo yang //
NK010(tha)012:2484: las rnams mthar phyin dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:2485: ka tang ka te dza ye bi dza ye a
NK010(tha)012:2486: dzi te a pa ra tsi te su ki b+ha
NK010(tha)012:2487: ya b+ha ra tsit+tam yo gi shwa ri ya ma
NK010(tha)012:2488: tsit+ta h'u phata a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK010(tha)012:2490: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba'i las mdzad ma //
NK010(tha)012:2491: grangs dang ldan pa ma nor rim par ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2492: rnam bzhi rtog pa'i khyad par ston mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2493: yang dag don dang ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2494: rnal 'byor chen po las ming po gsum las ma bshad pa ltar /
NK010(tha)012:2496: ma h+aa k+aa la mdog nag ste //
NK010(tha)012:2497: be con phur bu rgyan dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:2498: rgyal po dkar po king kar phur //
NK010(tha)012:2499: bse yi skyes bu bswe khrab gsol //
NK010(tha)012:2500: dmar po 'jigs pa phyag gnyis na //
NK010(tha)012:2501: se mda' se gzhu phur pa 'dril //
NK010(tha)012:2502: ming po gsum gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK010(tha)012:2503: k+aa la ma tram ma h+aa k+aa la ra ti ye k+aa la r+au pa h'u phata /
NK010(tha)012:2504: k+aa ra m+aa k+aa r+aa ya tri tsa pa la tri la thun /
NK010(tha)012:2505: ma ra sa ni ra sha ni ra sha b+hi
NK010(tha)012:2506: ku lan shu lan h'u phata a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u
NK010(tha)012:2507: / de ltar bum pa'i dbang bskur bas bskyed rim sgom pa'i snod du gyur /
NK010(tha)012:2509: lus rags pa bzhin lag gi rnam pa tha mal du 'dzin pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:2510: phra ba rtsa'i rnam grangs tha dad pa sbyangs pas sku rdo rje'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:2511: lam bskyed pa'i rim pa dang dga' ba'i ye shes
NK010(tha)012:2512: la brten nas bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyis non
NK010(tha)012:2513: / sprul pa'i sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin te /
NK010(tha)012:2515: slob ma'i lus ni dag cing smin //
NK010(tha)012:2516: rdo rje'i lus ni rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:2517: de ni bum pa'i dbang yin te //
NK010(tha)012:2518: lha yi sku yi rnam dag pa //
NK010(tha)012:2519: myur du thob te the tshom med //
NK010(tha)012:2521: gnyis pa gsang dbang ni rdo rje slob dpon lus kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur ba yin te /
NK010(tha)012:2523: rdo rje slob dpon dpa' bo che //
NK010(tha)012:2524: yab yum bde ba sbyor ba'i sgras //
NK010(tha)012:2525: byang sems dkar dmar thig le'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2526: zhes pas gsung rdo rje'i rang bzhin ni gsang dbang gi ngo bo yin la /
NK010(tha)012:2527: byang chub kyi sems de nyid slob ma'i dag bya'i
NK010(tha)012:2528: rtsa ba ngag gi rang bzhin rlung la 'dres par
NK010(tha)012:2529: bya ba'i slad du bde stong gnyis su med pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2530: 'dod chags rjes su chags pa'i mes bzhu ba'i tshul
NK010(tha)012:2532: rdo rje theg pa la mos pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2533: bu mo mtshan bzang ldan pa btsal //
NK010(tha)012:2534: thabs kyi rdo rje gzhon nu ste //
NK010(tha)012:2535: de nyid shes rab bde ba'i yum //
NK010(tha)012:2537: bde ba thugs kyi thig le spro //
NK010(tha)012:2538: zag med nyi zla'i snying po de //
NK010(tha)012:2539: slob ma'i ngag la yang dag sbyin //
NK010(tha)012:2540: zhes pas mkha' gsang dngos gnas ma yin par rnam
NK010(tha)012:2541: pa dang sa bon gyi rang bzhin du rlob pa
NK010(tha)012:2542: dang / brda' dang brda' len gyis rjes chags bskul
NK010(tha)012:2543: te 'du shes gsum ldan gyi snyoms par zhugs pa
NK010(tha)012:2544: sogs sher dbang ltar shes par byas nas mas brtan
NK010(tha)012:2545: gyi rten 'brel lugs las ldog pa de nyid skal
NK010(tha)012:2546: med dang nyan thos kyi theg pa can gyis mthong
NK010(tha)012:2547: dang / ba lta ci / thos su yang mi
NK010(tha)012:2548: rung bas gsang zhes bya ba'i sgra zhugs la de
NK010(tha)012:2549: nyid slob bu'i lce thog tu byin pa ni dbang
NK010(tha)012:2550: dang / ba lta ci / ste / de'ang dngos
NK010(tha)012:2551: 'dzin dag pa'i slob mas rdo rje nor bu'i rtse
NK010(tha)012:2552: nas myong ba thabs bde ba chen po'i gsang dbang
NK010(tha)012:2553: dang / ba lta ci / ste / / pad+ma'i
NK010(tha)012:2554: sna rtse nas myong ba shes rab stong pa nyid
NK010(tha)012:2555: dang / ba lta ci / ste / / kyi
NK010(tha)012:2556: gsang dbang / mkha' gsang du 'dres pa yab kyi
NK010(tha)012:2557: lces blangs te byin pa 'dir dngos brtan gyi gnyis
NK010(tha)012:2558: med bde ba chen po'i gsang dbang ste /
NK010(tha)012:2559: lnga brgya'i tha ma la gsang sngags mos pas spyod pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK010(tha)012:2560: dpon slob gnyis ka'i cha nas de ltar rngo thogs pa ma mchis na /
NK010(tha)012:2561: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa khrel bag yod pa
NK010(tha)012:2562: nyid kha na ma tho ba chung bas gsang dbang
NK010(tha)012:2563: tsam po ba nyid lag len la gdab pa ltar
NK010(tha)012:2564: legs pas / dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po yab yum
NK010(tha)012:2565: snyoms par zhugs pas mos pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK010(tha)012:2566: rang bzhin bde skyong gi snod du bskyil ba bdud
NK010(tha)012:2567: rtsi lnga dang sbyar nas lce thog tu byin la
NK010(tha)012:2569: bde chen thig le yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)012:2571: bu yi lce la dbab par bya //
NK010(tha)012:2572: snying gi dkyil du gzung bar gyis //
NK010(tha)012:2573: +amo bo d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah slob mas dang du blangs nas /
NK010(tha)012:2575: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK010(tha)012:2576: +amo +aahmh'u ma h+aa su kha hoh zhes brjod /
NK010(tha)012:2577: de ltar gsang dbang bskur bas sgron ma lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga brten zhing lam tsan+da li dang /
NK010(tha)012:2578: bzlas brjod byed pa la dbang /
NK010(tha)012:2580: dag bya ngag gi rang bzhin phra ba'i rlung la
NK010(tha)012:2581: zhu bde las skyes pa'i byang chub kyi sems kun
NK010(tha)012:2582: rdzob pa 'dres pas phra ba rlung dang rags pa
NK010(tha)012:2584: gsung rdo rje'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:2585: mchog dag'i ye shes la brten nas ma chags pad+ma can gyis non /
NK010(tha)012:2586: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin te /
NK010(tha)012:2588: gsang ba byang sems rdo rje dang //
NK010(tha)012:2589: rdo rje gsung ni rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)012:2592: yum gyi mkha' gsang du thabs shes gnyis su med
NK010(tha)012:2593: pa'i byang chub kyi sems la brten nas bskur ba
NK010(tha)012:2594: ste / rdo rje khros pa'i dbang le las /
NK010(tha)012:2595: gsang ba'i dbang rnams bskur ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:2596: dbang gi stegs bu rab brtsegs la //
NK010(tha)012:2597: sha rtsi dkar la lcang lo'i skra //
NK010(tha)012:2598: pad+ma'i mchu la so tshags dam //
NK010(tha)012:2599: smin mtshams bar yang ma chad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2600: tshes brgyad zla ba'i mig 'dra ba //
NK010(tha)012:2603: shes rab bcu drug lon pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:2604: bu mo mtshan dang ldan pa la //
NK010(tha)012:2606: rigs dang lo grangs ma nges pa'ang rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK010(tha)012:2607: sme sha can la sogs pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:2608: bcu gnyis dang ni bco brgyad dang //
NK010(tha)012:2609: yang ni nyi shu rtsa gcig la //
NK010(tha)012:2610: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod de //
NK010(tha)012:2611: rnam gsum tshul du nan tan bya //
NK010(tha)012:2612: ha cang sbom min phra ba min //
NK010(tha)012:2613: smin mtshams ring zhing sha mdog dkar //
NK010(tha)012:2614: sme ba'i ga shal yod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:2616: de lta bu'i dbang rten gyi lus byin gyis slob pa'i tshul yang /
NK010(tha)012:2617: spyi bor +amo la snying gar h'u //
NK010(tha)012:2620: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas
NK010(tha)012:2621: pa bde ba chen po'i mchod pa len pa'i phyir
NK010(tha)012:2622: du dbang rten gyi lus la bskyed pa yang /
NK010(tha)012:2623: slob dpon snang ba'i thugs rje bskyed //
NK010(tha)012:2624: yum gyi dus gsum bde gshegs bskyed //
NK010(tha)012:2626: de lta bu'i bskyed rim la mos pa brtan pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2627: rig ma dbang gi rgyud smin zhing srid pa'i 'dod
NK010(tha)012:2628: pa dag pa'i dga' bzhi'i sgyu stsal la goms pa
NK010(tha)012:2629: de nyid / dbang gsum pa bskur ba'i yum gyi
NK010(tha)012:2630: gsang gnas h'u las skyes pa'i rdo rje nor bu'i
NK010(tha)012:2631: rtse mo +amo gyis mtshan par 'du shes pa dang
NK010(tha)012:2632: de nyid / / yum gyi mkha' gsang +aahls pad+ma
NK010(tha)012:2633: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i ze'u 'brur h+r+aihyiga gis mtshan pa
NK010(tha)012:2635: thabs kyi nang nas thabs su gyur pa la brten
NK010(tha)012:2636: nas bde stong lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes mngon
NK010(tha)012:2637: sum du bya'o snyam pa chos kyi 'du shes te
NK010(tha)012:2638: / 'du shes gsum dang ldan pa'i slob ma'i lag tu byin la rtogs pa bskyed pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:2640: bde ba thugs kyi sems dpa' che //
NK010(tha)012:2641: yab yum gnyis med mu tig gi //
NK010(tha)012:2642: khu 'phang byang sems phab pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2643: dus gsum bla ma sangs rgyas dang //
NK010(tha)012:2644: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la bde chen gyi //
NK010(tha)012:2645: byang chub sems kyi mchod pa phul //
NK010(tha)012:2646: rdo rje bde chen thig le'i dbyings //
NK010(tha)012:2647: zag med dbyings su mi rtog skye //
NK010(tha)012:2648: de bas blo mchog longs spyod cig /
NK010(tha)012:2649: ces brjod pa na dbang rten des slob bu'i rgyud
NK010(tha)012:2650: la thig le bcu drug dang dga' ba bcu drug
NK010(tha)012:2651: pa brten nas de nyid rnam pa bcu drug gi
NK010(tha)012:2652: ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir lus gcer bur byas nas
NK010(tha)012:2653: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ngom bzhin par /
NK010(tha)012:2655: yab chen chos kyi dbyings mthong ba'i //
NK010(tha)012:2657: de las byang chub sems 'khyil ba'i //
NK010(tha)012:2658: zag med bde ba longs spyod dam //
NK010(tha)012:2660: slob ma blo chen skal ba dang ldan pa sngags
NK010(tha)012:2661: kyi kun tu spyod pa dang myur lam gyi dam
NK010(tha)012:2662: tshig la shin tu gus pas phyag 'tshal zhing me
NK010(tha)012:2664: e ma hoh shes rab lha mo yum chen mo //
NK010(tha)012:2665: chos kyi dbyings la 'o byed do //
NK010(tha)012:2666: byang chub sems mthong thig le las //
NK010(tha)012:2667: rtag tu gus shing bde ba sbyor //
NK010(tha)012:2668: zhes brjod pas slob ma la tha mal gyi kun
NK010(tha)012:2669: rtog med par mthong nas shin tu dgyes te gsang
NK010(tha)012:2670: chen rdo rje theg pa'i thabs mchog tu gyur pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2671: lam 'di la ma brten par shes bya'i sgrib pa
NK010(tha)012:2672: shin tu phra ba dag thabs gzhan gyis 'dag par
NK010(tha)012:2673: mi nus pas / mchog gi dngos grub rang rig
NK010(tha)012:2674: bde chen ye shes chen po'i 'byung gnas yin par
NK010(tha)012:2676: gar dang ldan pas yang dag bskyod //
NK010(tha)012:2677: bde chen sgyu ma'i brda' mtshon te //
NK010(tha)012:2678: gnyis shor gnyis mnyam dbus dag tu //
NK010(tha)012:2679: dbyings kyi bde chen byung ba de //
NK010(tha)012:2680: rang rig ye shes de la yod //
NK010(tha)012:2681: ces brjod nas rtog pa med par slob ma'i pang du byon /
NK010(tha)012:2682: dza h'u bam hoh zhes brjod pas lcags kyu'i rgyas phrag pa phan tshun sbrel /
NK010(tha)012:2683: zhags pa'i rgyas stod smad zung du 'jug /
NK010(tha)012:2684: lcags sgrog gi rgyas dbang po'i reg pa 'phrod /
NK010(tha)012:2685: dril bu'i rgyas thabs shes snyoms par zhugs pa la yab kyis /
NK010(tha)012:2686: sa ma ya hoh zhes rang gi dam tshig gang yin dang du blang bar brda' sbyar bas /
NK010(tha)012:2689: zhes dam tshig de nyid dang du blangs /
NK010(tha)012:2690: yab kyis a nu r+aa ga ya hoh zhes de
NK010(tha)012:2691: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rjes su chags pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2692: rdo rje'i rang bzhin gyi bdag nyid du nga rgyal
NK010(tha)012:2694: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK010(tha)012:2695: zhes rjes su chags pa'i nga rgyal nyams brtas par mdzad /
NK010(tha)012:2698: zhes pas dbu ma'i mar snar bde ba'i rgyun lam
NK010(tha)012:2699: gyi rtsa rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma btsal
NK010(tha)012:2700: zhing yang dag par bskur bas rjes chags kyi rlung
NK010(tha)012:2701: g.yos / des tsan+da li rab tu 'bar nas spyi
NK010(tha)012:2702: bo'i ham yig las zhu bde'i ye shes bskyed pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2703: tshul gnas kyi sgo nas ngos bzung na mgrin pa
NK010(tha)012:2708: srub dang srub pa'i thabs dag las //
NK010(tha)012:2709: mi rtog pa ni rab tu skye //
NK010(tha)012:2710: dga' dang mchog tu dga' ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:2711: mngon dga' rang bzhin dga' ba ste //
NK010(tha)012:2712: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK010(tha)012:2713: bgrod byed man ngag dag gis so //
NK010(tha)012:2714: dang po dga' ba'i dus su ni //
NK010(tha)012:2715: dbugs ni rgyu ba bcu drug la //
NK010(tha)012:2716: chu tshod lnga bar sbyar byas te //
NK010(tha)012:2717: bzung dang bzlog pa bde bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)012:2718: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya ni //
NK010(tha)012:2719: chu tshod sum cu gnyis ldan bya //
NK010(tha)012:2720: dbyu gu drug cu rtsa bzhi yin //
NK010(tha)012:2722: ljid des gzhal ba'i zangs srang bcu gnyis la snod
NK010(tha)012:2723: rgyar sor mo bcu gnyis 'phang sor brgyad pa'i dbus
NK010(tha)012:2724: gser 'ol ma se sum cu la sor drug pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2725: thur ma phra sbom snyoms pa bug pa /
NK010(tha)012:2726: de chu dwangs pa'i steng du bzhag nas khengs pa'i bar dbyu gu gcig go //
NK010(tha)012:2727: de'i ring la gang zag nad med snyoms pa gcig
NK010(tha)012:2728: gi dbugs sum brgya sum cu rtsa phyed dang brgyad
NK010(tha)012:2729: rgyu / de tsam re re lte ba'i rtsa 'dab
NK010(tha)012:2730: re re nas rgyu ba'i de lta bu drug cu
NK010(tha)012:2731: rtsa bzhi re nyin zhag phrugs gcig la rgyu'o //
NK010(tha)012:2732: de lta bu gnyis la chu tshod gcig de'i bar la dbugs drug brgya bdun cu rtsa lnga rgyu /
NK010(tha)012:2733: de lta bu sum cu so gnyis te spyi bo'i rtsa 'dab so gnyis las de tsam re rgyu'o //
NK010(tha)012:2734: de lta bu gnyis la 'pho ba gcig bya ste stong sum brgya lnga bcu'o //
NK010(tha)012:2735: de lta bu bcu drug longs spyod 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab bcu drug la 'pho zhing rgyu'o //
NK010(tha)012:2736: de tsam pa gnyis la thun phyed pa gcig ste nyis stong bdun bargya'o //
NK010(tha)012:2737: de snying ga'i rtsa 'dab brgyad la 'pho zhing rgyu'o //
NK010(tha)012:2738: thun tshod gnyis las thun tshod gcig ste lnga stong bzhi bargya'o //
NK010(tha)012:2739: de bzhi la nyis khri chig stong drug brgya ste nyin zhag phrugs gcig gi rlung yin no //
NK010(tha)012:2740: phra mo'i thun ni drug cu bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:2741: chen po thun bzhi thun brgyad yin //
NK010(tha)012:2742: dga' ba'i gnas su dbugs dang ni //
NK010(tha)012:2743: thun tshod chu tshod rtsis byas te //
NK010(tha)012:2744: de bzhin mchog dag'i dus su ni //
NK010(tha)012:2745: thun tshod chu tshod de bzhin bslab //
NK010(tha)012:2746: bde ba gang skyes gnas der ni //
NK010(tha)012:2747: man ngag dag kyang der bstan bya //
NK010(tha)012:2748: de don man ngag bcas pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:2749: shes rab ye shes dbang du bshad //
NK010(tha)012:2750: ces rdo rje'i lus kyis bzung ba'i nang gi yul
NK010(tha)012:2751: nyi shu rtsa bzhi la rlung sems 'jug pa'i cha
NK010(tha)012:2752: rnams srog rtsol gyi mthus bcings pas 'khor lo gsum
NK010(tha)012:2753: las gyes pa'i rtsa phran bdun khri nyis stong du
NK010(tha)012:2754: rlung dang dwangs ma zin pas bde ba'i ye shes
NK010(tha)012:2755: gsar du 'khrungs / khu rdul rlung gsum dag pa'i
NK010(tha)012:2756: cha nas lam gyi yon tan ma lus pa rdzogs
NK010(tha)012:2757: gsar du 'khrungs / / de'ang nges pa'i don du
NK010(tha)012:2758: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes dang sbyar na dbang dang
NK010(tha)012:2759: po gsum dang mthun pa ni rtog bcas kyi dga'
NK010(tha)012:2760: ba yin la dbang bzhi pa dang mthun pa ni
NK010(tha)012:2761: rang bzhin gyis rtog med dga' bral lhan cig skyes
NK010(tha)012:2762: pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo yin la rang bzhin
NK010(tha)012:2763: brgyad cu'i rtog tshogs dbyings su nub pas snang ba
NK010(tha)012:2764: stong pa mched pa las snang ba g.yo byed kyi
NK010(tha)012:2765: rlung dang bcas pas stong pas shin tu stong pa
NK010(tha)012:2766: nyer thob la mched pa rlung dang bcas pas kyang
NK010(tha)012:2767: stong pas na stong pa chen po ste /
NK010(tha)012:2768: rags pa'i rlung sems kyis bslad pa'i cha thams cad
NK010(tha)012:2769: las 'das pa'i chos nyid ma 'khrul ba gang yin
NK010(tha)012:2770: pa de gsang sngags lam gyi thabs zab mo la
NK010(tha)012:2771: brten te snying ga'i rtsa mdud grol ba las byung
NK010(tha)012:2772: ba yin te rdo rje 'bar ba bskal pa dum
NK010(tha)012:2773: bu'i rgyud las / sems ni ming bzhi'i phung po ste //
NK010(tha)012:2774: phung po'i rten ni 'byung ba lnga //
NK010(tha)012:2775: 'byung ba'i rten ni rtsa rnams so //
NK010(tha)012:2776: rtsa rnams brten pa srog gi rlung //
NK010(tha)012:2777: srog rlung brten pa byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)012:2778: de rnams gyen du yar ldog pas //
NK010(tha)012:2779: sems ni rlung rten rlung ni rtsa //
NK010(tha)012:2780: rtsa rnams 'byung ba ltar gnas pa //
NK010(tha)012:2781: yab yum bcu ru ye nas gnas //
NK010(tha)012:2783: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus ni //
NK010(tha)012:2784: sku gsung thugs yon lnga la 'dus //
NK010(tha)012:2785: rigs lngar snang ba ye shes dngos //
NK010(tha)012:2786: de yi byin rlabs sprul pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:2787: ji ltar 'dod pa'i yid bzhin tshul //
NK010(tha)012:2788: khro bo khro mo'i rnam sprul yang //
NK010(tha)012:2789: gud na med de de las sprul //
NK010(tha)012:2790: sprul pa rnams kyi rgyu las sprul //
NK010(tha)012:2791: rgyu ni rig pa byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)012:2792: sems nyid yi ge ar snang ba //
NK010(tha)012:2793: a mthong chos kyi dbyings kyang mthong //
NK010(tha)012:2794: ma g.yos lta ba'i rgyas btab na //
NK010(tha)012:2795: dkyil 'khor thams cad bsgom pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:2796: zhes pas dbang gsum pa'i nyams myong la brten nas
NK010(tha)012:2797: bzhi pa'i mtshon don shees pa yin pa'i tshul 'og
NK010(tha)012:2798: tu ston la rdo rje khros pa'i rgyud las kyang
NK010(tha)012:2799: / de yi shes rab ye shes kyi //
NK010(tha)012:2800: dbang gis rdo rje thugs nyid dag /
NK010(tha)012:2801: rdo rje sems dpa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)012:2802: sems nyid mkha' dang mtshungs par mthong //
NK010(tha)012:2804: de ltar dbang gsum pa'i rim pa de dag kyang
NK010(tha)012:2805: sgom don la de ltar shes par bya ba las
NK010(tha)012:2806: re zhig tshangs par spyod pa'i gegs su 'gyur ba
NK010(tha)012:2807: dang / byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa stobs su mi 'gyur zhing /
NK010(tha)012:2808: gnang bkag mi shes pa thams cad las dang po pa kho na yin pas na tshod dang /
NK010(tha)012:2810: cho 'brang la sogs la dpag tu mi rung bas mtshon pa brda'i dbang rig tsaka dang /
NK010(tha)012:2812: kha t+w+aam ka la sogs pa la brten nas bskur ba nyid lag len la gnas pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:2813: de'i phyir thun mong tsam du dag pa brjod pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:2814: de ltar dbang gsum pa bskur bas /
NK010(tha)012:2815: dngos sam yid kyi sna tshogs gzugs can sgom pa la dbang /
NK010(tha)012:2817: dga' ba bzhi'i mas brtan gyi dpe'i ye shes la brten nas rags pa thig le'i sgrib pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:2818: phra ba yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)012:2819: de nyid rnam pa bcu drug gi don mngon du
NK010(tha)012:2820: byas nas chos kyi sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud
NK010(tha)012:2822: dbang bzhi pa ni de bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur ba yin te /
NK010(tha)012:2824: chos sku mngon sum mthong ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)012:2825: mchog gi dbang du de nyid nges //
NK010(tha)012:2827: bzhi pa mchog gi dbang chen yin //
NK010(tha)012:2828: zhes pas bskur ma thag pa'i sher dbang gi dga' ba'i ye shes bzhi pa dga' bral chen po'am /
NK010(tha)012:2829: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i dpe'i ye shes chen po'i rtogs par bya ba ste /
NK010(tha)012:2831: bzhi pa'i dbang ni bskur bya ste //
NK010(tha)012:2832: rlung gi rang bzhin nges shes shing //
NK010(tha)012:2833: bo la ka ko la sbyar la //
NK010(tha)012:2834: rang bzhin bde skor phan tshun 'byung //
NK010(tha)012:2835: gzung du med de brjod du med //
NK010(tha)012:2836: rtog pa kun dang bral ba yi //
NK010(tha)012:2837: rang bzhin 'od gsal der gnas pa //
NK010(tha)012:2838: tshig tshogs dbang gi rang bzhin byin //
NK010(tha)012:2839: rtog pa'i bag chags 'joms par byed //
NK010(tha)012:2840: dbang gsum 'bras bu de bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:2841: zhes pas 'di ni tshig gis mtshon la dad pa dang byin rlabs kyi thob pa'i dbang yin te /
NK010(tha)012:2842: de bas na bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK010(tha)012:2843: gnyis su med par bltas la mos gus kyi gdung
NK010(tha)012:2844: ba drag po dang ldan pas rjes thog tu gsum
NK010(tha)012:2845: pa'i nyams myong lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes ngo
NK010(tha)012:2846: bo nyid kyis stong pas bdag tu lta ba dang
NK010(tha)012:2848: rnam par rig bya rig byed las 'das pa'i chos
NK010(tha)012:2849: nyid ye gnas chen po la phyi gzung ba'i yul
NK010(tha)012:2851: shes pas mthong ba'i chos nyid med pas ma mthong
NK010(tha)012:2852: ba'i mthong ba chen po ni dbang bzhi pa'i ngo
NK010(tha)012:2853: bo nyid yin pa dran par bya ste /
NK010(tha)012:2855: ngo bo nyid kyi stong pa las //
NK010(tha)012:2856: bdag dang chos dang rnam rig dang //
NK010(tha)012:2857: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam spangs pa //
NK010(tha)012:2858: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:2859: stong nyid ye nas gnas pa la //
NK010(tha)012:2860: shes pas mthong ba'i yul min te //
NK010(tha)012:2861: gang gis ye shes bskyed gyur pa //
NK010(tha)012:2862: de yis ye shes rnam dag mthong //
NK010(tha)012:2864: de ltar dbang bzhi pa bskur bas rnam rtog 'joms
NK010(tha)012:2865: byed chos nyid byang chub sems kyi phur pa sgom
NK010(tha)012:2866: pa la dbang / drag po'i las 'grub /
NK010(tha)012:2867: kun gzhi lung ma bstan dang shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK010(tha)012:2868: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs dang /
NK010(tha)012:2869: slob ma'i sgo gsum rdul dang bral ba'i dwangs ma gsum ldan gcig tu 'dres /
NK010(tha)012:2870: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la brten nas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa non /
NK010(tha)012:2871: ngo bo nyid sku 'grub pa'i skal ba rgyud la bzhag pa yin te phrin las kyi rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:2872: nyon mongs thams cad dag par byed //
NK010(tha)012:2873: rnam par rtog pa kun 'joms pa //
NK010(tha)012:2874: dbang gi las kyis byed pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:2876: de ltar dbang bzhi po nyan thos theg pa dang
NK010(tha)012:2877: bstun na bden pa bzhi'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'ang
NK010(tha)012:2878: / phur pa rdo rje phreng ba las /
NK010(tha)012:2879: dang po rgyud rnams nyan pa'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2880: bum pa'i dbang du yang dag blangs //
NK010(tha)012:2881: gnyis pa dam rdzas brten pa'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2882: gsang ba'i dbang du yang dag blangs //
NK010(tha)012:2883: gsum pa nyams su myong ba'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2884: shes rab ye shes dbang du yang dag blangs //
NK010(tha)012:2885: bzhi pa de rnams smin pa'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2886: bden pa bzhi yi bye brag gi //
NK010(tha)012:2887: chos dang ye shes ldan pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:2889: de dag gi dam tshig gi rim pa 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:2891: bum pa'i dam tshig gang yin pa //
NK010(tha)012:2892: bskyed pa'i rim pa brtag pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:2893: rmongs pa rnams la mi bya ste //
NK010(tha)012:2894: snod kyi lo ka gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)012:2895: bcud kyi 'jig rten lha yi mchog /
NK010(tha)012:2896: de ni bum pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK010(tha)012:2897: gang zhig gsang ba ston pa la //
NK010(tha)012:2898: gsang ba'i dam tshig 'di yin te //
NK010(tha)012:2899: bud med shes rab rang bzhin te //
NK010(tha)012:2900: tsan+da li la rtag tu bsgom //
NK010(tha)012:2901: zas lnga rtag tu bza' bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:2902: spyad par bya ba'i mchog yin no //
NK010(tha)012:2903: ye shes chen po'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)012:2904: shes rab kun la spyad pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:2905: dga' ba rtag tu bsten par bya //
NK010(tha)012:2906: sems kyang d+h+au tir blta bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:2907: ye shes snying po'i dam tshig go //
NK010(tha)012:2908: de lta bu dang mi ldan pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2909: dbang dang dam tshig kun las 'das //
NK010(tha)012:2911: sngags pa bya ba gang yang med //
NK010(tha)012:2912: sngags pa sngags pa zhes bya ba //
NK010(tha)012:2913: rtsa ba dang ni yan lag dang //
NK010(tha)012:2914: khyad par dam tshig gang yin dang //
NK010(tha)012:2915: shin tu dbang gi dam tshig dang //
NK010(tha)012:2916: rtsa dang rlung gi dam tshig dang //
NK010(tha)012:2917: byang chub sems kyi gzhag sa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:2918: gang zhig gzhag pa sngags pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:2919: de la mchog gi dngos grub babs //
NK010(tha)012:2920: myur du bla na med pa 'thob //
NK010(tha)012:2923: dam tshig nyams par gyur pa na //
NK010(tha)012:2924: bla ma mnyes par byas pas skong //
NK010(tha)012:2925: gong bzhin dam tshig bsrung ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:2926: dam tshig dang po yin par brjod //
NK010(tha)012:2927: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod cing //
NK010(tha)012:2928: de bzhin b+ha ga'i snying po gzhibs //
NK010(tha)012:2929: dam tshig gnyis pa yin par nges //
NK010(tha)012:2930: shes rab rang bzhin bud med la //
NK010(tha)012:2931: rigs lnga'i mkha' 'gro nyid du brtag /
NK010(tha)012:2932: mdog dang bskyod pa ri mo dang //
NK010(tha)012:2933: dri dang pad+ma yongs brtags la //
NK010(tha)012:2934: gus pas bsten cing brtse bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:2935: dam tshig gsum pa yin par nges //
NK010(tha)012:2936: ting 'dzin gsum la nges pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:2937: sems can sangs rgyas dbyer med kyang //
NK010(tha)012:2938: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par dmigs //
NK010(tha)012:2939: nam yang 'bral bar mi byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:2940: dam tshig bzhi pa yin par bshad //
NK010(tha)012:2942: gal te dam tshig dang mi ldan pa dag la ni dbang mi sbyin te /
NK010(tha)012:2944: dam tshig med pa phal rnams la //
NK010(tha)012:2945: dbang dang sbyin par mi bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:2946: slob dpon slob ma shi ma thag /
NK010(tha)012:2947: mnar med gnas su ltung bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:2949: gnyis pa mtha' rten nam le lag phrin las rab
NK010(tha)012:2950: 'byams kyi dbang dang 'brel bar smad las drag po
NK010(tha)012:2951: sgrol dbang ni / rtsa rgyud rdo rje khros pa las /
NK010(tha)012:2952: dur khrod dbang dang dam rdzas dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2953: rim pa bzhin du bskur bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:2954: phur pa'i dbang dang 'debs pa'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:2955: drag po'i las su gyur pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2956: kun kyang ma lus dbang du bskur //
NK010(tha)012:2959: rgyan dang go cha de bzhin gdugs //
NK010(tha)012:2960: drag po'i rdzas dbang gdug pa sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:2962: zhes pa'i don bshad pa'i rgyud dri med 'od ldan
NK010(tha)012:2963: gyi le'u so bzhi pa las bstan pa 'khrugs sdebs
NK010(tha)012:2964: kyis gtan la phab pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:2965: dbang rdzas so so lag tu byin la /
NK010(tha)012:2969: 'od gsal stobs su gyur pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:2970: bde bar gshegs pa'i mtshon cha 'dis //
NK010(tha)012:2974: rtog pa'i khyad par mtshon byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2975: gab pa'i rmongs pa sel byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:2977: rtogs shing shes pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2980: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:2981: rin chen gser bas lhag pas na //
NK010(tha)012:2982: yab yum gnyis su med pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:2983: gnyis med sgra dbyangs dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2986: chos rnams thugs su chud pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:2987: thams cad rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK010(tha)012:2988: 'gro ba kun la khyab par gnas //
NK010(tha)012:2989: bde gshegs snying po'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2992: chos sku lhun grub thams cad thob //
NK010(tha)012:2993: 'khor ba'i bag chags sbyong mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:2994: bum pa rgyan ldan 'khor ba sel //
NK010(tha)012:2995: chos rnams lhun grub dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:2998: rigs lnga nyon mongs dug lnga 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:2999: ye shes lnga ru mnyam sbyar nas //
NK010(tha)012:3000: mtshon pas rang bzhin dbu la bzhugs //
NK010(tha)012:3001: ye shes lnga yi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3003: cod pan chos rnams mtshon pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3004: snang srid chos kyi dar po che //
NK010(tha)012:3005: bder gshegs kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
NK010(tha)012:3006: cod pan dam pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3009: rigs lnga rgyal bas don mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3010: rigs lnga mtshon byed dam pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3011: gang 'dul bstan pa rgyas mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3012: rigs kyi mtshan ma'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3014: yi ge 'bru lnga ye shes lnga //
NK010(tha)012:3015: mtshon byed don gyi snying po ste //
NK010(tha)012:3016: snying po dam pa lha yi sku //
NK010(tha)012:3017: 'bru lnga snying po'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3019: gdug pa 'joms shing ye shes gsal //
NK010(tha)012:3020: sku lnga mtshon byed phyag mtshan lnga //
NK010(tha)012:3021: rgyal ba 'byung ba'i rang rtags te //
NK010(tha)012:3022: phyag mtshan lnga yi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3025: dug lnga'i mtshon gyis mi tshugs pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3026: gser gyi rdo rjes rab tu mtshon //
NK010(tha)012:3027: dpa' brtul stag gi rgyan chas can //
NK010(tha)012:3028: 'joms byed go cha'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3031: dus gsum 'phags pa mchod mdzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3032: rin chen mdzes su sdug pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:3033: dad pa'i stobs kyis mchod pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:3034: me tog dam pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3037: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku yi rgyan //
NK010(tha)012:3038: 'khor rnams rab tu mnyes mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3039: nyes pas ma gos dbu la bskor //
NK010(tha)012:3040: rgyal ba gdugs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3041: ro mchog lnga ldan zhal zas la //
NK010(tha)012:3042: dbul zhing phongs pa sel mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3044: zhal zas mod la dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3046: de nas smad kyi las la gzer brgyad gces pa'i drag po'i sgrol dbang la gnyis /
NK010(tha)012:3047: rtogs pas bdag nyid bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3051: de la phur pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)012:3052: lta bas mnyam par rtogs pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3053: spyod pas cir yang mi snyoms shing //
NK010(tha)012:3054: thabs kyis 'gro la phan byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3055: de ni dam tshig mchog tu gsungs //
NK010(tha)012:3056: de las 'das na ltung bar gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3058: lta ba'i sgo nas yul dang dngos por 'dzin pa
NK010(tha)012:3059: thams cad de kho na nyid kyi dbyings nam mkha'
NK010(tha)012:3060: lta bu spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du mnyam
NK010(tha)012:3062: spyod pa'i rang bzhin snang srid 'khor 'das lha dang
NK010(tha)012:3063: gzhal yas khang du mnyam par bltas nas snying po
NK010(tha)012:3064: bzlas brjod rgyun mi gcad cing thabs snying rje chen
NK010(tha)012:3065: pos gzhan dbang du gyur pa'i byang chub sems kyi
NK010(tha)012:3066: phur pas log par 'dren pa'i tshogs la drag po
NK010(tha)012:3067: mngon spyod kyis gdab pa'i las rnam pa thams cad
NK010(tha)012:3068: pa byas / de dag gi rnam par shes pa
NK010(tha)012:3069: chos kyi dbyings su yang dag par sbyar nas gzhan
NK010(tha)012:3070: la phan gdags pa ni sgrol ba'i grub mtha' yin
NK010(tha)012:3071: pa byas / te / de ltar ma rtogs pa'i
NK010(tha)012:3072: sgrol ba rang rgyud can ni ngan song gi rgyu
NK010(tha)012:3073: las gzhan cir yang ci 'gyur te sngags kyi theg
NK010(tha)012:3074: pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod khyad par
NK010(tha)012:3076: de'i phyir rtogs pas bdag bsgral nas thugs rjes gzhan don byed pa'i sems rgya chen po bskyed la /
NK010(tha)012:3077: brtul zhugs chen po'i dbang drag shul gyi cho ga'i
NK010(tha)012:3078: phrin las gang yin pa thogs med du 'grub pa'i
NK010(tha)012:3081: khams gsum dbang du sdud mdzad sgrol byed sku //
NK010(tha)012:3082: nyon mongs thang gcig yud la sgrol mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3083: rdo rje phur pa zhing bcu sgrol ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:3084: khams gsum dbyings su sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3087: rdo rje phur pa rab tu k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3088: zhing bcu sgrol mdzad badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3089: r+au tra gnas su sgrol mdzad badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3090: nyon mongs dbyings su sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3093: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas lhun gyis grub //
NK010(tha)012:3094: rang bzhin ye shes lha rnams bzhugs pa'i rten //
NK010(tha)012:3095: mthing nag gru gsum pho brang dbus gsal ba'i //
NK010(tha)012:3096: pho brang chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3099: gti mug sha yi mchod pa ri rab tsam //
NK010(tha)012:3100: 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho chi li li //
NK010(tha)012:3101: zhe sdang rus pa'i mchod pa khra la la //
NK010(tha)012:3102: dug gsum zhal du gsol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3105: gdug pa thabs kyis sgrol ba 'jigs pa'i sku //
