NK010(tha)012:3106: nyon mongs sgrol byed badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3107: zhen pa'i dngos po rab tu gcod byed pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3108: sgrol ba chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3111: gdug pa chen po thabs kyis 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3112: mthing nag drag pos thams cad 'joms pa'i sku //
NK010(tha)012:3113: zhal gsum phyag drug zur gsum dpal dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:3114: sgrub pa drag po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3117: nyon mongs dug lnga dug gis 'thib par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3118: rul cing myags pas 'khor ba gting nas skems //
NK010(tha)012:3119: gnyen po'i dbang du thabs la de ltar snang //
NK010(tha)012:3120: nyon mongs zhen pa sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3123: gu gul sbyar ma rdzas kyi dam pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3124: ye shes mnga' brnyes nyes byed rten dang 'bral //
NK010(tha)012:3125: rab tu sgrub pas 'od dang du bar snang //
NK010(tha)012:3126: drag po rdzas kyi dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3129: yungs kar rgyal po sgrol ba'i dbang //
NK010(tha)012:3130: khro bo'i rgyal po 'bum phrag bsam las 'das //
NK010(tha)012:3131: stong gsum khro bos dus gcig khengs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3132: yungs kar rgyal po sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3135: khams gsum nyon mongs gnas su drang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3136: rab tu 'gugs byed badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3137: nyon mongs zhing bcu gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3138: nyon mongs 'gugs pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3141: nyon mongs rang gar mi btang bcing ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3142: rab tu 'ching byed badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3143: zhing bcu 'ching byed badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3144: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3147: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3148: 'brel ba'i lha mchog badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3149: gang yin sdom byed mthu 'phrog badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3150: gdug byed stobs dang bral ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3153: gdug pa can rnams rab tu 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3154: smyo byed chen po badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3155: nyon mongs 'joms phyir badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3156: smyo byed chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3157: dbye ba'i sgro gnyis kyi dbang /
NK010(tha)012:3159: gzas pa bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa la //
NK010(tha)012:3160: rten dang dbral ba'i phra mar rab tu basngagasa //
NK010(tha)012:3161: rang gi rdzas la dbye ba'i dbang dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:3162: zhing bcu dbye ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3163: rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba chos nyid dam pa'i dbang /
NK010(tha)012:3166: phye nas rab tu bsgral ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3167: nga rgyal rang gar 'dzin pa sgrol mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3168: zhe sdang rang rgyud ngan song gnas su ltung //
NK010(tha)012:3169: stong pa chen por sgrol ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3170: tshe khrus gnas gsum gyi dgongs pas sgrol ba tha mal gyi zhen pa gcod pa'i dbang /
NK010(tha)012:3173: khyad par chen po 'bar bas zhen pa gcod //
NK010(tha)012:3174: sna lnga mtshon las nad lngas 'khor ba gnyen //
NK010(tha)012:3175: de nyid rgyal bas byin brlab rab tu gsungs //
NK010(tha)012:3176: zhen pa gcod pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3180: 'khor ba rang rgyud ngan song dbyings su 'khyams //
NK010(tha)012:3181: 'dzin pa sgrol phyir mtshon gyi rgyal po dang //
NK010(tha)012:3182: mkha' 'gro gdug byed phyag chas dbyings su sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:3183: 'joms byed mtshon gyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3186: gtun khung gru gsum yum gyi mkha' dbyings su //
NK010(tha)012:3187: rig pa'i ye shes yab kyi rdo rje 'di //
NK010(tha)012:3188: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:3189: rdo rje tho ba'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3192: rdos pa'i dngos po brlag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3193: stob byed chen po badz+ra k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3194: gdangs pa'i zhal du nyon mongs stob byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3195: stob byed chen po'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3196: de ltar drag po mngon spyod kyi mjug sdud cha gsum du nges pa las /
NK010(tha)012:3197: klu bdud la gtad pa mnan pa'i dbang /
NK010(tha)012:3199: zhe sdang chen po rab tu gnon mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3200: rdo rje rgya gram phrin las mthar phyin pas //
NK010(tha)012:3201: gang la bya ba'i las nyid gdon mi za //
NK010(tha)012:3202: gnon byed rgya gram dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3203: byin za la stob pa sreg pa'i dbang /
NK010(tha)012:3205: 'khor ba nyon mongs ma lus bsreg pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3206: me yi rgyal po drang srong rab tu 'bar //
NK010(tha)012:3207: thams cad sreg par byed pa me yi dbang //
NK010(tha)012:3208: nyon mongs rabs rgyud sreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK010(tha)012:3210: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i rtags //
NK010(tha)012:3211: drag po hom la rab tu mchod par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3212: sreg byed drang srong mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul //
NK010(tha)012:3213: mchod 'bul dgang blugs dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3214: rlung lha la bskur ba zor gyi dbang ni /
NK010(tha)012:3216: drag po mtshon gyi rgyal po gtor ma la //
NK010(tha)012:3217: ngar 'dzin rab tu brtas pa gcod par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3218: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i zangs dang lcags //
NK010(tha)012:3219: gcod byed ral gri'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK010(tha)012:3220: de ltar sgrol byed drag shul spyod pa'i phrin las
NK010(tha)012:3221: kyi dbang bskur bas dgra bgegs gdug pa can tshar
NK010(tha)012:3222: gcod pa'i mthu rtsal dang nus pa'i dbang thob nas
NK010(tha)012:3223: gzhan don byed nus pa yin te /
NK010(tha)012:3225: drag po'i rdzas dbang gdug pa sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:3228: drag po 'dul ba'i dbang thob na //
NK010(tha)012:3229: phyin chad 'gro ba'i don rnams nus //
NK010(tha)012:3231: de ltar rang don mngon du byas nas /
NK010(tha)012:3232: gnyis pa thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba'i dbang ni //
NK010(tha)012:3234: gab pa'i sdom pa gzung ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3235: gzir mnan drag po'i bsdu ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3236: snying po drag tu bzlas pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3237: dam can gnang la dbab pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3238: rtsa ba khams gsum bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3239: bsgral nas mchod pa bstan pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3240: bkrag mdangs 'phrog nas tshe lung bstan //
NK010(tha)012:3241: 'di ni bsgral ba'i las mchog ste //
NK010(tha)012:3242: thams cad ma lus 'dus par bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3243: gnyis med phur pa shes pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3244: yon tan ldan pa'i sngags pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:3245: 'dis ni gzhan bsgral byang chub thob //
NK010(tha)012:3246: rtogs pas bdag nyid bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3247: thugs rjes gzhan bsgral shes par bya //
NK010(tha)012:3248: zhes pas rnam thar gsum ldan mtshon pa'i lcags kyi
NK010(tha)012:3249: brub khung du nya bo mgo rang la bstan te
NK010(tha)012:3254: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3255: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3256: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3257: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3258: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3259: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3260: khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3261: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3262: bdag cag rnal 'byor sgrub pa po //
NK010(tha)012:3263: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK010(tha)012:3264: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3265: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK010(tha)012:3266: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK010(tha)012:3267: bdud dang bar du gcod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3269: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK010(tha)012:3270: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir khug la //
NK010(tha)012:3271: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3272: lus ngag rdul du bshigs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3273: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:3274: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan /
NK010(tha)012:3276: b+ha ga w+aa na sh+ri kri byi kri /
NK010(tha)012:3277: badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3278: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)012:3279: dzahh+aum bam hoh sarba big nan /
NK010(tha)012:3281: dngos grub bar chod byed pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)012:3282: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:3283: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)012:3284: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)012:3285: rings par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)012:3286: phob cig rnam par gzir bar byos //
NK010(tha)012:3287: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3288: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par byos //
NK010(tha)012:3289: h+aum pa ra bid tan h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3292: g+h+ri na g+h+ri na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3293: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3294: b+han d+ha b+han d+ha h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3295: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3296: ha sa ya ra ha ha na h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3297: shi krin a na ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3298: dz+wa la pa ya dz+wa la pa ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3299: +aa be sha ya +aa be sha ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3300: bin d+ha ya bin d+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3302: de'i tshe de kho na nyid las mi g.yo ba'i rtogs pas bdag bsgral nas /
NK010(tha)012:3303: rjes la thob pa'i snying rje zhe sdang rol pa'i mngon spyod la zhugs /
NK010(tha)012:3304: phyag gnyis rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams na
NK010(tha)012:3305: gnas pa'i mtshan ma rdzas kyi phur bu mgar gyi
NK010(tha)012:3306: so mal nas phyung ma thag pa lta bu de
NK010(tha)012:3307: nyid yi dam gyi lhar gsal ba mi rdugs pa'i
NK010(tha)012:3308: gnad / phyi gzung yul du mngon pa'i snang ba
NK010(tha)012:3309: dngos zhen thams cad nyams pa bdun dang ldan pa'i
NK010(tha)012:3310: bsgral yul du gsal ba ni mi 'byams pa'i gnad
NK010(tha)012:3311: gnad / / nang 'dzin byed kyi rnam par rig
NK010(tha)012:3312: pa thams cad lha'i phyag rgyar gsal ba ni mi
NK010(tha)012:3313: gnad / / ldog pa'i gnad / gsal ba gsum
NK010(tha)012:3314: ldan gyi ngang nas shar ba'i tshad med snying rje'i
NK010(tha)012:3315: phur pas phyi dgra gzung 'dzin gyi nya bo sprul
NK010(tha)012:3317: nyams pa bdun po gnas ngan las bsgral 'dod byang
NK010(tha)012:3318: chub sems kyi phur bus nang dgra dug gsum gyi
NK010(tha)012:3319: ngo bo longs sku'i dbyings su bsad /
NK010(tha)012:3320: bsgral bya sgrol byed kyi kun tu rtog pa las
NK010(tha)012:3321: grol ba'i rig pa ye shes kyi phur bus gsang
NK010(tha)012:3322: dgra bdag 'dzin gyi ngo bo chos sku'i dbyings su
NK010(tha)012:3323: bsad pa ste / phur pa phrin las kyi rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:3324: byang chub sems kyi phur bu ni //
NK010(tha)012:3325: rnam par rtog pa kun 'joms byed //
NK010(tha)012:3326: phur bu'i rgyu tshad dbyibs dang ni //
NK010(tha)012:3327: skur gsal byin brlabs byas pa yis //
NK010(tha)012:3328: rnam rtog sgrol bar rab tu bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3330: de'i tshe skye mched dur khrod du bsgral bas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK010(tha)012:3331: chags rtog yum mkha' la bsgral bas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK010(tha)012:3332: ming bzhi'i phung po dag pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK010(tha)012:3333: rnam shes 'og min du bsgral bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK010(tha)012:3334: lta ba la spros pa med pa rtag chad kyi 'phrang las grol /
NK010(tha)012:3335: bsgom pa la bsal bzhag med pas byings rgod kyi 'phrang las grol /
NK010(tha)012:3336: spyod pa la dngos 'dzin med pas tshul 'chos kyi 'phrang las grol ba ste /
NK010(tha)012:3337: yul gsum gsal dang dgra gsum gsad //
NK010(tha)012:3338: bdud bzhi bsgral dang 'phrang gsum bsal //
NK010(tha)012:3339: bla tshe'i lhag ma bdag la 'dres //
NK010(tha)012:3340: ye shes chu yis sdig sgrib bkrus //
NK010(tha)012:3341: rnam shes rgyal ba'i zhing du 'phang //
NK010(tha)012:3342: de ni sgrol dbang ngo bo yin //
NK010(tha)012:3345: rnam shes snying gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK010(tha)012:3346: byang chub sems kyi rtse gtad de //
NK010(tha)012:3347: dkar nag mtshams kyi snying la ni //
NK010(tha)012:3348: dge sdig las kyi shan phye ste //
NK010(tha)012:3349: rnam par rtog pa'i sdig sbyangs nas //
NK010(tha)012:3350: rnam bzhi las kyi 'dul sbyangs kyis //
NK010(tha)012:3351: nyon mongs dug gsum bcom nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3352: rnam shes gser zhun lta bu de //
NK010(tha)012:3353: yam gyis bteg la phata kyis 'phang //
NK010(tha)012:3354: h+aum gis bsdus nas mkha' la bstim //
NK010(tha)012:3355: rigs lnga'i sras su nges par bya //
NK010(tha)012:3357: sku gsung thugs su gsal byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:3358: ngan song sgo gsum shin tu bcad //
NK010(tha)012:3359: rnam rtog bsgral ba'i zhing bcur brlab //
NK010(tha)012:3360: de yi rnam shes chos kyi sku //
NK010(tha)012:3361: rnam dag dbyings kyi ngang du bsgom //
NK010(tha)012:3362: don du rang sems mya ngan 'da' //
NK010(tha)012:3364: phur pa phrin las kyi rgyud las kyang /
NK010(tha)012:3365: gdab pa kun gyi gong du ni //
NK010(tha)012:3367: nyon mongs mnar ba'i sems can dag /
NK010(tha)012:3368: 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3369: rdo rje phur bus rab tu gdab //
NK010(tha)012:3370: ngan song rgyu ni des tshar bcad //
NK010(tha)012:3371: rgya mdud gnyis dang logs brgyad dang //
NK010(tha)012:3372: dbal dang bcas pa'i 'od zer gyis //
NK010(tha)012:3373: ngan song gsum gyi der sbyong byed //
NK010(tha)012:3374: phur bu'i 'od zer chen po des //
NK010(tha)012:3375: bdag dang gzhan gyi don bsgrub bya //
NK010(tha)012:3376: sngags kyi 'od zer drag po ste //
NK010(tha)012:3377: spros pas gzhan gyi sdig pa 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:3378: bsdus pas bdag gi sdig pa 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:3379: phur pa'i 'od zer de bsgoms shing //
NK010(tha)012:3380: rnam rtog thams cad des sgrol byed //
NK010(tha)012:3381: drag po'i las ni thams cad kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3382: snying rjes zin pa'i zhe sdang gis //
NK010(tha)012:3383: nyon mongs gnas su dag byas bsgral //
NK010(tha)012:3384: zhes rtogs pa bskyed nas slob bu'i lag tu sras
NK010(tha)012:3385: mchog gi phur pa gtad pa ting nge 'dzin dang
NK010(tha)012:3386: ldan pa'i chu srin rnam rol gyi phyag rgyas bzung
NK010(tha)012:3388: g.yas g.yon nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor las //
NK010(tha)012:3389: h+aum dang +aa ni shin tu gsal //
NK010(tha)012:3390: gung bu mthe bong mdzub srin dang //
NK010(tha)012:3391: mathe'u chung la sogs g.yas g.yon la //
NK010(tha)012:3393: rim pa bzhin du gsal bkod la //
NK010(tha)012:3396: thal mo mnyam par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:3398: sor mo cung zad bsnol bar bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:3400: sor mo rgyab tu bsnol te bsdams /
NK010(tha)012:3402: phur bu blangs te chang bar gzhug /
NK010(tha)012:3403: lag pa'i rting pa kha phye la //
NK010(tha)012:3404: mthe bong gnyis dang srin lag dang //
NK010(tha)012:3405: mathe'u chung bar du phur pa gzhug /
NK010(tha)012:3406: mthe bong bsgul la phur pa bsgril //
NK010(tha)012:3408: zhes pa'i don gyis phur skor byed du gzhug cing /
NK010(tha)012:3409: rdo rje khros pa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:3411: yab yum bde klong thig le las //
NK010(tha)012:3412: mi shigs byang chub sems kyi h+aum //
NK010(tha)012:3413: 'joms byed dpa' be'u phur bu'i dbyibs //
NK010(tha)012:3414: thig le yig 'bru rnam pa kun //
NK010(tha)012:3415: phur pa'i logs la lha bkod nas //
NK010(tha)012:3416: 'gyur med dbyings kyi ngang nyid las //
NK010(tha)012:3418: sras kyi mchog gyur phur pa'i tshul //
NK010(tha)012:3419: zhal gsum phyag drug 'jigs byed sku //
NK010(tha)012:3421: khro dang bzhad dang gshe ba'i tshul //
NK010(tha)012:3422: phyag drug rgyud drug rtsad nas gcod //
NK010(tha)012:3423: phyag mtshan mtshon chas 'gro drug sgrol //
NK010(tha)012:3424: sku smad chu srin phur pa'i dbal //
NK010(tha)012:3425: rgya mdud nang nas sngags kyi sgra //
NK010(tha)012:3426: 'brug stong lta bur ldir zhing grags //
NK010(tha)012:3427: chu srin kha nas me lce 'od //
NK010(tha)012:3428: glog ltar 'khyug cing stong gsum gsal //
NK010(tha)012:3429: gdug pa chu srin kha nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:3431: stong gsum gang zhing klu rnams 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:3432: thugs ka dpal be'u'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)012:3433: bzhi bcu rtsa bdun lha ru rdzogs //
NK010(tha)012:3434: dbu la rigs lnga khrag 'thung rdzogs //
NK010(tha)012:3435: ye shes lnga ldan dug lnga 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:3436: sras kyi thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)012:3437: bde chen yab yum dbyings su bzhugs //
NK010(tha)012:3438: khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang //
NK010(tha)012:3439: khro mo'i sprul pas sa gzhi gang //
NK010(tha)012:3440: phra men sprul pas bar snang gang //
NK010(tha)012:3441: sgo ba'i sprul pas phyogs bzhir 'gyed //
NK010(tha)012:3442: khro bo phra men sgo ba'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)012:3443: thams cad 'dus pa sras kyi mchog /
NK010(tha)012:3444: ma btab tsam na lhun gyis grub //
NK010(tha)012:3445: btab na lha yang brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3446: dgra bgegs thig le'i dkyil du k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3447: dug gsum rtsad nas chod cig k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3448: rgyu drug gnas su sgrol cig k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3449: sems kyi bag chags sbyongs shig k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3450: sems nyid dbyings su stims shig k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3451: dbyings las bde chen rgyas gyur k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3452: sprul sku'i 'gro don mdzod cig k+ai la ya //
NK010(tha)012:3454: de nas pho nya bskul zhing bsgral ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:3456: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)012:3457: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3458: sngon chad ji bzhin dam bcas pa'i //
NK010(tha)012:3459: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:3469: a tsi te a pa ra tsi te mar sa ni pra mar ta na ye h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3470: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)012:3471: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3472: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)012:3473: klad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)012:3474: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)012:3475: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)012:3476: h+aum m+aa ma pa shi ku ru /
NK010(tha)012:3477: ma tam nya ka ra i nan d+ha ti ma ma karma shi krang ka ra ye h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3478: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:3479: lha'am gnod sbyin bdud kyang rung //
NK010(tha)012:3480: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:3481: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par byos //
NK010(tha)012:3482: sarba a pa na ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3483: ta th+aa ya ta th+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)012:3485: gtun khung du rdo rje bsdam pa'i phyag rgyas bzung ba'i tho bas brdung zhing /
NK010(tha)012:3486: sbyor sgrol zung 'jug 'pho med bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes dran par byas nas /
NK010(tha)012:3488: rdungs shig rdo rje 'bar ba'i gtun //
NK010(tha)012:3489: bka' las 'da' byed sdig can rnams //
NK010(tha)012:3490: rdo rje me dbal snying bsreg nas //
NK010(tha)012:3491: lus ngag rdul phran bzhin du lhogs //
NK010(tha)012:3492: khro mo 'bar ba'i gtun khung du //
NK010(tha)012:3493: rdo rje tho bas brdung byas nas //
NK010(tha)012:3494: lha yang rung ste brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3496: zhes nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK010(tha)012:3500: de nas ling ro'i yan lag rnams hom la bsreg
NK010(tha)012:3501: cing nang khrol zhal du bstab pa'i phyir sbyin bsreg
NK010(tha)012:3503: chos 'byung gi steng du drag po'i shing la hom brtsig /
NK010(tha)012:3504: dz+wa la ram gyis me sbar nas dam tshig ye shes gnyis med dkrong bskyed bya /
NK010(tha)012:3507: bshad rgyud tshig sna bstung ba /
NK010(tha)012:3508: steng 'og phyogs mtshams skyong ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:3509: sku mdog sna tshogs 'od dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:3510: g.yas pa rang rtags g.yon me dpung //
NK010(tha)012:3511: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul myur ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:3512: bus shig bus shig me bus shig /
NK010(tha)012:3513: rgya mtsho'i gting nas me long la //
NK010(tha)012:3514: ri rab rtse nas me bus shig /
NK010(tha)012:3515: nyams pa gang yin sreg par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:3517: ag+na ye ha bya ka b+ha ha na ye dgra bgegs 'byung po m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)012:3518: ces pas me lha la slob mar 'bul du bcug /
NK010(tha)012:3519: me lha'i lto ba yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du dkyil 'khor ba rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK010(tha)012:3520: zhes skad cig dkrong bskyed byas la /
NK010(tha)012:3522: dgra bgegs 'byung po m+aa ra ya phata /
NK010(tha)012:3524: bstod cing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:3527: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor dang bcas //
NK010(tha)012:3529: khros pas yud kyis brlag par mdzod //
NK010(tha)012:3530: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK010(tha)012:3531: brlag mdzad lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK010(tha)012:3532: drag po'i phrin las grub pa yi //
NK010(tha)012:3533: dngos grub bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:3534: badz+ra muhs ye shes pa gshegs /
NK010(tha)012:3535: de nas zor gtor slob ma'i lag tu byin la /
NK010(tha)012:3538: mthing nag gru gsum dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)012:3539: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yang //
NK010(tha)012:3540: g.yas na khrag zor mda' ltar 'phen //
NK010(tha)012:3541: g.yon pa nyungs zor rbab ltar 'dril //
NK010(tha)012:3542: khrag zor dmar po mtsho ltar rlog /
NK010(tha)012:3543: mda' zor drag po skar ltar 'khrug /
NK010(tha)012:3544: drag po nyungs zor rbab ltar 'dril //
NK010(tha)012:3545: mtshe zer rnon po mdung ltar 'debs //
NK010(tha)012:3546: drag po'i phur zor snying la 'debs //
NK010(tha)012:3547: do nub zor gyi las mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)012:3550: g.yas pa khrag zor mda' ltar drag /
NK010(tha)012:3551: g.yon pa nyungs zor rbab ltar 'dril //
NK010(tha)012:3553: dbus dang phyogs 'dul sras mchog ni //
NK010(tha)012:3554: stod ni zhal gsum phyag drug la //
NK010(tha)012:3555: sku smad lcags phur dbal dang ldan //
NK010(tha)012:3556: g.yas pa 'dral byed gri gug bsnams //
NK010(tha)012:3557: g.yon pa khrag zor mda' ltar 'phen //
NK010(tha)012:3560: khro bo khro mo yab yum bcu //
NK010(tha)012:3561: phyogs bcu'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:3562: g.yas pa 'dral byed gri gug bsnams //
NK010(tha)012:3563: g.yon pa khrag zor mda' ltar 'phen //
NK010(tha)012:3565: shwa na ma bzhi bdag nyid bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:3566: bse mo bzhi dang ming po gsum //
NK010(tha)012:3567: las su sha za khrag 'thung ma //
NK010(tha)012:3568: g.yas pas phur zor mda' ltar 'phen //
NK010(tha)012:3569: g.yon pas khrag zor mtsho ltar rlog /
NK010(tha)012:3570: nyid kyi dam tshig khrag mda' 'di //
NK010(tha)012:3571: da ni 'phen pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)012:3572: khrag mda' khrag sbur chi li li //
NK010(tha)012:3573: khrag mda' bu yug char ltar phob //
NK010(tha)012:3574: dgra bo'i khong du dug mda' rgyob //
NK010(tha)012:3575: las kyi mkha' 'gro rnam gsum yang //
NK010(tha)012:3576: khrag zor dmar po'i sna drongs la //
NK010(tha)012:3577: khrag zor me ltar mched nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3578: dam nyams dgra bo tshig par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3579: khrag zor chu ltar brub nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3580: dam nyams dgra bo 'khyer bar byed //
NK010(tha)012:3581: khrag zor gnyen po'i sna drongs shig /
NK010(tha)012:3582: zor 'phang slar la ma log cig /
NK010(tha)012:3583: gnyen byas dgra ru ma ldang zhig /
NK010(tha)012:3584: zas sbyor dug tu ma g.yo zhig /
NK010(tha)012:3585: dam nyams gang yin yul mkhar bsgyel //
NK010(tha)012:3586: mi nad me ltar mched nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3587: gang yin nyams pa phung bar byed //
NK010(tha)012:3588: dmag sna drongs shig drag po zor gyi lha //
NK010(tha)012:3589: b+h+yo b+h+yo drag po zor gyi thun phob cig /
NK010(tha)012:3592: mnan pa'i las yin pas mgo bo gtor gzhong ri rib tu bsam pa'i 'og tu mnan la /
NK010(tha)012:3596: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu yang //
NK010(tha)012:3597: khro rngams rab tu gdug pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3598: thugs rje chen pos bro la gshegs //
NK010(tha)012:3599: dgra ni thal bar brlag pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3600: bdud ni phye mar 'thag pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3601: rngam pa chen po bro la gshegs //
NK010(tha)012:3603: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)012:3604: tshangs pa 'dul ba gdug pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)012:3605: h+aum mdzad yab yum bro la gshegs //
NK010(tha)012:3606: khro bo mthing ga sprin ltar gtibs //
NK010(tha)012:3607: khro chung tshon gang skar ltar 'khrug /
NK010(tha)012:3608: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3609: dgra ni thal bar brlag pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3611: bla med byang chub thob pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3612: phung po rdul du bshig pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3613: rnam shes dbyings su 'dren pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3614: ta krita chen po bro la gshegs //
NK010(tha)012:3616: gdug pa phag dang rmig bu'i mgo //
NK010(tha)012:3618: la la lding zhing la la 'dral //
NK010(tha)012:3619: gshog pa can gyis mtha' nas sdud //
NK010(tha)012:3620: mche ba can gyis gsod par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3621: tsham rngams drag pos bdud dpung 'joms //
NK010(tha)012:3622: dpal brtul drag po'i tshangs rigs 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:3623: 'jigs pa'i khro bdag sprin ltar gtibs //
NK010(tha)012:3624: khro chung tshon gang skar ltar 'khrug /
NK010(tha)012:3625: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3627: khro bos gdug pa grogs dang 'bral //
NK010(tha)012:3628: thugs las sprul cing las rnams byed //
NK010(tha)012:3629: sras mchog mthing ga sprin ltar gtibs //
NK010(tha)012:3630: khro chung tshon gang skar ltar 'khrug /
NK010(tha)012:3631: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3633: mkha' 'gro ma chen gdug pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3634: ma mo'i rta bro si li li //
NK010(tha)012:3635: sngon dmar byad thag rgyang se rgyang //
NK010(tha)012:3636: sha khrag dmar po mkha' 'gro'i zas //
NK010(tha)012:3637: sha la rol cig mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)012:3640: mkha' 'gro rngam byed ro la rngam //
NK010(tha)012:3641: g.yas su bltas nas g.yon du 'khyud //
NK010(tha)012:3642: rngam pa'i tshems gcig mdun du blta //
NK010(tha)012:3643: nyams pa gang yin spyan gyis gzigs //
NK010(tha)012:3644: so brdar mche gtsigs ha sgra can //
NK010(tha)012:3645: stong gsum ro za khrag 'thung yang //
NK010(tha)012:3647: mkha' 'gro ma chen sprin ltar gtibs //
NK010(tha)012:3648: pho nya phyag brnyan skar ltar 'khrug /
NK010(tha)012:3649: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3651: snying gi dkyil du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3652: ye shes lnga po mnyes par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3653: dran pa gnas su dag pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3654: mig gi steng du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3655: gzugs kyi lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3656: rna ba'i steng du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3657: sgra yi lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3658: sna yi steng du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3659: dri yi lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3660: lce yi steng du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3661: ro yi lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3662: lus kyi steng du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3663: reg bya'i lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3664: snying gi dkyil du bro brdungs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3665: chos kyi lha mo mnyes pa'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3666: mdzes byed lha mo sprin ltar gtibs //
NK010(tha)012:3667: phyi nang lha mo skar ltar 'khrugs //
NK010(tha)012:3668: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i bro //
NK010(tha)012:3670: de nas smad las drag po sgrol dbang gi dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK010(tha)012:3672: dngos grub dam pa lha yi lha //
NK010(tha)012:3673: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK010(tha)012:3674: dur khrod rdzas la brten te bsgrubs lags na //
NK010(tha)012:3675: snang srid byams pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:3676: ye shes lha ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)012:3677: dngos grub stsal dang stsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3678: gdug pa chen po thabs kyis 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3679: drag pos 'dren pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:3681: chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i byin rlabs las //
NK010(tha)012:3682: dregs pa 'dul phyir thugs rje'i byin rlabs 'byung //
NK010(tha)012:3683: bdud kyi rgyal po r+au tra 'dul ba ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3684: bdud rgyal dregs pa 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3686: bdud dpung chom nas chos nyid mngon mthong bas //
NK010(tha)012:3687: bdud rgyal r+au tras chos nyid don rtogs nas //
NK010(tha)012:3688: thugs rje'i byin rlabs bdud la snang ba ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3689: nyon mongs dbyings su bsgral ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3691: 'khor gyi gdug pa ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3692: steng phyogs khro rgyal yab yum 'khor dang bcas //
NK010(tha)012:3693: tshangs pa 'khor bcas rab tu btul ba ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3694: 'jig rten dregs pa btul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3696: rol pa chen po steng gi sras mchog yang //
NK010(tha)012:3697: zhing bcu stobs dang rab tu 'dral mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3698: bdud rgyal r+au tra grogs dang bral ba bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:3699: zhing bcu stobs dang bral ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3700: sprul pas stong khams rab tu bkang nas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3701: gdul ba'i dbang gis gang la ci 'dul ston //
NK010(tha)012:3702: rgyal bas stong gsum sprul pas bkang ba ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3703: sprul pa khams gsum 'gengs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3705: dpal gyi bka' nyan las la brtson pa mo //
NK010(tha)012:3706: 'jig rten dregs pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3707: 'jig rten dbang du bsdud pa'i las byas ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3708: dam las mi 'da' bka' nyan dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3710: 'jig rten khams la dbang sgyur mthu mo che //
NK010(tha)012:3711: las ngan zhing bcu ma lus sgrol mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3712: bcol zhing rbad na las su pho nya mdzad pa ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3713: gang du mngags pa'i las rnams 'grub pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3715: dregs pa sde bzhi rab tu 'dul mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)012:3716: nad kyi bdag mo bka' nyan gsung sdod ma //
NK010(tha)012:3717: bran dang pho nya las rnams 'grub byed ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3718: gang la bya ba'i las rnams myur 'grub dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3720: rol pa chen po'i byin rlabs cir yang snang //
NK010(tha)012:3721: 'dul thabs drag po bdud kyi chas 'dra yang //
NK010(tha)012:3722: snying rje byang chub sems las nyams pa med //
NK010(tha)012:3723: brag po byams pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)012:3725: thugs rje byams pas 'gro la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK010(tha)012:3726: la lar zhi dang la lar khro bor snang //
NK010(tha)012:3727: 'dul thabs drag pos 'gro ba 'dul lags na //
NK010(tha)012:3728: nyon mongs gnas su 'dren pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3729: bdud dang srin po 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3730: don dam chos nyid rtogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3731: sangs rgyas sa la 'gro ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3732: 'khor ba ngan song sbyong ba'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)012:3733: zhes pas bkra shis par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:3734: gsum pa dbang gi srog shing du gyur pa dam tshig yin par bstan pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:3736: snga rabs 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3737: dam tshig 'di la brten nas grub //
NK010(tha)012:3738: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3739: dam tshig 'di la brten pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3740: slad nas 'byon pa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3741: dam tshig 'di la brten nas grub //
NK010(tha)012:3742: de phyir dam tshig theg chen 'di //
NK010(tha)012:3743: phyi rabs sngags 'chang rnams kyis bsrungs //
NK010(tha)012:3745: sa las skye 'khrungs kun bskyed ltar //
NK010(tha)012:3746: dam tshig gzhi yi sa gzhi ni //
NK010(tha)012:3747: kun la ye shes bskyed par byed //
NK010(tha)012:3748: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum po dang //
NK010(tha)012:3749: yan lag dam tshig lnga rnams las //
NK010(tha)012:3750: ma 'das bsrungs na sangs rgyas yin //
NK010(tha)012:3751: de las 'das na sems can yin //
NK010(tha)012:3752: dam tshig gzhung bzhin bsrung ba la //
NK010(tha)012:3753: dam can rnams kyi bsgo ba nyan //
NK010(tha)012:3754: gal te bsgo ba ma nyan na //
NK010(tha)012:3755: dam can nyid kyang brlag par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3758: dam tshig 'di ni gtso yin zhes //
NK010(tha)012:3759: dpa' bo chen po yang dag bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3760: dam tshig nyams pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK010(tha)012:3761: bya ru mi rung sna tshogs byed //
NK010(tha)012:3762: slob dpon bka' bslu smod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3763: lu gu rgyud la dbyen 'dogs dang //
NK010(tha)012:3764: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun bcad nas //
NK010(tha)012:3765: gzhan nas dngos grub thob 'dod pa //
NK010(tha)012:3766: 'di yang nyams pa'i snga ltas yin //
NK010(tha)012:3767: rdzas dang lag cha mngon bstan nas //
NK010(tha)012:3768: pha rol gzhan la bsdigs byed cing //
NK010(tha)012:3769: man ngag gting nas ma thob par //
NK010(tha)012:3770: agatsha&a&a&ara kha yis ngoms pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:3771: rig pa'i rtsal dang mi ldan par //
NK010(tha)012:3772: kha nas lha srin gnyan 'bod pa //
NK010(tha)012:3773: 'di yang nyams pa'i snga ltas yin //
NK010(tha)012:3774: mtshan dang ldan pa'i rig ma la //
NK010(tha)012:3775: phrad nas sbyor ba ma byas dang //
NK010(tha)012:3776: las ngan skyon can mtshan rdzogs pa //
NK010(tha)012:3777: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma bsgral na //
NK010(tha)012:3778: 'di yang nyams pa'i snga ltas yin //
NK010(tha)012:3779: dam tshig nyams pa'i lnga ltas ni //
NK010(tha)012:3780: rtsa ba gsum po nyams gyur na //
NK010(tha)012:3781: rdo rje dmyal bar skye bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3782: 'dir yang nyes pa sna bcu yong //
NK010(tha)012:3783: phyi ma na rag dmyal khams skye //
NK010(tha)012:3784: 'dir yang nad dang sdug bsngal che //
NK010(tha)012:3785: mdze dad nad dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs 'ong //
NK010(tha)012:3786: ma tshogs stong gis snying nas 'dren //
NK010(tha)012:3787: sha zan stong gis sha rus 'dral //
NK010(tha)012:3789: dam tshig nyams pa'i bdud du 'bab //
NK010(tha)012:3790: ma mo kun kyang gshed du 'ong //
NK010(tha)012:3791: tshe dang srog la bar chad byed //
NK010(tha)012:3792: dam tshig 'di la mi gnas na //
NK010(tha)012:3793: brtsams pa mi 'grub mya ngan non //
NK010(tha)012:3794: dam tshig bsrung ba'i yon tan ni //
NK010(tha)012:3796: yi dam lha yi dngos grub thob //
NK010(tha)012:3798: dngos grub rnam gsum rim bzhin thob //
NK010(tha)012:3799: tshe dang bsod nams dbang thang 'phel //
NK010(tha)012:3800: lha srin kun kyang de bzhin bkur //
NK010(tha)012:3801: dgra bgegs kun kyang gzhom zhing 'dul //
NK010(tha)012:3802: bstan pa kun kyang dar zhing bsrungs //
NK010(tha)012:3803: dam tshig 'di dang gtsor len na //
NK010(tha)012:3805: dam tshig bsrung ba'i rim pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:3806: rdo rje slob dpon pha ltar 'khur //
NK010(tha)012:3807: yum gyi dbang mo ma ltar 'khur //
NK010(tha)012:3808: mched dang lcam dral spun ltar brtse //
NK010(tha)012:3809: nyin dang mtshan du dus med par //
NK010(tha)012:3810: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:3811: ma yengs gsal ba'i don brtson pa //
NK010(tha)012:3812: 'di yang bsrung ba'i rim pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3813: mnyan bsam thos pa rgya bskyed nas //
NK010(tha)012:3815: rtag tu bsgrub la brtson byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3816: 'di yang bsrung ba'i rim pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3817: pha rol dam nyams dgra bo la //
NK010(tha)012:3818: dmod btsugs kha tsho mi zer bar //
NK010(tha)012:3819: gsang zhing bstun nas las byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3820: 'di yang bsrung ba'i rim pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3822: mdor na dam tshig sa ma ya 'bum sder gnas kyang /
NK010(tha)012:3823: bsdu na spyi'i dam tshig nyi shu /
NK010(tha)012:3824: khyad par gyi dam tshig nyi shu /
NK010(tha)012:3825: lhag pa'i dam tshig bzhi ste rnam grangs nyi shu rtsa bzhir dngos bstan dang /
NK010(tha)012:3826: brda tshig gis bshad pa ni /
NK010(tha)012:3827: phur pa mya ngan las 'das pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:3828: sbyor sgrol ma byin len dang tshig barlanga rdzun //
NK010(tha)012:3829: nyon mongs rang gar spyad pas ngan song rgyu //
NK010(tha)012:3830: dug lnga ye shes lnga yi ngo bo la //
NK010(tha)012:3831: ma rig log par mthong nas spang bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:3832: mi spang dam tshig nyams pa de bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:3833: dri chen dri chu dmar chen m+aam sa sems //
NK010(tha)012:3834: so so'i rnam rtog dbyings su ma 'byongs te //
NK010(tha)012:3835: nyon mongs las la chags pa'i ngo bor bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3836: gnyis med don dang 'gal bas de bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:3837: phung po 'byung ba kha dog dbang po'i yul /
NK010(tha)012:3838: gnyis med lta ba ngan pas so sor brtags //
NK010(tha)012:3839: ye shes lnga yi don dang ma 'gal bya //
NK010(tha)012:3840: gnyis med don dang 'gal bas de bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:3841: de bzhin rdo rje'i rigs dang pad+ma las //
NK010(tha)012:3842: rigs kyi khyad par ye shes lnga snang na //
NK010(tha)012:3843: ye shes dmigs med don de ma rtogs pas //
NK010(tha)012:3844: grub pas 'bras bu med pas dmyal bar bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3845: spyi yi dam tshig de dag gzhung bsrongs na //
NK010(tha)012:3846: sa gzhi chen po 'dra ste kun gyi rten //
NK010(tha)012:3847: yid bzhin nor bu 'dra ste 'dod pa skong //
NK010(tha)012:3848: gcan gzan seng ge bzhin du zil gyis gnon //
NK010(tha)012:3849: don gyi rtsa ba don gyi mkhar bzhin bsrung //
NK010(tha)012:3850: 'bras bu yang dag nges pa gdon mi za'o //
NK010(tha)012:3851: gzhan yang khyad par dam tshig rnam mang yang //
NK010(tha)012:3852: mdo dang don du nyi shu'i don dang bstun //
NK010(tha)012:3853: gcan gzan rgyal po bla ma la mi brnyas /
NK010(tha)012:3855: za ma tog tu ngan pa'i bsam ngan spang /
NK010(tha)012:3857: rin po che yi sems bskyed mi spang /
NK010(tha)012:3859: gangs kyi zhun chu khol ma gsang dbang gi yum la mi spyad /
NK010(tha)012:3861: pad+ma rgyas pa'i ze'u 'bru mched mo la mi spyod /
NK010(tha)012:3863: bug rdol can gyi snod du bcud mi blug /
NK010(tha)012:3864: ma smin pa dang log lta can la chos mi ston /
NK010(tha)012:3865: ma brtags pa yi nor dang byin gyis ma brlabs pa'i zas mi za /
NK010(tha)012:3867: shel sgong dkar po rdzab dam tshig ma nyams par byed /
NK010(tha)012:3869: snod ngan nang du seng ge'i zho mi bzho //
NK010(tha)012:3870: snod med la gdams pa gsang /
NK010(tha)012:3871: yid bzhin nor bu thab tu snod ldan la mi gsang /
NK010(tha)012:3873: bya yi rgyal po khyung gi gshog mi bcag /
NK010(tha)012:3875: gnam lcags sder mo sa la brdab gang rung la mi bya /
NK010(tha)012:3877: stag gzig rol pa'i zas kyi lhag tshogs phud ma nyams par /
NK010(tha)012:3879: rdo rje gtams pa'i brag rnams yongs dam tshig mi gtang /
NK010(tha)012:3881: rdo rje ra bas bskor ba'i go mtshams la ral ba bya /
NK010(tha)012:3883: mun pa sel ba'i sgron me yongs mi gsod //
NK010(tha)012:3885: rdo rje chu bo'i 'ol kha gcad mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:3887: rgyal po rtags kyi phyag rgya sbyin mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:3888: snod med la dbang mi bskur /
NK010(tha)012:3889: rdo rje mkhar rdzong gtams dam tshig la gtsor 'don bya /
NK010(tha)012:3891: rgyal mtshan rtser bla ma spyi bor sgom pa dang mi 'bral /
NK010(tha)012:3892: btags nor bu rin po che //
NK010(tha)012:3893: 'dod par gyur pa'i mtshan mas dpog mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:3894: gnyis med don gyi mya ngan 'das mod kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3895: log par brtags pa'i dbang gi so sor snang //
NK010(tha)012:3896: khyad par bstan pa'i dam tshig don rnams te //
NK010(tha)012:3897: dngos su nyams na ljon shing mes tshig 'dra //
NK010(tha)012:3898: zur gyis nyams kyang bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu ring //
NK010(tha)012:3899: kun tu nyams na brjod pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NK010(tha)012:3900: gzhung du bsrungs na rang snang 'bras bu 'chang //
NK010(tha)012:3901: rgyun du bsrings na don dang man ngag 'grub //
NK010(tha)012:3902: lhag pa'i dam tshig don gyi bzhi ru sbyar //
NK010(tha)012:3903: spyod pa rgyun dang rang bzhin lta ba gnyis //
NK010(tha)012:3904: gal mdo nges pa lta ba nyams drod bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:3905: spyod pa rgyun la dmigs pa bzhi snang ngo //
NK010(tha)012:3906: gnyid kyi sgra dang myos 'gyur ba yang gzhom //
NK010(tha)012:3907: gsang ba'i brda' bsrung le lo'i dgra spang ngo //
NK010(tha)012:3908: rang bzhin lta ba'i dam tshig bzhir snang ngo //
NK010(tha)012:3909: srid gsum yongs bsgral khams gsum zhing du blta //
NK010(tha)012:3910: dug gsum rtser 'gyur 'khor ba gnas 'gyur blta //
NK010(tha)012:3911: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig gsum du snang //
NK010(tha)012:3912: ma khrel tshul dang ma nyams pa yi mdo //
NK010(tha)012:3913: mthar phyin rtags dang rnam pa gsum du bstan //
NK010(tha)012:3914: ma nyams pa yi mdo la bzhi ru snang //
NK010(tha)012:3915: rtsa ba yan lag zhar gyis nyams bzhi'o //
NK010(tha)012:3916: mthar phyin rtags kyang de dag bzhi ru snang //
NK010(tha)012:3917: dam can 'du zhing mthu rtsal che ba dang //
NK010(tha)012:3918: byin rlabs che zhing rig pa chags pa gnyis //
NK010(tha)012:3920: mang pos bkur zhing grags thob pa bzhi'o //
NK010(tha)012:3921: lta ba nyams drod dam tshig rnam pa bzhi //
NK010(tha)012:3922: brdal ba chos nyid kyi lta ba ye 'byams lta bu'o //
NK010(tha)012:3923: rig pa ye shes kyi lta ba ye gsal du'o //
NK010(tha)012:3924: sprul pa phyag rgya'i lta ba ye gnas su'o //
NK010(tha)012:3925: khyab pa snying rje'i lta ba kun khyab pa'o //
NK010(tha)012:3926: lhag pa'i dam tshig don la ma gnas na //
NK010(tha)012:3927: ji ltar bsnyen cing bsgrubs kyang tshi chad pas //
NK010(tha)012:3928: gnyis med don gyi ngo bo rtogs par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:3929: don dam bsgrub pa'i don du ma yengs bsrungs //
NK010(tha)012:3930: dam tshig ma yengs gzhung yod na //
NK010(tha)012:3932: dpal chen khro bo'i rgyal pos bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3934: slar yang ngan sems brlag par bya'o //
NK010(tha)012:3937: phur pa rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud las dgongs pa
NK010(tha)012:3938: lung ston ltar rigs lnga'i dam tshig tu bsdus nas
NK010(tha)012:3939: bstan pa'i tshul / theg chen smod pa la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)012:3940: ci nas gsang bar nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3941: pha dang rigs kyi skyes pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:3942: gsad pas sangs rgyas rigs su nges //
NK010(tha)012:3943: slob dpon slob ma gsad nges na //
NK010(tha)012:3944: rdo rje'i rigs su nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3945: zhang po dmag pa gsad nges na //
NK010(tha)012:3946: rin chen rigs su nges pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3947: ma sring bu mo mo chags la //
NK010(tha)012:3948: chags par byas pa pad+ma can //
NK010(tha)012:3949: thams cad gsod cing las byed pa //
NK010(tha)012:3950: las kyi rigs su nges pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3951: de ltar dgongs pa'i rtog pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:3952: rgyal po yul 'khor gzhom par bya //
NK010(tha)012:3953: bram ze btson bzung rje'u rigs gsad //
NK010(tha)012:3954: dmangs rigs las bkol dug la spyad //
NK010(tha)012:3955: mi dge dang blang sbyor sgrol bya //
NK010(tha)012:3956: 'di ni sangs rgyas spyod pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3957: dug lnga las ni thams cad 'grub //
NK010(tha)012:3958: ces las kyi rlung dang de la zhon byed rnam
NK010(tha)012:3959: par rtog pa'i tshogs dbu ma'i grong khyer du gsad
NK010(tha)012:3960: pa dang / de bzhin du bcom bya ma yin
NK010(tha)012:3961: pa rgyal po dang yul 'khor gzhom pa ni kun
NK010(tha)012:3962: gzhi dang sred len sogs la brdar btags pa'i don
NK010(tha)012:3963: rig par byas nas nang gi nyon mongs pa dang
NK010(tha)012:3964: mi dge ba'i tshogs mnyam pa chen po'i lta ba
NK010(tha)012:3965: dang brtul zhugs kyis tshar chod pa'i tshe byang chub
NK010(tha)012:3966: sems dpa' la gzhan don du gnang ba'i lus ngag
NK010(tha)012:3967: gi mi dge ba bdun rjes thob kyi rol pa
NK010(tha)012:3968: tshad med pa'i snying rje chen po la sogs pa'i
NK010(tha)012:3969: gsang sngags kyi thabs chen zab mo dang du blangs
NK010(tha)012:3970: pa ni khyad par gyi dam tshig dang lta spyod
NK010(tha)012:3973: khyad par dam tshig bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:3974: slob dpon smad par mi bya ste //
NK010(tha)012:3975: ngan song gsum las thar mi 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:3976: khyad par lta ba bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:3977: ci yang med pa'i sems nyid la //
NK010(tha)012:3978: bcos su yod par ngas ma bstan //
NK010(tha)012:3979: khyad par spyod pa bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:3980: rig ma dag la spyod pa ste //
NK010(tha)012:3981: bza' ba'i zas la sngags bzlas la //
NK010(tha)012:3982: dam tshig can rnams spyan drangs te //
NK010(tha)012:3983: gdug pa rnam gnyis tshogs la bstim //
NK010(tha)012:3984: khyad par ting 'dzin bstan pa ni //
NK010(tha)012:3985: spyi bor ham la mgrin par h+r+aih snying gar h+aum la lte bar +amo //
NK010(tha)012:3986: yi ge gang yin yan lag la //
NK010(tha)012:3987: thabs kyi sbyor bas 'od du zhu //
NK010(tha)012:3988: de nyid yongs su khyab pa las //
NK010(tha)012:3989: nyal ba rgyun gyi ting 'dzin ni //
NK010(tha)012:3990: drug po bkag nas nyal ba'i tshe //
NK010(tha)012:3991: 'od gsal mthong ba nga yis bshad //
NK010(tha)012:3992: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)012:3993: yan lag nyi shu rtsa brgyad nyid //
NK010(tha)012:3994: dam tshig kun gyi gzhi dang rtsa //
NK010(tha)012:3995: spyod pa gtam col ci spyad kyang //
NK010(tha)012:3996: lta ba ma nyams dam tshig yin //
NK010(tha)012:3997: mo rnams kun la smad mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:3998: gdol pa mo yang dang du blang //
NK010(tha)012:3999: khyad par rigs can gces par bzung //
NK010(tha)012:4000: de yang dam tshig rtsa ba yin //
NK010(tha)012:4001: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:4002: de yang dam tshig rtsa ba yin //
NK010(tha)012:4003: tan gan spyod pa rgyun du spyod //
NK010(tha)012:4004: de yang dam tshig rtsa ba yin //
NK010(tha)012:4006: mdor bsdu na dam tshig gi rim pa de dag
NK010(tha)012:4007: kyang rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig la
NK010(tha)012:4008: 'du ba'i tshul / phur pa myang 'das chen po las /
NK010(tha)012:4009: don dam dam tshig gnyis med ston pa'i sgron ma la //
NK010(tha)012:4010: lta log ngan sems rku 'phrog brdeg la sogs //
NK010(tha)012:4011: ngan du smra zhing gnod pa dngos mi bgyid //
NK010(tha)012:4012: de dag dngos su byas na dmyal bar skye //
NK010(tha)012:4013: bzlas brjod sngags dang snying po bar mi gcad //
NK010(tha)012:4014: gsung gi dam tshig nyams na dmyal bar skye //
NK010(tha)012:4015: don dam gnyis med gzhan la spel mi bya //
NK010(tha)012:4016: rang gsang thabs kyis chod nas mi rtog pas //
NK010(tha)012:4017: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa de bzhin no //
NK010(tha)012:4018: zhes ston pa rdo rje slob dpon bkur zhing de
NK010(tha)012:4019: la ngan sems dang dpya sems ma shor ba dang
NK010(tha)012:4020: / bzlas brjod rgyun mi bcad pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:4021: gsang ba zab mo gzhan la mi sgrogs pa gsum
NK010(tha)012:4022: dang du blang bar bya zhing gal te de ltar
NK010(tha)012:4023: mi byed na nyams pa chen po yin pas ltung
NK010(tha)012:4026: lha spangs nyams pa chen po dang //
NK010(tha)012:4027: sngags dang phyag rgya nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4028: dran rtog lha ru ma rtogs nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4029: gsal la 'dzin med ma bsgoms nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4030: gnyan pa'i rim pa ma khur nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4031: brtse ba'i rim pa rgyun bcad nyams pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4032: gzungs ma mtshan ldan spangs pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4033: 'di rnams nyams pa'i rang bzhin yin //
NK010(tha)012:4034: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa na //
NK010(tha)012:4035: rdo rje dmyal bar skye bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:4037: byas pa mi 'grub mya ngan non //
NK010(tha)012:4039: phur pa myang 'das kyi rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:4040: de ltar dam la mi gnas na //
NK010(tha)012:4041: sa bon me yis tshigs pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:4042: t+aa la'i shing ni mgo bcad bzhin //
NK010(tha)012:4045: gal te nyams pa'i gnas la nyes byas dang mi
NK010(tha)012:4046: 'grogs par 'bum lnga'i bshags pas dag par bya ba'i
NK010(tha)012:4047: tshul yang / phur pa gsang rgyud las /
NK010(tha)012:4048: sku yi dam tshig nyams na sats+tsha 'bum //
NK010(tha)012:4049: gsung gi dam nyams bshags pa gsung rab 'bum //
NK010(tha)012:4050: thugs kyi dam nyams bshags pa srog 'don 'bum //
NK010(tha)012:4051: khyad par dam tshig bshags pa tshogs mchod 'bum //
NK010(tha)012:4052: lhag pa'i dam nyams pa la bshags pa 'bum //
NK010(tha)012:4053: 'bum lnga'i bshags pas mtshams med byas pa'ang 'byangs //
NK010(tha)012:4057: dam tshig bsrung ba'i las rnams kyi //
NK010(tha)012:4059: yi dam lha yi dngos grub myur //
NK010(tha)012:4060: 'jig rten dbang chen bran bzhin nyan //
NK010(tha)012:4063: rgyal po mdzod ldan zad med 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:4064: zhes gsang sngags kyi yon tan ni dam tshig gcig pu la brten nas 'byung bas na /
NK010(tha)012:4065: nyams pa'i nyes dmigs la 'jigs pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:4066: bsrung ba'i yon tan la brod pa bskyed nas rtag
NK010(tha)012:4067: tu dam tshig chen po'i rim pa las mi 'ada'o
NK010(tha)012:4069: gtso bos ji ltar sogs brjod /
NK010(tha)012:4070: de nas sku drin gtang rag gi yon la dngos
NK010(tha)012:4071: 'byor gyi 'bul bas dmigs rten byas nas zhing khams
NK010(tha)012:4074: de ltar bla ma lung ldan la //
NK010(tha)012:4075: gser la sogs pa'i yo byad dang //
NK010(tha)012:4076: rang gi lus dang nor gyi dbyig /
NK010(tha)012:4077: ma sring mo rnams brgyan pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4078: grong dang grong khyer bcas pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:4079: dmigs pa med pa'i sems kyis ni //
NK010(tha)012:4080: de dang mnyam pa kho nar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)012:4082: rigs so so dang mthun pa'i yon ni /
NK010(tha)012:4084: bdag lus srog dang nor la sogs //
NK010(tha)012:4085: bu dang chung mar bcas pa rnams //
NK010(tha)012:4086: zhum pa med pa'i sems kyis 'bul //
NK010(tha)012:4087: rdo rje rigs kyis yon yin no //
NK010(tha)012:4088: bran dang bcas pa'i 'don yon lnga //
NK010(tha)012:4089: 'khor lo can gyi yon yin no //
NK010(tha)012:4090: rin chen sna lnga la sogs dang //
NK010(tha)012:4091: glang po rta dang ma her bcas //
NK010(tha)012:4092: rin chen rigs kyi yon yin no //
NK010(tha)012:4093: ma dang sring mo chung ma dang //
NK010(tha)012:4094: rab tu brgyan pa dgod pa dang //
NK010(tha)012:4095: rgod ma la sogs mo chags rnams //
NK010(tha)012:4096: pad+ma rigs kyi yon du dbul //
NK010(tha)012:4097: rta dang glang chen ma he dang //
NK010(tha)012:4098: rdzas kyi rnam pa mang po bkal ba ni //
NK010(tha)012:4099: las kyi rigs kyi yon du dbul //
NK010(tha)012:4100: slob dpon man+dala khri la bzhugs //
NK010(tha)012:4101: gser la sogs pa'i rin po che //
NK010(tha)012:4102: dar gyi thum por bcug nas ni //
NK010(tha)012:4103: gzhan yang rdzas rnams ci 'bul ba //
NK010(tha)012:4104: slob dpon nyid la gtor te dbul //
NK010(tha)012:4106: de nas rjes bsngo smon gyis rgyas gdab pa dang /
NK010(tha)012:4107: tshogs kyi 'khor lo rgya chen po bskor ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:4113: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor badz+ra mus gshegs su gsol ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:4114: shes pa brjod pa sogs cho ga'i rjes chog spyi ltar bya /
NK010(tha)012:4115: gzugs brnyan rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bshig pa'i nyes
NK010(tha)012:4116: pa 'gegs phyir chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK010(tha)012:4117: don dran pa'i ngang nas a k+aa ro'i gsang sngags
NK010(tha)012:4118: bzla zhing rdo rje dang bcas pa'i lag gis thog
NK010(tha)012:4119: mar lha mtshan rnams nas cung zad re mgo bor
NK010(tha)012:4120: bkus la dbang ldan nas brtsams te lte ba'i bar
NK010(tha)012:4121: bsubs la rat+na'i bum par bstsal /
NK010(tha)012:4122: ras bris yin na brtan bzhugs bya /
NK010(tha)012:4123: rdul tshon gyi tshe cha gsum du bgos nas gter du sba ba dang /
NK010(tha)012:4125: chu klung la 'dor ba gsum du byed pa'am /
NK010(tha)012:4126: thams cad spos rol spyan gzigs la sogs pas sna drangs te chu klung chen po dang /
NK010(tha)012:4128: chu mig la sogs pa'i klu la rgyas par cho ga'i bya ba dang bcas pa'am /
NK010(tha)012:4129: rang bzhin du gtad pa'i tshul gyis gshegs shing /
NK010(tha)012:4130: rdul tshon gyi snod chus bkang ba dngos grub kyi
NK010(tha)012:4131: tshul du khyer nas dkyil 'khor gyi khang pa la
NK010(tha)012:4132: gtor ba dang / shis pa dang zhi ba'i las bya /
NK010(tha)012:4133: sgo byang dang rgyal chen la sngon 'gro'i skabs bzhin
NK010(tha)012:4134: gtang rag phul la gzugs brnyan gyi rten la brtan
NK010(tha)012:4135: bzhugs dang / tho la gshegs gsol bya zhing las kyi rjes rnams mi mngon par bsdu /
NK010(tha)012:4136: rgyun gyi spyod lam snang grags rig pa dkyil 'khor
NK010(tha)012:4137: gsum gyi rnal 'byor dang bsre zhing las kyi rjes
NK010(tha)012:4139: gnas la byin che dpal gyi mchims phu ru //
NK010(tha)012:4140: rang byung rdo rjee 'jigs med gling pa la //
NK010(tha)012:4141: rgyal dbang pad+ma'i dngos slob rlangs chen des //
NK010(tha)012:4142: ye shes sgyu ma'i sku mchog dngos bstan nas //
NK010(tha)012:4143: rnam dag rdo rje rim pa dbang gi rgyun //
NK010(tha)012:4144: gtor blugs mdzad pas gnas sbyin lhan skyes don //
NK010(tha)012:4145: mthong ba'i don gyi byi to ta ma la'i //
NK010(tha)012:4146: rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i dwangs bcud bsdus pa yin //
NK010(tha)012:4149: slob ma dbang bskur cho ga ni //
NK010(tha)012:4150: gang na'ang gcig gis rdzogs pa med //
NK010(tha)012:4151: de phyir mkhas pas cho ga ni //
NK010(tha)012:4152: rgyud kun las ni btu bar bya //
NK010(tha)012:4155: dge ba de yis lha sras khri srong gis //
NK010(tha)012:4156: lo pan spyan drangs 'bad pa don ldan du //
NK010(tha)012:4157: son pa rgyud kyi ring lugs dar gyur nas //
NK010(tha)012:4158: 'gro kun chos nyid phur bur sangs rgyas shog /
NK010(tha)012:4159: ces pa'ang dpal ldan sa skya'i phur khang chen mor
NK010(tha)012:4160: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas cho rigs
NK010(tha)012:4161: brgyud mar lhag pa'i lha mchog 'di nyid me tog
NK010(tha)012:4162: phog pa'i lha skal du che ba bdag chen rin
NK010(tha)012:4163: po che en+d+ra sany+dza gar+b+ha mched la rab gnas dang
NK010(tha)012:4164: 'brel bar dbang gi sgo 'phar dang por phye ba'i
NK010(tha)012:4165: tshe rdzogs chen pa mkhyen brtse'i 'oda zera gyis so
